# <a name="sensitive-information-type-entity-definitions"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-104">敏感資訊類型實體定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-104">Sensitive information type entity definitions</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-105">資料遺失防護 (規範中心中的 DLP) 包含許多可在 DLP 原則中使用的敏感資訊類型。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-105">Data loss prevention (DLP) in the Compliance Center includes many sensitive information types that are ready to use in your DLP policies.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="94f34-106">本文列出所有敏感資訊類型，並顯示 DLP 原則在偵測到每種類型時所尋找的功能。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-106">This article lists all of these sensitive information types and shows what a DLP policy looks for when it detects each type.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="94f34-107">敏感資訊類型是由正則運算式或函數所識別的模式所定義。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-107">A sensitive information type is defined by a pattern that can be identified by a regular expression or a function.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="94f34-108">確切證據（如關鍵字及校驗和）可用於識別敏感資訊類型。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-108">Corroborative evidence, like keywords and checksums, can be used to identify a sensitive information type.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="94f34-109">評估程式中也會使用信賴等級和近程。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-109">Confidence level and proximity are also used in the evaluation process.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-110">敏感資訊類型需要下列其中一項訂閱：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-110">Sensitive information types require one of these subscriptions:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-111">Microsoft 365 E3</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-111">Microsoft 365 E3</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-112">Microsoft 365 E5</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-112">Microsoft 365 E5</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-113">機密資訊類型的用途如下：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-113">Sensitive information types are used in:</span></span>

- [<span data-ttu-id="94f34-114">資料外洩防護原則</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-114">Data loss prevention policies</span></span>](data-loss-prevention-policies.md) 
- [<span data-ttu-id="94f34-115">敏感性標籤</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-115">Sensitivity labels</span></span>](sensitivity-labels.md)
- [<span data-ttu-id="94f34-116">保留標籤</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-116">Retention labels</span></span>](retention.md)
- [<span data-ttu-id="94f34-117">通訊合規性</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-117">Communication compliance</span></span>](communication-compliance.md)
- [<span data-ttu-id="94f34-118">自動標籤型原則</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-118">Auto-labelling policies</span></span>](apply-sensitivity-label-automatically.md#how-to-configure-auto-labeling-for-office-apps)

## <a name="aba-routing-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-119">ABA 路由號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-119">ABA routing number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-120">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-120">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-121">格式或未格式化的模式中的九位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-121">nine digits that may be in a formatted or unformatted pattern</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-122">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-122">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-123">格式 化：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-123">Formatted:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-124">以0、1、2、3、6、7或8開頭的四位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-124">four digits beginning with 0, 1, 2, 3, 6, 7, or 8</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-125">連字號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-125">a hyphen</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-126">四位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-126">four digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-127">連字號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-127">a hyphen</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-128">一個數位</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-128">a digit</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-129">未格式化：從0、1、2、3、6、7或8開始的九個連續數位</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-129">Unformatted: nine consecutive digits beginning with 0, 1, 2, 3, 6, 7, or 8</span></span> 

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-130">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-130">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-131">否</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-131">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-132">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-132">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-133">當接近300個字元以內時，原則就會偵測到這種敏感資訊類型：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-133">A policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-134">函數 Func_aba_routing 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-134">The function Func_aba_routing finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-135">會找到來自 Keyword_ABA_Routing 的關鍵字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-135">A keyword from Keyword_ABA_Routing is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-136">DLP 原則在接近300個字元以內時，偵測到此敏感資訊類型的信賴度很低：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-136">A DLP policy has low confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-137">函數 Func_aba_routing 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-137">The function Func_aba_routing finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
    <!-- ABA Routing Number -->
    <Entity id="cb353f78-2b72-4c3c-8827-92ebe4f69fdf" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_aba_routing" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_ABA_Routing" />
      </Pattern>
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_aba_routing" />
      </Pattern>
    </Entity>
```

- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-140">aba 編號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-140">aba number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-142">阿壩</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-142">aba</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-143">abarouting#</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-143">abarouting#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-144">abaroutingnumber</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-144">abaroutingnumber</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-145">americanbankassociationrouting#</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-145">americanbankassociationrouting#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-146">americanbankassociationroutingnumber</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-146">americanbankassociationroutingnumber</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-147">bankrouting#</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-147">bankrouting#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-148">bankroutingnumber</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-148">bankroutingnumber</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-149">路由#</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-149">routing #</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-150">路由編號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-150">routing no</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-151">路由編號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-151">routing number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-152">路由轉口號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-152">routing transit number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-153">路由#</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-153">routing#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-154">RTN</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-154">RTN</span></span>


## <a name="argentina-national-identity-dni-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-155">阿根廷國家身分識別 (DNI) 號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-155">Argentina national identity (DNI) number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-156">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-156">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-157">包含或不含句點的八位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-157">Eight digits with or without periods</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-158">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-158">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-159">八位數：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-159">Eight digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-160">兩位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-160">two digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-161">選用期間</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-161">an optional period</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-162">三位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-162">three digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-163">選用期間</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-163">an optional period</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-164">三位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-164">three digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-165">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-165">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-166">否</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-166">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-167">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-167">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-168">當鄰近性300個字元以內時，DLP 原則就會偵測到這種敏感資訊類型的信賴度。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-168">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-169">正則運算式 Regex_argentina_national_id 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-169">The regular expression Regex_argentina_national_id finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-170">會找到來自 Keyword_argentina_national_id 的關鍵字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-170">A keyword from Keyword_argentina_national_id is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Argentina National Identity (DNI) Number -->
<Entity id="eefbb00e-8282-433c-8620-8f1da3bffdb2" recommendedConfidence="75" patternsProximity="300">
   <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
      <IdMatch idRef="Regex_argentina_national_id"/>
      <Match idRef="Keyword_argentina_national_id"/>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-171">關鍵字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-171">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_argentina_national_id"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-172">Keyword_argentina_national_id</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-172">Keyword_argentina_national_id</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-173">阿根廷國內身分識別號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-173">Argentina National Identity number</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-174">cedula</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-174">cedula</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-175">cédula</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-175">cédula</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-176">dni</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-176">dni</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-177">documento nacional de identidad</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-177">documento nacional de identidad</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-178">documento número</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-178">documento número</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-179">documento numero</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-179">documento numero</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-180">registro nacional de 拉斯維加斯角色</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-180">registro nacional de las personas</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-181">rnp</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-181">rnp</span></span> 
   
## <a name="australia-bank-account-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-182">澳大利亞銀行帳戶號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-182">Australia bank account number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-183">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-183">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-184">具有或不含銀行狀態分公司號碼的六到十位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-184">six to ten digits with or without a bank state branch number</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-185">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-185">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-186">帳戶號碼是6到10位數。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-186">Account number is 6 to 10 digits.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-187">澳大利亞銀行狀態分支編號：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-187">Australia bank state branch number:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-188">三位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-188">three digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-189">連字號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-189">a hyphen</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-190">三位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-190">three digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-191">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-191">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-192">否</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-192">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-193">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-193">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-194">如果接近300個字元以內，則 DLP 原則偵測到此敏感資訊類型的置信量是85%：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-194">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-195">正則運算式 Regex_australia_bank_account_number 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-195">The regular expression Regex_australia_bank_account_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-196">會找到來自 Keyword_australia_bank_account_number 的關鍵字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-196">A keyword from Keyword_australia_bank_account_number is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-197">正則運算式 Regex_australia_bank_account_number_bsb 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-197">The regular expression Regex_australia_bank_account_number_bsb finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-198">如果接近300個字元以內，則 DLP 原則偵測到此敏感資訊類型的置信量是75%：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-198">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-199">正則運算式 Regex_australia_bank_account_number 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-199">The regular expression Regex_australia_bank_account_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-200">會找到來自 Keyword_australia_bank_account_number 的關鍵字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-200">A keyword from Keyword_australia_bank_account_number is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Australia Bank Account Number -->
<Entity id="74a54de9-2a30-4aa0-a8aa-3d9327fc07c7" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
        <IdMatch idRef="Regex_australia_bank_account_number" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_australia_bank_account_number" />
        <Match idRef="Regex_australia_bank_account_number_bsb" />
  </Pattern>
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Regex_australia_bank_account_number" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_australia_bank_account_number" />
  </Pattern>
 </Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-201">關鍵字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-201">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_australia_bank_account_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-202">Keyword_australia_bank_account_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-202">Keyword_australia_bank_account_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-203">swift 銀行代碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-203">swift bank code</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-204">通信銀行</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-204">correspondent bank</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-205">基礎貨幣</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-205">base currency</span></span>

## <a name="australia-business-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-216">澳大利亞商務電話號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-216">Australia business number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="94f34-217">此機密資訊類型僅可用於下列專案：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-217">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-218">資料遺失防護原則</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-218">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-219">通訊相容性原則</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-219">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-220">資訊管理</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-220">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-221">記錄管理</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-221">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-222">Microsoft cloud app security</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-222">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>


### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-223">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-223">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-224">11位數（選用分隔符號）</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-224">11 digits with optional delimiters</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-225">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-225">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-226">11位數（選用分隔符號）：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-226">11 digits with optional delimiters:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-227">兩位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-227">two digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-228">選用的連字號或空格</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-228">an optional hyphen or space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-229">三位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-229">three digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-230">選用的連字號或空格</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-230">an optional hyphen or space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-231">三位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-231">three digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-232">選用的連字號或空格</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-232">an optional hyphen or space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-233">三位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-233">three digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-234">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-234">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-235">是</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-235">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-236">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-236">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-237">當鄰近性300個字元以內時，DLP 原則就會偵測到這種敏感資訊類型：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-237">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-238">函數 Func_australian_business_number 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-238">The function Func_australian_business_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-239">會找到來自 Keywords_australian_business_number 的關鍵字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-239">A keyword from Keywords_australian_business_number is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-240">當鄰近性300個字元以內時，DLP 原則就會偵測到這種敏感資訊類型的信賴度。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-240">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-241">函數 Func_australian_business_number 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-241">The function Func_australian_business_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Australia Business Number -->
      <Entity id="76e83b3b-01ee-4530-aced-e667a6609f49" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_australian_business_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_australian_business_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_australian_business_number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-244">澳大利亞商務版否</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-244">australia business no</span></span>

## <a name="australia-company-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-251">澳大利亞公司號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-251">Australia company number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="94f34-252">此機密資訊類型僅可用於下列專案：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-252">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-253">資料遺失防護原則</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-253">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-254">通訊相容性原則</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-254">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-255">資訊管理</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-255">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-256">記錄管理</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-256">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-257">Microsoft cloud app security</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-257">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-258">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-258">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-259">具有分隔符號的九位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-259">nine digits with delimiters</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-260">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-260">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-261">九位數的分隔符號：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-261">nine digits with delimiters:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-262">三位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-262">three digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-263">一個空格</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-263">a space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-264">三位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-264">three digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-265">一個空格</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-265">a space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-266">三位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-266">three digits</span></span>


### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-267">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-267">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-268">是</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-268">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-269">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-269">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-270">當鄰近性300個字元以內時，DLP 原則就會偵測到這種敏感資訊類型：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-270">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-271">函數 Func_Australian_Company_Number 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-271">The function Func_Australian_Company_Number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-272">會找到來自 Keyword_Australian_Company_Number 的關鍵字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-272">A keyword from Keyword_Australian_Company_Number is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-273">DLP 原則在接近300個字元以內時，偵測到此敏感資訊類型的信賴度很低：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-273">A DLP policy has low confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-274">函數 Func_Australian_Company_Number 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-274">The function Func_Australian_Company_Number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Australia Company Number -->
      <Entity id="b1fba4f7-7b3e-4bb9-8f9a-9366df604dbb" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_Australian_Company_Number" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_Australian_Company_Number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_Australian_Company_Number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```
### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-275">關鍵字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-275">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_australia_company_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-276">Keyword_australia_company_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-276">Keyword_australia_company_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-277">可以</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-277">acn</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-278">澳大利亞公司 no</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-278">australia company no</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-279">澳大利亞公司 no#</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-279">australia company no#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-280">澳大利亞公司號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-280">australia company number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-281">澳大利亞公司無</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-281">australian company no</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-282">澳大利亞公司無#</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-282">australian company no#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-283">澳大利亞公司號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-283">australian company number</span></span>

## <a name="australia-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-284">澳大利亞駕駛執照號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-284">Australia driver's license number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-285">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-285">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-286">九個字母和數位</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-286">nine letters and digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-287">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-287">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-288">九個字母和數位：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-288">nine letters and digits:</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-289">兩位數的數位或字母 (不區分大小寫) </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-289">two digits or letters (not case-sensitive)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-290">兩位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-290">two digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-291">五個數字或字母 (不區分大小寫) </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-291">five digits or letters (not case-sensitive)</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-292">「或」</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-292">OR</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-293">一個至兩個選用的字母 (不區分大小寫) </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-293">one to two optional letters (not case-sensitive)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-294">四到九位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-294">four to nine digits</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-295">「或」</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-295">OR</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-296">九個數字或字母 (不區分大小寫) </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-296">nine digits or letters (not case-sensitive)</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-297">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-297">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-298">否</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-298">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-299">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-299">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-300">當鄰近性300個字元以內時，DLP 原則就會偵測到這種敏感資訊類型的信賴度。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-300">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-301">正則運算式 Regex_australia_drivers_license_number 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-301">The regular expression Regex_australia_drivers_license_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-302">會找到來自 Keyword_australia_drivers_license_number 的關鍵字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-302">A keyword from Keyword_australia_drivers_license_number is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-303">找不到 Keyword_australia_drivers_license_number_exclusions 的關鍵字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-303">No keyword from Keyword_australia_drivers_license_number_exclusions is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Australia Drivers License Number -->
<Entity id="1cbbc8f5-9216-4392-9eb5-5ac2298d1356" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
   <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Regex_australia_drivers_license_number" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_australia_drivers_license_number" />
        <Any minMatches="0" maxMatches="0">
          <Match idRef="Keyword_australia_drivers_license_number_exclusions" />
        </Any>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-308">國際駕駛允許</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-308">international driving permit</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-309">DriverLicence</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-309">DriverLicence</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-310">DriverLicences</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-310">DriverLicences</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-311">驅動程式許可證</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-311">Driver Lic</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-312">驅動程式許可證</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-312">Driver Licence</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-313">驅動程式授權</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-313">Driver Licences</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-314">DriversLic</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-314">DriversLic</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-315">DriversLicence</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-315">DriversLicence</span></span>

## <a name="australia-medical-account-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-403">澳大利亞醫療帳戶號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-403">Australia medical account number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-404">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-404">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-405">10-11 位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-405">10-11 digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-406">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-406">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-407">10-11 位數：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-407">10-11 digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-408">第一個數位是在2-6 範圍內</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-408">First digit is in the range 2-6</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-409">九個數字是檢查碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-409">Nine digit is a check digit</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-410">第十個數字是問題的位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-410">Tenth digit is the issue digit</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-411">第十個數字 (選用) 是個別數位</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-411">Eleventh digit (optional) is the individual number</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-412">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-412">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-413">是</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-413">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-414">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-414">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-415">當鄰近性300個字元以內時，DLP 原則就會偵測到這種敏感資訊類型：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-415">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-416">函數 Func_australian_medical_account_number 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-416">The function Func_australian_medical_account_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-417">會找到來自 Keyword_Australia_Medical_Account_Number 的關鍵字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-417">A keyword from Keyword_Australia_Medical_Account_Number is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-418">校驗和通過。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-418">The checksum passes.</span></span>


```xml
  <!-- Australia Medical Account Number -->
<Entity id="104a99a0-3d3b-4542-a40d-ab0b9e1efe63" recommendedConfidence="85" patternsProximity="300">
    <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
     <IdMatch idRef="Func_australian_medical_account_number"/>
     <Match idRef="Keyword_Australia_Medical_Account_Number"/>
    </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-419">關鍵字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-419">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_australia_medical_account_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-420">Keyword_Australia_Medical_Account_Number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-420">Keyword_Australia_Medical_Account_Number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-421">銀行帳戶詳細資料</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-421">bank account details</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-422">medicare 付款</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-422">medicare payments</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-423">抵押帳戶</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-423">mortgage account</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-424">銀行付款</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-424">bank payments</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-425">資訊分支</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-425">information branch</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-426">信用卡貸款</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-426">credit card loan</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-427">人體服務部門</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-427">department of human services</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-428">本機服務</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-428">local service</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-429">醫療</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-429">medicare</span></span>

   
## <a name="australia-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-430">澳大利亞護照號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-430">Australia passport number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-431">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-431">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-432">字母后接7位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-432">A letter followed by seven digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-433">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-433">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-434">字母 (不區分大小寫) 後接7位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-434">A letter (not case-sensitive) followed by seven digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-435">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-435">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-436">否</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-436">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-437">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-437">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-438">當鄰近性300個字元以內時，DLP 原則就會偵測到這種敏感資訊類型的信賴度。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-438">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-439">正則運算式 Regex_australia_passport_number 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-439">The regular expression Regex_australia_passport_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-440">會找到 Keyword_passport 或 Keyword_australia_passport_number 中的關鍵字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-440">A keyword from Keyword_passport or Keyword_australia_passport_number is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Australia Passport Number -->
<Entity id="29869db6-602d-4853-ab93-3484f905df50" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Regex_australia_passport_number" />
        <Any minMatches="1">
          <Match idRef="Keyword_passport" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_australia_passport_number" />
        </Any>
   </Pattern>
</Entity>   
```

## <a name="australia-tax-file-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-474">澳大利亞稅收檔編號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-474">Australia tax file number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-475">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-475">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-476">8至九位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-476">eight to nine digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-477">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-477">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-478">通常會以空格呈現的八至九位數，如下所示：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-478">eight to nine digits typically presented with spaces as follows:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-479">三位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-479">three digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-480">選擇性的空格</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-480">an optional space</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-481">三位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-481">three digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-482">選擇性的空格</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-482">an optional space</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-483">二到三位數的最後一個數位是檢查碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-483">two to three digits where the last digit is a check digit</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-484">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-484">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-485">是</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-485">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-486">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-486">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-487">當鄰近性300個字元以內時，DLP 原則就會偵測到這種敏感資訊類型：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-487">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-488">函數 Func_australian_tax_file_number 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-488">The function Func_australian_tax_file_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-489">找不到 Keyword_Australia_Tax_File_Number 或 Keyword_number_exclusions 的關鍵字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-489">No keyword from Keyword_Australia_Tax_File_Number or Keyword_number_exclusions is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-490">校驗和通過。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-490">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
   <!-- Australia Tax File Number -->
    <Entity id="e29bc95f-ff70-4a37-aa01-04d17360a4c5" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_australian_tax_file_number" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_Australia_Tax_File_Number" />
      </Pattern>
    </Entity>
```

## <a name="austria-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-502">奧地利駕駛執照號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-502">Austria driver's license number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-503">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-503">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-504">不含空格及分隔符號的八位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-504">eight digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-505">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-505">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-506">八位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-506">eight digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-507">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-507">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-508">否</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-508">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-509">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-509">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-510">當鄰近性300個字元以內時，DLP 原則就會偵測到這種敏感資訊類型的信賴度。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-510">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-511">正則運算式會  `Regex_austria_eu_driver's_license_number` 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-511">The regular expression  `Regex_austria_eu_driver's_license_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-512">`Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number`找到或的關鍵字 `Keywords_austria_eu_driver's_license_number` 。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-512">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` or `Keywords_austria_eu_driver's_license_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Austria Driver's License Number -->
      <Entity id="682f18ce-44eb-482b-8198-2bcb96a0761e" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_austria_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_austria_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="austria-identity-card"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-639">奧地利身分識別卡</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-639">Austria identity card</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="94f34-640">此機密資訊類型僅可用於下列專案：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-640">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-641">資料遺失防護原則</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-641">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-642">通訊相容性原則</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-642">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-643">資訊管理</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-643">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-644">記錄管理</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-644">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-645">Microsoft cloud app security</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-645">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-646">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-646">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-647">字母、數位及特殊字元的24個字元的組合</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-647">A 24-character combination of letters, digits, and special characters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-648">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-648">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-649">24個字元：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-649">24 characters:</span></span>
  
-  <span data-ttu-id="94f34-650">22個字母 (不區分大小寫) 、數位、反斜線、正斜線或正號）</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-650">22 letters (not case-sensitive), digits, backslashes, forward slashes, or plus signs</span></span> 
    
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-651">兩個字母 (不區分大小寫) 、數位、反斜線、正斜線、加號或等號）</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-651">two letters (not case-sensitive), digits, backslashes, forward slashes, plus signs, or equal signs</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-652">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-652">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-653">不適用</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-653">Not applicable</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-654">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-654">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-655">當鄰近性300個字元以內時，DLP 原則就會偵測到這種敏感資訊類型的信賴度。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-655">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-656">正則運算式會  `Regex_austria_eu_national_id_card` 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-656">The regular expression  `Regex_austria_eu_national_id_card` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-657">找到來自的關鍵字  `Keywords_austria_eu_national_id_card` 。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-657">A keyword from  `Keywords_austria_eu_national_id_card` is found.</span></span> 
   
```xml
      <!-- Austria Identity Card -->
      <Entity id="5ec06c3b-007e-4820-8343-7ff73b889735" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_austria_eu_national_id_card" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_austria_eu_national_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-658">關鍵字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-658">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keywords_austria_eu_national_id_card"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-659">Keywords_austria_eu_national_id_card</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-659">Keywords_austria_eu_national_id_card</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-660">身分識別號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-660">identity number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-661">國家識別碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-661">national id</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-662">personalausweis republik österreich</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-662">personalausweis republik österreich</span></span>

## <a name="austria-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-663">奧地利護照號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-663">Austria passport number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-664">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-664">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-665">一個字母后接一個選擇性的空格和七位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-665">One letter followed by an optional space and seven digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-666">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-666">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-667">一個字母、七位數和一個空格的組合：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-667">A combination of one letter, seven digits, and one space:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-668">一個字母 (不區分大小寫) </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-668">one letter (not case-sensitive)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-669">一個空格 (選用) </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-669">one space (optional)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-670">七位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-670">seven digits</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-671">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-671">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-672">不適用</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-672">not applicable</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-673">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-673">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-674">當鄰近性300個字元以內時，DLP 原則就會偵測到這種敏感資訊類型：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-674">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-675">正則運算式會  `Regex_austria_eu_passport_number` 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-675">The regular expression  `Regex_austria_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-676">`Keywords_eu_passport_number`找到或的關鍵字 `Keywords_austria_eu_passport_number` 。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-676">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_austria_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-677">正則運算式 `Regex_eu_passport_date1` 會發現日期格式為 DD YYYY 或關鍵字 from `Keywords_eu_passport_date`</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-677">The regular expression `Regex_eu_passport_date1` finds date in the format DD.MM.YYYY or a keyword from `Keywords_eu_passport_date` is found</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-678">當鄰近性300個字元以內時，DLP 原則就會偵測到這種敏感資訊類型的信賴度。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-678">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-679">正則運算式會  `Regex_austria_eu_passport_number` 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-679">The regular expression  `Regex_austria_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-680">`Keywords_eu_passport_number`找到或的關鍵字 `Keywords_austria_eu_passport_number` 。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-680">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_austria_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Austria Passport Number -->
      <Entity id="1c96ae4e-303b-447d-86c7-77113ac266bf" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_austria_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_austria_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Regex_eu_passport_date1" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_date" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_austria_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_austria_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="austria-social-security-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-704">奧地利的社會安全號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-704">Austria social security number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-705">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-705">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-706">指定之格式的10位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-706">10 digits in the specified format</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-707">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-707">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-708">10位數：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-708">10 digits:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-709">對應至序列值的三位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-709">three digits that correspond to a serial number</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-710">一個檢查碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-710">one check digit</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-711">對應至出生日期 (DDMMYY 的六位數) </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-711">six digits that correspond to the birth date (DDMMYY)</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-712">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-712">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-713">是</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-713">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-714">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-714">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-715">當鄰近性300個字元以內時，DLP 原則就會偵測到這種敏感資訊類型：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-715">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-716">函數  `Func_austria_eu_ssn_or_equivalent` 會找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-716">The function  `Func_austria_eu_ssn_or_equivalent` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-717">找到來自的關鍵字  `Keywords_austria_eu_ssn_or_equivalent` 。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-717">a keyword from  `Keywords_austria_eu_ssn_or_equivalent` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="94f34-718">當鄰近性300個字元以內時，DLP 原則就會偵測到這種敏感資訊類型的信賴度。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-718">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-719">函數  `Func_austria_eu_ssn_or_equivalent` 會找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-719">The function  `Func_austria_eu_ssn_or_equivalent` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Austria Social Security Number -->
      <Entity id="6896a906-86c9-4d19-a2da-6e43ccd19b7b" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_austria_eu_ssn_or_equivalent" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_austria_eu_ssn_or_equivalent" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_austria_eu_ssn_or_equivalent" />
          <Any minMatches="0" maxMatches="0">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_austria_eu_telephone_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_austria_eu_mobile_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="austria-tax-identification-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-745">奧地利納稅識別號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-745">Austria tax identification number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-746">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-746">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-747">具有選擇性連字號及正斜線的九位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-747">nine digits with optional hyphen and forward slash</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-748">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-748">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-749">具有選擇性連字號及正斜線的九位數：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-749">nine digits with optional hyphen and forward slash:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-750">兩位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-750">two digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-751">連字號 (選用) </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-751">a hyphen (optional)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-752">三位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-752">three digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-753">轉寄斜線 (選用) </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-753">a forward slash (optional)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-754">四位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-754">four digits</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-755">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-755">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-756">是</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-756">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-757">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-757">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-758">當鄰近性300個字元以內時，DLP 原則就會偵測到這種敏感資訊類型：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-758">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-759">函數  `Func_austria_eu_tax_file_number` 會找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-759">The function  `Func_austria_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-760">找到來自的關鍵字  `Keywords_austria_eu_tax_file_number` 。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-760">A keyword from  `Keywords_austria_eu_tax_file_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="94f34-761">DLP 原則在接近300個字元以內時，偵測到此敏感資訊類型的信賴度很低：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-761">A DLP policy has low confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-762">函數  `Func_austria_eu_tax_file_number` 會找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-762">The function  `Func_austria_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Austria Tax Identification Number -->
      <Entity id="4fd58d22-af28-4451-b18a-6f722430a56d" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_austria_eu_tax_file_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_austria_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_austria_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="austria-value-added-tax"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-785">奧地利加值稅</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-785">Austria value added tax</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="94f34-786">此機密資訊類型僅可用於下列專案：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-786">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-787">資料遺失防護原則</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-787">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-788">通訊相容性原則</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-788">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-789">資訊管理</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-789">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-790">記錄管理</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-790">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-791">Microsoft cloud app security</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-791">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-792">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-792">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-793">11個字元的數位元格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-793">11-character alphanumeric pattern</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-794">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-794">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-795">11個字元的字母數位模式：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-795">11-character alphanumeric pattern:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-796">A 或 a</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-796">A or a</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-797">T 或 t</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-797">T or t</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-798">選擇性空格</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-798">Optional space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-799">U 或 u</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-799">U or u</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-800">選擇性空格</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-800">optional space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-801">兩位數或三位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-801">two or three digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-802">選擇性空格</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-802">optional space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-803">四位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-803">four digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-804">選擇性空格</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-804">optional space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-805">一或兩位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-805">one or two digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-806">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-806">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-807">是</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-807">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-808">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-808">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-809">當鄰近性300個字元以內時，DLP 原則就會偵測到這種敏感資訊類型：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-809">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-810">函數 Func_Austria_Value_Added_Tax 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-810">The function Func_Austria_Value_Added_Tax finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-811">會找到來自 Keyword_Austria_Value_Added_Tax 的關鍵字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-811">A keyword from Keyword_Austria_Value_Added_Tax is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-812">當鄰近性300個字元以內時，DLP 原則就會偵測到這種敏感資訊類型的信賴度。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-812">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-813">函數 Func_Austria_Value_Added_Tax 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-813">The function Func_Austria_Value_Added_Tax finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Austria Value Added Tax -->
      <Entity id="b6a3eda2-c56c-4b69-a5f7-dca34db00f48" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_Austria_Value_Added_Tax" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_Austria_Value_Added_Tax" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_Austria_Value_Added_Tax" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-819">加值稅編號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-819">vat no.</span></span>

## <a name="azure-documentdb-auth-key"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-831">Azure DocumentDB 驗證金鑰</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-831">Azure DocumentDB auth key</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-832">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-832">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-833">字串 "DocumentDb"，後面加上下列模式中所述的字元及字串。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-833">The string "DocumentDb" followed by the characters and strings outlined in the pattern below.</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-834">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-834">Pattern</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-835">字串 "DocumentDb"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-835">The string "DocumentDb"</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-836">介於3-200 小寫或大寫字母、數位、符號、特殊字元或空格之間的任何組合</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-836">Any combination of between 3-200 lower- or uppercase letters, digits, symbols, special characters, or spaces</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-837">大於符號 (>) 、等號 (=) 、引號 ( ") 或撇號 ( ' ) </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-837">A greater than symbol (>), an equal sign (=), a quotation mark ("), or an apostrophe (')</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-838">任何86小寫或大寫字母、數位、正斜線 (/) 或加號 (+) 的組合</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-838">Any combination of 86 lower- or uppercase letters, digits, forward slash (/), or plus sign (+)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-839">兩個等號 (=) </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-839">Two equal signs (=)</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-840">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-840">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-841">否</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-841">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-842">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-842">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-843">當鄰近性300個字元以內時，DLP 原則就會偵測到這種敏感資訊類型：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-843">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-844">正則運算式 CEP_Regex_AzureDocumentDBAuthKey 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-844">The regular expression CEP_Regex_AzureDocumentDBAuthKey finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-845">正則運算式 CEP_CommonExampleKeywords 找不到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-845">The regular expression CEP_CommonExampleKeywords doesn't find content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Azure Document DB Auth Key -->
<Entity id="0f587d92-eb28-44a9-bd1c-90f2892b47aa" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
        <IdMatch idRef="CEP_Regex_AzureDocumentDBAuthKey" />
        <Any minMatches="0" maxMatches="0">
            <Match idRef="CEP_CommonExampleKeywords" />
          </Any>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-853">onebox</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-853">onebox</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-858">s-int。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-858">s-int.</span></span><!--no-hyperlink--><span data-ttu-id="94f34-859">網</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-859">net</span></span>

## <a name="azure-iaas-database-connection-string-and-azure-sql-connection-string"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-860">Azure IAAS 資料庫連接字串和 Azure SQL 連接字串</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-860">Azure IAAS database connection string and Azure SQL connection string</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-861">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-861">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-862">字串 "Server"、"server" 或 "data source"，後面加上模式中所述的字元及字串（包括字串 "cloudapp"）。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-862">The string "Server", "server", or "data source" followed by the characters and strings outlined in the pattern below, including the string "cloudapp.azure.</span></span><!--no-hyperlink--><span data-ttu-id="94f34-863">com "或" cloudapp。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-863">com" or "cloudapp.azure.</span></span><!--no-hyperlink--><span data-ttu-id="94f34-864">net "或" database。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-864">net" or "database.windows.</span></span><!--no-hyperlink--><span data-ttu-id="94f34-865">net "，及字串" Password "或" password "或" pwd "。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-865">net", and the string "Password" or "password" or "pwd".</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-866">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-866">Pattern</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-867">字串「伺服器」、「伺服器」或「資料來源」</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-867">the string "Server", "server", or "data source"</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-868">零至兩個空白字元</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-868">zero to two whitespace characters</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-869">等號 (=) </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-869">an equal sign (=)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-870">零至兩個空白字元</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-870">zero to two whitespace characters</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-871">介於1-200 小寫或大寫字母、數位、符號、特殊字元或空格之間的任何組合</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-871">any combination of between 1-200 lower- or uppercase letters, digits, symbols, special characters, or spaces</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-872">字串 "cloudapp"。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-872">The string "cloudapp.azure.</span></span><!--no-hyperlink--><span data-ttu-id="94f34-873">com "，" cloudapp。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-873">com", "cloudapp.azure.</span></span><!--no-hyperlink--><span data-ttu-id="94f34-874">net "或" database。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-874">net", or "database.windows.</span></span><!--no-hyperlink--><span data-ttu-id="94f34-875">真實</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-875">net"</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-876">介於1-300 小寫或大寫字母、數位、符號、特殊字元或空格之間的任何組合</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-876">any combination of between 1-300 lower- or uppercase letters, digits, symbols, special characters, or spaces</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-877">字串 "Password"、"password" 或 "pwd"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-877">the string "Password", "password", or "pwd"</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-878">零至兩個空白字元</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-878">zero to two whitespace characters</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-879">等號 (=) </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-879">an equal sign (=)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-880">零至兩個空白字元</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-880">zero to two whitespace characters</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-881">一個或多個不是分號的字元 (; ) 、引號 ( ") 或單引號 ( ' ) </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-881">one or more characters that aren't a semicolon (;), quotation mark ("), or apostrophe (')</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-882">分號 (; ) ，引號 ( ") 或單引號 ( ' ) </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-882">a semicolon (;), quotation mark ("), or apostrophe (')</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-883">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-883">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-884">否</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-884">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-885">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-885">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-886">當鄰近性300個字元以內時，DLP 原則就會偵測到這種敏感資訊類型：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-886">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-887">正則運算式 CEP_Regex_AzureConnectionString 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-887">The regular expression CEP_Regex_AzureConnectionString finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-888">正則運算式 CEP_CommonExampleKeywords 找不到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-888">The regular expression CEP_CommonExampleKeywords doesn't find content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
<!--Azure IAAS Database Connection String and Azure SQL Connection String-->
<Entity id="ce1a126d-186f-4700-8c0c-486157b953fd" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
        <IdMatch idRef="CEP_Regex_AzureConnectionString" />
        <Any minMatches="0" maxMatches="0">
            <Match idRef="CEP_CommonExampleKeywords" />
        </Any>
    </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-889">關鍵字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-889">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="cep_common_example_keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-890">CEP_common_example_keywords</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-890">CEP_common_example_keywords</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-891"> (技術上而言，這個敏感資訊類型是使用正則運算式來識別這些關鍵字，而不是關鍵字清單。 ) </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-891">(Technically, this sensitive information type identifies these keywords by using a regular expression, not a keyword list.)</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-892">尚未</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-892">contoso</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-893">送交</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-893">fabrikam</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-894">資料庫</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-894">northwind</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-895">沙 箱</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-895">sandbox</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-896">onebox</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-896">onebox</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-897">本地 主機</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-897">localhost</span></span>
