## <a name="azure-iot-connection-string"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-903">Azure IoT 連接字串</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-903">Azure IoT connection string</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-904">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-904">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-905">字串 "HostName"，後面加上下列模式中所述的字元及字串，包括字串 "azure 裝置。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-905">The string "HostName" followed by the characters and strings outlined in the pattern below, including the strings "azure-devices.</span></span><!--no-hyperlink--><span data-ttu-id="94f34-906">net "和" SharedAccessKey "。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-906">net" and "SharedAccessKey".</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-907">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-907">Pattern</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-908">字串 "HostName"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-908">the string "HostName"</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-909">零至兩個空白字元</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-909">zero to two whitespace characters</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-910">等號 (=) </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-910">an equal sign (=)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-911">零至兩個空白字元</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-911">zero to two whitespace characters</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-912">介於1-200 小寫或大寫字母、數位、符號、特殊字元或空格之間的任何組合</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-912">any combination of between 1-200 lower- or uppercase letters, digits, symbols, special characters, or spaces</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-913">"azure 裝置" 字串。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-913">the string "azure-devices.</span></span><!--no-hyperlink--><span data-ttu-id="94f34-914">真實</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-914">net"</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-915">介於1-200 小寫或大寫字母、數位、符號、特殊字元或空格之間的任何組合</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-915">any combination of between 1-200 lower- or uppercase letters, digits, symbols, special characters, or spaces</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-916">字串 "SharedAccessKey"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-916">the string "SharedAccessKey"</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-917">零至兩個空白字元</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-917">zero to two whitespace characters</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-918">等號 (=) </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-918">an equal sign (=)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-919">零至兩個空白字元</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-919">zero to two whitespace characters</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-920">任何43小寫或大寫字母、數位、正斜線 (/) 或加號 (+) 的組合</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-920">any combination of 43 lower- or uppercase letters, digits, forward slash (/), or plus sign (+)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-921">等號 (=) </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-921">an equal sign (=)</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-922">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-922">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-923">否</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-923">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-924">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-924">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-925">當鄰近性300個字元以內時，DLP 原則就會偵測到這種敏感資訊類型：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-925">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-926">正則運算式 CEP_Regex_AzureIoTConnectionString 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-926">The regular expression CEP_Regex_AzureIoTConnectionString finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-927">正則運算式 CEP_CommonExampleKeywords 找不到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-927">The regular expression CEP_CommonExampleKeywords doesn't find content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
<!--Azure IoT Connection String-->
<Entity id="0b34bec3-d5d6-4974-b7b0-dcdb5c90c29d" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
        <IdMatch idRef="CEP_Regex_AzureIoTConnectionString" />
        <Any minMatches="0" maxMatches="0">
            <Match idRef="CEP_CommonExampleKeywords" />
        </Any>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="azure-publish-setting-password"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-942">Azure 發佈設定密碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-942">Azure publish setting password</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-943">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-943">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-944">字串 "userpwd ="，後面加上字母元字串。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-944">The string "userpwd=" followed by an alphanumeric string.</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-945">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-945">Pattern</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-946">字串 "userpwd ="</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-946">the string "userpwd="</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-947">任何60小寫字母或數位的組合</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-947">any combination of 60 lowercase letters or digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-948">引號 ( ") </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-948">a quotation mark (")</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-949">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-949">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-950">否</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-950">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-951">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-951">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-952">當鄰近性300個字元以內時，DLP 原則就會偵測到這種敏感資訊類型：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-952">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-953">正則運算式 CEP_Regex_AzurePublishSettingPasswords 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-953">The regular expression CEP_Regex_AzurePublishSettingPasswords finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-954">正則運算式 CEP_CommonExampleKeywords 找不到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-954">The regular expression CEP_CommonExampleKeywords doesn't find content that matches the pattern.</span></span>


```xml
<!--Azure Publish Setting Password-->
<Entity id="75f4cc8a-a68e-49e5-89ce-fa8f03d286a5" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
       <IdMatch idRef="CEP_Regex_AzurePublishSettingPasswords" />
       <Any minMatches="0" maxMatches="0">
           <Match idRef="CEP_CommonExampleKeywords" />
       </Any>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="azure-redis-cache-connection-string"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-969">Azure Redis cache connection string</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-969">Azure Redis cache connection string</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-970">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-970">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-971">字串 "redis。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-971">The string "redis.cache.windows.</span></span><!--no-hyperlink--><span data-ttu-id="94f34-972">net "後接下列模式中所述的字元和字串，包含字串" password "或" pwd "。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-972">net" followed by the characters and strings outlined in the pattern below, including the string "password" or "pwd".</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-973">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-973">Pattern</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-974">字串 "redis。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-974">the string "redis.cache.windows.</span></span><!--no-hyperlink--><span data-ttu-id="94f34-975">真實</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-975">net"</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-976">介於1-200 小寫或大寫字母、數位、符號、特殊字元或空格之間的任何組合</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-976">any combination of between 1-200 lower- or uppercase letters, digits, symbols, special characters, or spaces</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-977">字串 "password" 或 "pwd"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-977">the string "password" or "pwd"</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-978">零至兩個空白字元</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-978">zero to two whitespace characters</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-979">等號 (=) </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-979">an equal sign (=)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-980">零至兩個空白字元</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-980">zero to two whitespace characters</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-981">43個字元的任何組合，其為小寫或大寫字母、數位、正斜線 (/) 或加號 (+) </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-981">any combination of 43 characters that are lower- or uppercase letters, digits, forward slash (/), or plus sign (+)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-982">等號 (=) </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-982">an equal sign (=)</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-983">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-983">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-984">否</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-984">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-985">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-985">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-986">如果接近300個字元以內，則 DLP 原則偵測到此敏感資訊類型的置信量是85%：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-986">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-987">正則運算式 CEP_Regex_AzureRedisCacheConnectionString 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-987">The regular expression CEP_Regex_AzureRedisCacheConnectionString finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-988">正則運算式 CEP_CommonExampleKeywords 找不到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-988">The regular expression CEP_CommonExampleKeywords doesn't find content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
<!--Azure Redis Cache Connection String-->
<Entity id="095a7e6c-efd8-46d5-af7b-5298d53a49fc" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
        <IdMatch idRef="CEP_Regex_AzureRedisCacheConnectionString" />
        <Any minMatches="0" maxMatches="0">
            <Match idRef="CEP_CommonExampleKeywords" />
        </Any>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="azure-sas"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-1003">Azure SAS</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-1003">Azure SAS</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-1004">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-1004">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-1005">字串 "sig"，後面加上下列模式中所述的字元及字串。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-1005">The string "sig" followed by the characters and strings outlined in the pattern below.</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-1006">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-1006">Pattern</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-1007">字串 "sig"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-1007">the string "sig"</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-1008">零至兩個空白字元</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-1008">zero to two whitespace characters</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-1009">等號 (=) </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-1009">an equal sign (=)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-1010">零至兩個空白字元</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-1010">zero to two whitespace characters</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-1011">介於43-53 個字元、小寫字母、數位或百分號 (% ) 之間的任何組合</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-1011">any combination of between 43-53 characters that are lower- or uppercase letters, digits, or the percent sign (%)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-1012">字串 "% 三維"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-1012">the string "%3d"</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-1013">不是小寫或大寫字母、數位或百分號的任何字元 (% ) </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-1013">any character that isn't a lower- or uppercase letter, digit, or percent sign (%)</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-1014">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-1014">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-1015">否</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-1015">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-1016">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-1016">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-1017">當鄰近性300個字元以內時，DLP 原則就會偵測到這種敏感資訊類型：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-1017">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-1018">正則運算式 CEP_Regex_AzureSAS 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-1018">The regular expression CEP_Regex_AzureSAS finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
<!--Azure SAS-->
<Entity id="4d235014-e564-47f4-a6fb-6ebb4a826834" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
        <IdMatch idRef="CEP_Regex_AzureSAS" />
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="azure-service-bus-connection-string"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-1019">Azure 服務匯流排連接字串</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-1019">Azure service bus connection string</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-1020">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-1020">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-1021">字串 "EndPoint" 後接下列模式中所述的字元及字串，包含字串 "</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-1021">The string "EndPoint" followed by the characters and strings outlined in the pattern below, including the strings "servicebus.windows.</span></span><!--no-hyperlink--><span data-ttu-id="94f34-1022">net "和" SharedAccesKey "。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-1022">net" and "SharedAccesKey".</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-1023">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-1023">Pattern</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-1024">字串 "EndPoint"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-1024">the string "EndPoint"</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-1025">零至兩個空白字元</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-1025">zero to two whitespace characters</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-1026">等號 (=) </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-1026">an equal sign (=)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-1027">零至兩個空白字元</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-1027">zero to two whitespace characters</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-1028">介於1-200 小寫或大寫字母、數位、符號、特殊字元或空格之間的任何組合</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-1028">any combination of between 1-200 lower- or uppercase letters, digits, symbols, special characters, or spaces</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-1029">字串 "</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-1029">the string "servicebus.windows.</span></span><!--no-hyperlink--><span data-ttu-id="94f34-1030">真實</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-1030">net"</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-1031">介於1-200 小寫或大寫字母、數位、符號、特殊字元或空格之間的任何組合</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-1031">any combination of between 1-200 lower- or uppercase letters, digits, symbols, special characters, or spaces</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-1032">字串 "SharedAccessKey"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-1032">the string "SharedAccessKey"</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-1033">零至兩個空白字元</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-1033">zero to two whitespace characters</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-1034">等號 (=) </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-1034">an equal sign (=)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-1035">零至兩個空白字元</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-1035">zero to two whitespace characters</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-1036">43個字元的任何組合，其為小寫或大寫字母、數位、正斜線 (/) 或加號 (+) </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-1036">any combination of 43 characters that are lower- or uppercase letters, digits, forward slash (/), or plus sign (+)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-1037">等號 (=) </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-1037">an equal sign (=)</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-1038">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-1038">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-1039">否</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-1039">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-1040">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-1040">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-1041">如果接近300個字元以內，則 DLP 原則偵測到此敏感資訊類型的置信量是85%：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-1041">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-1042">正則運算式 CEP_Regex_AzureServiceBusConnectionString 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-1042">The regular expression CEP_Regex_AzureServiceBusConnectionString finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-1043">正則運算式 CEP_CommonExampleKeywords 找不到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-1043">The regular expression CEP_CommonExampleKeywords doesn't find content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
<!--Azure Service Bus Connection String-->
<Entity id="b9a6578f-a83f-4fcd-bf44-2130bae49a6f" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
        <IdMatch idRef="CEP_Regex_AzureServiceBusConnectionString" />
        <Any minMatches="0" maxMatches="0">
            <Match idRef="CEP_CommonExampleKeywords" />
        </Any>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="azure-storage-account-key"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-1058">Azure 儲存體帳戶金鑰</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-1058">Azure storage account key</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-1059">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-1059">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-1060">字串 "DefaultEndpointsProtocol"，後面加上下列模式中所述的字元及字串（包括字串 "AccountKey"）。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-1060">The string "DefaultEndpointsProtocol" followed by the characters and strings outlined in the pattern below, including the string "AccountKey".</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-1061">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-1061">Pattern</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-1062">字串 "DefaultEndpointsProtocol"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-1062">the string "DefaultEndpointsProtocol"</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-1063">零至兩個空白字元</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-1063">zero to two whitespace characters</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-1064">等號 (=) </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-1064">an equal sign (=)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-1065">零至兩個空白字元</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-1065">zero to two whitespace characters</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-1066">介於1-200 小寫或大寫字母、數位、符號、特殊字元或空格之間的任何組合</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-1066">any combination of between 1-200 lower- or uppercase letters, digits, symbols, special characters, or spaces</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-1067">字串 "AccountKey"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-1067">the string "AccountKey"</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-1068">零至兩個空白字元</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-1068">zero to two whitespace characters</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-1069">等號 (=) </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-1069">an equal sign (=)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-1070">零至兩個空白字元</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-1070">zero to two whitespace characters</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-1071">86個字元的任何組合，其為小寫或大寫字母、數位、正斜線 (/) 或加號 (+) </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-1071">any combination of 86 characters that are lower- or uppercase letters, digits, forward slash (/), or plus sign (+)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-1072">兩個等號 (=) </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-1072">two equal signs (=)</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-1073">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-1073">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-1074">否</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-1074">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-1075">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-1075">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-1076">當鄰近性300個字元以內時，DLP 原則就會偵測到這種敏感資訊類型：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-1076">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-1077">正則運算式 CEP_Regex_AzureStorageAccountKey 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-1077">The regular expression CEP_Regex_AzureStorageAccountKey finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-1078">正則運算式 CEP_AzureEmulatorStorageAccountFilter 找不到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-1078">The regular expression CEP_AzureEmulatorStorageAccountFilter doesn't find content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-1079">正則運算式 CEP_CommonExampleKeywords 找不到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-1079">The regular expression CEP_CommonExampleKeywords doesn't find content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
<!--Azure Storage Account Key-->
<Entity id="c7bc98e8-551a-4c35-a92d-d2c8cda714a7" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
        <IdMatch idRef="CEP_Regex_AzureStorageAccountKey" />
        <Any minMatches="0" maxMatches="0">
            <Match idRef="CEP_AzureEmulatorStorageAccountFilter" />
            <Match idRef="CEP_CommonExampleKeywords" />
        </Any>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-1085"> (技術上而言，這個敏感資訊類型是使用正則運算式來識別這些關鍵字，而不是關鍵字清單。 ) </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-1085">(Technically, this sensitive information type identifies these keywords by using a regular expression, not a keyword list.)</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-1086">尚未</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-1086">contoso</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-1088">資料庫</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-1088">northwind</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-1095">s-int。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-1095">s-int.</span></span><!--no-hyperlink--><span data-ttu-id="94f34-1096">網</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-1096">net</span></span>

## <a name="azure-storage-account-key-generic"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-1097">Azure 儲存體帳戶金鑰 (泛型) </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-1097">Azure Storage account key (generic)</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-1098">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-1098">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-1099">任何86的小寫字母或大寫字母、數位、正 )  (斜線 (+) 的任何組合，前面或後面接著所列模式中所述的字元。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-1099">Any combination of 86 lower- or uppercase letters, digits, the forward slash (/), or plus sign (+), preceded or followed by the characters outlined in the pattern below.</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-1100">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-1100">Pattern</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-1101">0到大於符號 (>) 、撇號 ( ' ) 、等號 (=) 、引號 ( ") 或數位簽章 ( # ) </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-1101">zero to one of the greater than symbol (>), apostrophe ('), equal sign (=), quotation mark ("), or number sign (#)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-1102">86個字元的任何組合，其小寫或大寫字母、數位、正斜線 (/) 或加號 (+) </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-1102">any combination of 86 characters that are lower- or uppercase letters, digits, the forward slash (/), or plus sign (+)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-1103">兩個等號 (=) </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-1103">two equal signs (=)</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-1104">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-1104">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-1105">否</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-1105">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-1106">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-1106">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-1107">當鄰近性300個字元以內時，DLP 原則就會偵測到這種敏感資訊類型：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-1107">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-1108">正則運算式 CEP_Regex_AzureStorageAccountKeyGeneric 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-1108">The regular expression CEP_Regex_AzureStorageAccountKeyGeneric finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
<!--Azure Storage Account Key (Generic)-->
<Entity id="7ff41bd0-5419-4523-91d6-383b3a37f084" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
        <IdMatch idRef="CEP_Regex_AzureStorageAccountKeyGeneric" />
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```
## <a name="belgium-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-1109">比利時駕駛執照號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-1109">Belgium driver's license number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-1110">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-1110">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-1111">10位數，不含空格及分隔符號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-1111">10 digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-1112">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-1112">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-1113">10位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-1113">10 digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-1114">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-1114">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-1115">否</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-1115">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-1116">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-1116">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-1117">當鄰近性300個字元以內時，DLP 原則就會偵測到這種敏感資訊類型的信賴度。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-1117">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-1118">正則運算式會  `Regex_belgium_eu_driver's_license_number` 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-1118">The regular expression  `Regex_belgium_eu_driver's_license_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-1119">`Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number`找到或的關鍵字 `Keywords_belgium_eu_driver's_license_number` 。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-1119">A keyword from `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` or `Keywords_belgium_eu_driver's_license_number` is found.</span></span>
    
```xml
      <!-- Belgium Driver's License Number -->
      <Entity id="d89fd329-9324-433c-b687-2c37bd5166f3" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_belgium_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_belgium_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="belgium-national-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-1252">比利時國號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-1252">Belgium national number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-1253">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-1253">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-1254">11位數加上選擇性分隔符號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-1254">11 digits plus optional delimiters</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-1255">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-1255">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-1256">11位數加上分隔符號：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-1256">11 digits plus delimiters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-1257">六位數和兩個選用句點，格式為 YY。MM.DD 出生日期</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-1257">six digits and two optional periods in the format YY.MM.DD for date of birth</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-1258">自點、破折號、空間的選擇性分隔符號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-1258">An optional delimiter from dot, dash, space</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-1259">三個連續數位 (奇數男生，即便是女生) </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-1259">three sequential digits (odd for males, even for females)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-1260">自點、破折號、空間的選擇性分隔符號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-1260">An optional delimiter from dot, dash, space</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-1261">兩個檢查碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-1261">two check digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-1262">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-1262">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-1263">是</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-1263">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-1264">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-1264">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-1265">當鄰近性300個字元以內時，DLP 原則就會偵測到這種敏感資訊類型的信賴度。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-1265">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-1266">函數 Func_belgium_national_number 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-1266">The function Func_belgium_national_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-1267">會找到來自 Keyword_belgium_national_number 的關鍵字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-1267">A keyword from Keyword_belgium_national_number is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-1268">校驗和通過。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-1268">The checksum passes.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-1269">DLP 原則在接近300個字元以內時，偵測到此敏感資訊類型的信賴度很低：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-1269">A DLP policy has low confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-1270">函數 Func_belgium_national_number 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-1270">The function Func_belgium_national_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-1271">校驗和通過。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-1271">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Belgium National Number -->
       <Entity id="fb969c9e-0fd1-4b18-8091-a2123c5e6a54" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_belgium_national_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_belgium_national_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_belgium_national_number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="belgium-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-1330">比利時護照號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-1330">Belgium passport number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-1331">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-1331">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-1332">兩個字母后接六位數，不含空格或分隔符號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-1332">two letters followed by six digits with no spaces or delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-1333">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-1333">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-1334">兩個字母后接六位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-1334">two letters and followed by six digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-1335">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-1335">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-1336">不適用</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-1336">not applicable</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-1337">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-1337">Definition</span></span>

 <span data-ttu-id="94f34-1338">當鄰近性300個字元以內時，DLP 原則就會偵測到這種敏感資訊類型：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-1338">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-1339">正則運算式會  `Regex_belgium_eu_passport_number` 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-1339">The regular expression  `Regex_belgium_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-1340">`Keywords_eu_passport_number`找到或的關鍵字 `Keywords_belgium_eu_passport_number` 。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-1340">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_belgium_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-1341">正則運算式 `Regex_eu_passport_date2` 會找到格式為 DD MM YY 的日期，或 `Keywords_eu_passport_date` 找到來自或的關鍵字。 `Keywords_belgium_eu_passport_number`</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-1341">The regular expression `Regex_eu_passport_date2` finds date in the format DD MM YY or a keyword from `Keywords_eu_passport_date` or `Keywords_belgium_eu_passport_number` is found</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-1342">當鄰近性300個字元以內時，DLP 原則就會偵測到這種敏感資訊類型的信賴度。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-1342">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-1343">正則運算式會  `Regex_belgium_eu_passport_number` 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-1343">The regular expression  `Regex_belgium_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-1344">`Keywords_eu_passport_number`找到或的關鍵字 `Keywords_belgium_eu_passport_number` 。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-1344">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_belgium_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 

```xml
      <!-- Belgium Passport Number -->
      <Entity id="d7b1315b-21ca-4774-a32a-596010ff78fd" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_belgium_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_belgium_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Regex_eu_passport_date2" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_date" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_belgium_eu_passport_date" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_belgium_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_belgium_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>

```

## <a name="belgium-value-added-tax-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-1371">比利時增值的納稅號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-1371">Belgium value added tax number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="94f34-1372">此機密資訊類型僅可用於下列專案：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-1372">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-1373">資料遺失防護原則</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-1373">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-1374">通訊相容性原則</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-1374">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-1375">資訊管理</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-1375">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-1376">記錄管理</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-1376">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-1377">Microsoft cloud app security</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-1377">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-1378">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-1378">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-1379">12個字元的數位元格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-1379">12-character alphanumeric pattern</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-1380">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-1380">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-1381">12個字元的字母數位樣式：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-1381">12-character alphanumeric pattern:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-1382">a 字母 B 或 B</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-1382">a letter B or b</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-1383">字母 E 或 E</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-1383">a letter E or e</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-1384">數位0</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-1384">a digit 0</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-1385">從1到9的數位</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-1385">a digit from 1 to 9</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-1386">選用的點或連字號或空格</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-1386">an optional dot or Hyphen or space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-1387">四位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-1387">four digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-1388">選用的點或連字號或空格</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-1388">an optional dot or Hyphen or space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-1389">四位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-1389">four digits</span></span>


### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-1390">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-1390">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-1391">是</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-1391">Yes</span></span>


### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-1392">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-1392">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-1393">當鄰近性300個字元以內時，DLP 原則就會偵測到這種敏感資訊類型：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-1393">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-1394">函數 Func_belgium_value_added_tax_number 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-1394">The function Func_belgium_value_added_tax_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-1395">會找到來自 Keywords_belgium_value_added_tax_number 的關鍵字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-1395">A keyword from Keywords_belgium_value_added_tax_number is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-1396">當鄰近性300個字元以內時，DLP 原則就會偵測到這種敏感資訊類型的信賴度。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-1396">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-1397">函數 Func_belgium_value_added_tax_number 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-1397">The function Func_belgium_value_added_tax_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Belgium Value Added Tax Number -->
      <Entity id="85b5b3c3-f2de-4ae8-ac46-fd3cb38bf9ed" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_belgium_value_added_tax_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_belgium_value_added_tax_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_belgium_value_added_tax_number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
    </Version>
```

## <a name="brazil-cpf-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-1409">巴西 CPF 號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-1409">Brazil CPF number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-1410">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-1410">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-1411">11位數包含檢查碼，可格式化或未格式化</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-1411">11 digits that include a check digit and can be formatted or unformatted</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-1412">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-1412">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-1413">格式 化：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-1413">Formatted:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-1414">三位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-1414">three digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-1415">一個句點</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-1415">a period</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-1416">三位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-1416">three digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-1417">一個句點</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-1417">a period</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-1418">三位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-1418">three digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-1419">連字號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-1419">a hyphen</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-1420">兩位數的檢查碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-1420">two digits that are check digits</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-1421">非</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-1421">Unformatted:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-1422">11位數的最後兩位數的檢查碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-1422">11 digits where the last two digits are check digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-1423">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-1423">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-1424">是</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-1424">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-1425">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-1425">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-1426">當鄰近性300個字元以內時，DLP 原則就會偵測到這種敏感資訊類型：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-1426">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-1427">函數 Func_brazil_cpf 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-1427">The function Func_brazil_cpf finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-1428">會找到來自 Keyword_brazil_cpf 的關鍵字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-1428">A keyword from Keyword_brazil_cpf is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-1429">校驗和通過。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-1429">The checksum passes.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-1430">當鄰近性300個字元以內時，DLP 原則就會偵測到這種敏感資訊類型的信賴度。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-1430">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-1431">函數 Func_brazil_cpf 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-1431">The function Func_brazil_cpf finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-1432">校驗和通過。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-1432">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Brazil CPF Number -->
<Entity id="78e09124-f2c3-4656-b32a-c1a132cd2711" recommendedConfidence="85" patternsProximity="300">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
     <IdMatch idRef="Func_brazil_cpf"/>
     <Match idRef="Keyword_brazil_cpf"/>
  </Pattern>
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
     <IdMatch idRef="Func_brazil_cpf"/>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="brazil-legal-entity-number-cnpj"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-1444">巴西法人編號 (CNPJ) </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-1444">Brazil legal entity number (CNPJ)</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-1445">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-1445">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-1446">14位數包含登記編號、分支編號及檢查數位，加上分隔符號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-1446">14 digits that include a registration number, branch number, and check digits, plus delimiters</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-1447">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-1447">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-1448">14位數，加上分隔符號：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-1448">14 digits, plus delimiters:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-1449">兩位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-1449">two digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-1450">一個句點</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-1450">a period</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-1451">三位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-1451">three digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-1452">一個句點</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-1452">a period</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-1453">三位數 (這些前八位數是登記編號) </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-1453">three digits (these first eight digits are the registration number)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-1454">一個正斜線</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-1454">a forward slash</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-1455">四位數的分支編號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-1455">four-digit branch number</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-1456">連字號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-1456">a hyphen</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-1457">兩位數的檢查碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-1457">two digits that are check digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-1458">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-1458">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-1459">是</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-1459">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-1460">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-1460">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-1461">當鄰近性300個字元以內時，DLP 原則就會偵測到這種敏感資訊類型：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-1461">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-1462">函數 Func_brazil_cnpj 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-1462">The function Func_brazil_cnpj finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-1463">會找到來自 Keyword_brazil_cnpj 的關鍵字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-1463">A keyword from Keyword_brazil_cnpj is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-1464">校驗和通過。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-1464">The checksum passes.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-1465">當鄰近性300個字元以內時，DLP 原則就會偵測到這種敏感資訊類型的信賴度。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-1465">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-1466">函數 Func_brazil_cnpj 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-1466">The function Func_brazil_cnpj finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-1467">校驗和通過。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-1467">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Brazil Legal Entity Number (CNPJ) -->
<Entity id="9b58b5cd-5e90-4df6-b34f-1ebcc88ceae4" recommendedConfidence="85" patternsProximity="300">
   <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
     <IdMatch idRef="Func_brazil_cnpj"/>
     <Match idRef="Keyword_brazil_cnpj"/>
  </Pattern>
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
     <IdMatch idRef="Func_brazil_cnpj"/>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="brazil-national-identification-card-rg"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-1489">巴西國身分識別卡 (RG) </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-1489">Brazil national identification card (RG)</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-1490">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-1490">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-1491">Registro Geral (舊格式) ：九位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-1491">Registro Geral (old format): Nine digits</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-1492">Registro de Identidade (RIC)  (新格式) ：11位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-1492">Registro de Identidade (RIC) (new format): 11 digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-1493">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-1493">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-1494">Registro Geral (舊格式) ：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-1494">Registro Geral (old format):</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-1495">兩位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-1495">two digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-1496">一個句點</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-1496">a period</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-1497">三位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-1497">three digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-1498">一個句點</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-1498">a period</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-1499">三位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-1499">three digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-1500">連字號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-1500">a hyphen</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-1501">一種檢查碼的數位</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-1501">one digit that is a check digit</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-1502">Registro de Identidade (RIC)  (新格式) ：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-1502">Registro de Identidade (RIC) (new format):</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-1503">10位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-1503">10 digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-1504">連字號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-1504">a hyphen</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-1505">一種檢查碼的數位</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-1505">one digit that is a check digit</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-1506">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-1506">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-1507">是</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-1507">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-1508">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-1508">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-1509">當鄰近性300個字元以內時，DLP 原則就會偵測到這種敏感資訊類型：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-1509">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-1510">函數 Func_brazil_rg 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-1510">The function Func_brazil_rg finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-1511">會找到來自 Keyword_brazil_rg 的關鍵字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-1511">A keyword from Keyword_brazil_rg is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-1512">校驗和通過。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-1512">The checksum passes.</span></span>


```xml
      <!-- Brazil National ID Card (RG) -->
      <Entity id="486de900-db70-41b3-a886-abdf25af119c" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_brazil_rg" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_brazil_rg" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="bulgaria-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-1523">保加利亞駕駛執照號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-1523">Bulgaria driver's license number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-1524">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-1524">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-1525">九位數，不含空格及分隔符號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-1525">nine digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-1526">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-1526">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-1527">九位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-1527">nine digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-1528">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-1528">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-1529">否</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-1529">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-1530">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-1530">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-1531">當鄰近性300個字元以內時，DLP 原則就會偵測到這種敏感資訊類型的信賴度。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-1531">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-1532">正則運算式會  `Regex_bulgaria_eu_driver's_license_number` 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-1532">The regular expression  `Regex_bulgaria_eu_driver's_license_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-1533">`Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number`找到或的關鍵字 `Keywords_bulgaria_eu_driver's_license_number` 。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-1533">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` or `Keywords_bulgaria_eu_driver's_license_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Bulgaria Driver's License Number -->
      <Entity id="66d39258-94c2-43b2-804b-aa312258e54b" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_bulgaria_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_bulgaria_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>    
```

## <a name="bulgaria-uniform-civil-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-1660">保加利亞統一的民事編號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-1660">Bulgaria uniform civil number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="94f34-1661">此機密資訊類型僅可用於下列專案：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-1661">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-1662">資料遺失防護原則</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-1662">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-1663">通訊相容性原則</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-1663">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-1664">資訊管理</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-1664">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-1665">記錄管理</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-1665">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-1666">Microsoft cloud app security</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-1666">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-1667">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-1667">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-1668">10位數，不含空格及分隔符號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-1668">10 digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-1669">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-1669">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-1670">10位數，不含空格及分隔符號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-1670">10 digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-1671">對應至出生日期 (YYMMDD 的六位數) </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-1671">six digits that correspond to the birth date (YYMMDD)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-1672">對應至出生順序的兩位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-1672">two digits that correspond to the birth order</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-1673">對應于性別的一個數位：用於男的偶數位數和用於女的奇數數位</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-1673">one digit that corresponds to gender: An even digit for male and an odd digit for female</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-1674">一個檢查碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-1674">one check digit</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-1675">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-1675">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-1676">是</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-1676">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-1677">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-1677">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-1678">當鄰近性300個字元以內時，DLP 原則就會偵測到這種敏感資訊類型：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-1678">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-1679">函數  `Func_bulgaria_eu_national_id_card` 會找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-1679">The function  `Func_bulgaria_eu_national_id_card` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-1680">找到來自的關鍵字  `Keywords_bulgaria_eu_national_id_card` 。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-1680">A keyword from  `Keywords_bulgaria_eu_national_id_card` is found.</span></span> 

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-1681">當鄰近性300個字元以內時，DLP 原則就會偵測到這種敏感資訊類型的信賴度。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-1681">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-1682">函數  `Func_bulgaria_eu_national_id_card` 會找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-1682">The function  `Func_bulgaria_eu_national_id_card` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Bulgaria Uniform Civil Number -->
      <Entity id="100d58b1-0a35-4fb1-aa89-e4a86fb53fcc" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_bulgaria_eu_national_id_card" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_bulgaria_eu_national_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_bulgaria_eu_national_id_card" />
          <Any minMatches="0" maxMatches="0">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_bulgaria_eu_telephone_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_bulgaria_eu_mobile_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

#### <a name="keywords_bulgaria_eu_national_id_card"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-1684">Keywords_bulgaria_eu_national_id_card</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-1684">Keywords_bulgaria_eu_national_id_card</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-1685">安娜#</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-1685">bnn#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-1686">安娜</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-1686">bnn</span></span>

## <a name="bulgaria-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-1727">保加利亞護照號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-1727">Bulgaria passport number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-1728">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-1728">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-1729">九位數，不含空格及分隔符號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-1729">nine digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-1730">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-1730">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-1731">九位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-1731">nine digits</span></span> 
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-1732">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-1732">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-1733">否</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-1733">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-1734">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-1734">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-1735">當鄰近性300個字元以內時，DLP 原則就會偵測到這種敏感資訊類型：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-1735">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-1736">正則運算式會  `Regex_bulgaria_eu_passport_number` 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-1736">The regular expression  `Regex_bulgaria_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-1737">`Keywords_eu_passport_number`找到或的關鍵字 `Keywords_bulgaria_eu_passport_number` 。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-1737">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_bulgaria_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-1738">正則運算式 `Regex_eu_passport_date1` 會發現日期格式為 DD YYYY 或關鍵字 from `Keywords_eu_passport_date`</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-1738">The regular expression `Regex_eu_passport_date1` finds date in the format DD.MM.YYYY or a keyword from `Keywords_eu_passport_date` is found</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-1739">當鄰近性300個字元以內時，DLP 原則就會偵測到這種敏感資訊類型的信賴度。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-1739">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-1740">正則運算式會  `Regex_bulgaria_eu_passport_number` 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-1740">The regular expression  `Regex_bulgaria_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-1741">`Keywords_eu_passport_number`找到或的關鍵字 `Keywords_bulgaria_eu_passport_number` 。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-1741">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_bulgaria_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 

```xml
      <!-- Bulgaria Passport Number -->
      <Entity id="f7172b82-c588-4216-845e-4e54e397f29a" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_bulgaria_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_bulgaria_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Regex_eu_passport_date1" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_date" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_bulgaria_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_bulgaria_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="canada-bank-account-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-1761">加拿大銀行帳戶號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-1761">Canada bank account number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-1762">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-1762">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-1763">7或12位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-1763">7 or 12 digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-1764">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-1764">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-1765">加拿大銀行帳戶號碼是7或12位數。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-1765">A Canada Bank Account Number is 7 or 12 digits.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-1766">加拿大銀行帳戶中轉號碼為：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-1766">A Canada bank account transit number is:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-1767">五位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-1767">five digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-1768">連字號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-1768">a hyphen</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-1769">三位數或</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-1769">three digits OR</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-1770">零 "0"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-1770">a zero "0"</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-1771">八位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-1771">eight digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-1772">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-1772">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-1773">否</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-1773">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-1774">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-1774">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-1775">當鄰近性300個字元以內時，DLP 原則就會偵測到這種敏感資訊類型：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-1775">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-1776">正則運算式 Regex_canada_bank_account_number 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-1776">The regular expression Regex_canada_bank_account_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-1777">會找到來自 Keyword_canada_bank_account_number 的關鍵字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-1777">A keyword from Keyword_canada_bank_account_number is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-1778">正則運算式 Regex_canada_bank_account_transit_number 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-1778">The regular expression Regex_canada_bank_account_transit_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-1779">當鄰近性300個字元以內時，DLP 原則就會偵測到這種敏感資訊類型：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-1779">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-1780">正則運算式 Regex_canada_bank_account_number 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-1780">The regular expression Regex_canada_bank_account_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-1781">會找到來自 Keyword_canada_bank_account_number 的關鍵字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-1781">A keyword from Keyword_canada_bank_account_number is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Canada Bank Account Number -->
<Entity id="552e814c-cb50-4d94-bbaa-bb1d1ffb34de" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
        <IdMatch idRef="Regex_canada_bank_account_number" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_canada_bank_account_number" />
        <Match idRef="Regex_canada_bank_account_transit_number" />
   </Pattern>
   <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Regex_canada_bank_account_number" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_canada_bank_account_number" />
   </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-1792">兒童護理權益</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-1792">child care benefit</span></span>

## <a name="canada-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-1805">加拿大駕駛執照號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-1805">Canada driver's license number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-1806">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-1806">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-1807">依省份</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-1807">Varies by province</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-1808">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-1808">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-1809">涵蓋 Alberta、英屬哥倫比亞、Manitoba、新的 Brunswick、Newfoundland/Labrador、Nova Scotia、安大略、Prince Edward 孤島、魁北克和薩斯的各種模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-1809">Various patterns covering Alberta, British Columbia, Manitoba, New Brunswick, Newfoundland/Labrador, Nova Scotia, Ontario, Prince Edward Island, Quebec, and Saskatchewan</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-1810">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-1810">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-1811">否</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-1811">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-1812">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-1812">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-1813">當鄰近性300個字元以內時，DLP 原則就會偵測到這種敏感資訊類型的信賴度。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-1813">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-1814">函數 Func_ [province_name] _drivers_license_number 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-1814">The function Func_[province_name]_drivers_license_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-1815">找到來自 Keyword_ [province_name] _drivers_license_name 的關鍵字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-1815">A keyword from Keyword_[province_name]_drivers_license_name is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-1816">會找到來自 Keyword_canada_drivers_license 的關鍵字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-1816">A keyword from Keyword_canada_drivers_license is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Canada Driver's License Number -->
    <Entity id="37186abb-8e48-4800-ad3c-e3d1610b3db0" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_alberta_drivers_license_number" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_alberta_drivers_license_name" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_canada_drivers_license" />
      </Pattern>
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_british_columbia_drivers_license_number" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_british_columbia_drivers_license_name" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_canada_drivers_license" />
      </Pattern>
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_manitoba_drivers_license_number" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_manitoba_drivers_license_name" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_canada_drivers_license" />
      </Pattern>
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_new_brunswick_drivers_license_number" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_new_brunswick_drivers_license_name" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_canada_drivers_license" />
      </Pattern>
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_newfoundland_labrador_drivers_license_number" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_newfoundland_labrador_drivers_license_name" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_canada_drivers_license" />
      </Pattern>
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_nova_scotia_drivers_license_number" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_nova_scotia_drivers_license_name" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_canada_drivers_license" />
      </Pattern>
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_ontario_drivers_license_number" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_ontario_drivers_license_name" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_canada_drivers_license" />
      </Pattern>
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_prince_edward_island_drivers_license_number" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_prince_edward_island_drivers_license_name" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_canada_drivers_license" />
      </Pattern>
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_quebec_drivers_license_number" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_quebec_drivers_license_name" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_canada_drivers_license" />
      </Pattern>
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_saskatchewan_drivers_license_number" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_saskatchewan_drivers_license_name" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_canada_drivers_license" />
      </Pattern>
    </Entity>
```
