## <a name="canada-health-service-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-1952">加拿大健康情況服務號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-1952">Canada health service number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-1953">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-1953">Format</span></span>

 <span data-ttu-id="94f34-1954">10位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-1954">10 digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-1955">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-1955">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-1956">10位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-1956">10 digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-1957">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-1957">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-1958">否</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-1958">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-1959">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-1959">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-1960">當鄰近性300個字元以內時，DLP 原則就會偵測到這種敏感資訊類型的信賴度。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-1960">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-1961">正則運算式 Regex_canada_health_service_number 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-1961">The regular expression Regex_canada_health_service_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-1962">會找到來自 Keyword_canada_health_service_number 的關鍵字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-1962">A keyword from Keyword_canada_health_service_number is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Canada Health Service Number -->
<Entity id="59c0bf39-7fab-482c-af25-00faa4384c94" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Regex_canada_health_service_number" />
        <Any minMatches="1">
          <Match idRef="Keyword_canada_health_service_number" />
        </Any>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-1963">關鍵字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-1963">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_canada_health_service_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-1964">Keyword_canada_health_service_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-1964">Keyword_canada_health_service_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-1965">個人健康號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-1965">personal health number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-1966">患者資訊</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-1966">patient information</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-1967">健康情況服務</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-1967">health services</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-1968">speciality 服務</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-1968">speciality services</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-1969">汽車意外</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-1969">automobile accident</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-1970">病人醫院</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-1970">patient hospital</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-1971">心理醫生</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-1971">psychiatrist</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-1972">工作人員薪酬</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-1972">workers compensation</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-1973">殘疾</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-1973">disability</span></span>

      
## <a name="canada-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-1974">加拿大護照號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-1974">Canada passport number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-1975">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-1975">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-1976">兩個大寫字母後接六位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-1976">two uppercase letters followed by six digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-1977">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-1977">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-1978">兩個大寫字母後接六位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-1978">two uppercase letters followed by six digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-1979">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-1979">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-1980">否</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-1980">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-1981">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-1981">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-1982">當鄰近性300個字元以內時，DLP 原則就會偵測到這種敏感資訊類型的信賴度。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-1982">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-1983">正則運算式 Regex_canada_passport_number 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-1983">The regular expression Regex_canada_passport_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-1984">會找到 Keyword_canada_passport_number 或 Keyword_passport 中的關鍵字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-1984">A keyword from Keyword_canada_passport_number or Keyword_passport is found.</span></span>

```xml 
<!-- Canada Passport Number -->
<Entity id="14d0db8b-498a-43ed-9fca-f6097ae687eb" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Regex_canada_passport_number" />
        <Any minMatches="1">
          <Match idRef="Keyword_canada_passport_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_passport" />
        </Any>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="canada-personal-health-identification-number-phin"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-2014">加拿大個人健康身分識別號碼 (PHIN) </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-2014">Canada personal health identification number (PHIN)</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-2015">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-2015">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-2016">九位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-2016">nine digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-2017">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-2017">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-2018">九位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-2018">nine digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-2019">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-2019">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-2020">否</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-2020">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-2021">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-2021">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-2022">當鄰近性300個字元以內時，DLP 原則就會偵測到這種敏感資訊類型的信賴度。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-2022">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-2023">正則運算式 Regex_canada_phin 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-2023">The regular expression Regex_canada_phin finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-2024">找到 Keyword_canada_phin 或 Keyword_canada_provinces 中至少有兩個關鍵字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-2024">At least two keywords from Keyword_canada_phin or Keyword_canada_provinces are found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Canada PHIN -->
<Entity id="722e12ac-c89a-4ec8-a1b7-fea3469f89db" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Regex_canada_phin" />
        <Any minMatches="2">
          <Match idRef="Keyword_canada_phin" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_canada_provinces" />
        </Any>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="canada-social-insurance-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-2057">加拿大社交保險號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-2057">Canada social insurance number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-2058">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-2058">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-2059">具有選擇性連字號或空格的九位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-2059">nine digits with optional hyphens or spaces</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-2060">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-2060">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-2061">格式 化：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-2061">Formatted:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-2062">三位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-2062">three digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-2063">連字號或空格</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-2063">a hyphen or space</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-2064">三位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-2064">three digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-2065">連字號或空格</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-2065">a hyphen or space</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-2066">三位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-2066">three digits</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-2067">未格式化：九位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-2067">Unformatted: nine digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-2068">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-2068">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-2069">是</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-2069">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-2070">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-2070">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-2071">當鄰近性300個字元以內時，DLP 原則就會偵測到這種敏感資訊類型：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-2071">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-2072">函數 Func_canadian_sin 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-2072">The function Func_canadian_sin finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-2073">下列其中一種組合，至少有兩種：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-2073">At least two of any combination of the following:</span></span>
    - <span data-ttu-id="94f34-2074">會找到來自 Keyword_sin 的關鍵字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-2074">A keyword from Keyword_sin is found.</span></span>
    - <span data-ttu-id="94f34-2075">會找到來自 Keyword_sin_collaborative 的關鍵字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-2075">A keyword from Keyword_sin_collaborative is found.</span></span>
    - <span data-ttu-id="94f34-2076">函數 Func_eu_date 會找到正確日期格式的日期。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-2076">The function Func_eu_date finds a date in the right date format.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-2077">校驗和通過。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-2077">The checksum passes.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-2078">當鄰近性300個字元以內時，DLP 原則就會偵測到這種敏感資訊類型的信賴度。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-2078">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-2079">函數 Func_unformatted_canadian_sin 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-2079">The function Func_unformatted_canadian_sin finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-2080">會找到來自 Keyword_sin 的關鍵字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-2080">A keyword from Keyword_sin is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-2081">校驗和通過。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-2081">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Canada Social Insurance Number -->
<Entity id="a2f29c85-ecb8-4514-a610-364790c0773e" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_canadian_sin" />
        <Any minMatches="2">
          <Match idRef="Keyword_sin" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_sin_collaborative" />
          <Match idRef="Func_eu_date" />
        </Any>
  </Pattern>
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_unformatted_canadian_sin" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_sin" />
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="chile-identity-card-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-2106">智利身分識別卡號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-2106">Chile identity card number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-2107">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-2107">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-2108">七到八位數加上分隔符號 a check digits 或字母</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-2108">seven to eight digits plus delimiters a check digit or letter</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-2109">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-2109">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-2110">7到8位數加上分隔符號：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-2110">seven to eight digits plus delimiters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-2111">一到兩位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-2111">one to two digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-2112">選用期間</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-2112">an optional period</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-2113">三位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-2113">three digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-2114">選用期間</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-2114">an optional period</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-2115">三位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-2115">three digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-2116">虛線</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-2116">a dash</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-2117">一個數位或字母 (不區分大小寫) （該碼是檢查碼）</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-2117">one digit or letter (not case-sensitive) which is a check digit</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-2118">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-2118">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-2119">是</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-2119">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-2120">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-2120">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-2121">當鄰近性300個字元以內時，DLP 原則就會偵測到這種敏感資訊類型：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-2121">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-2122">函數 Func_chile_id_card 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-2122">The function Func_chile_id_card finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-2123">會找到來自 Keyword_chile_id_card 的關鍵字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-2123">A keyword from Keyword_chile_id_card is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-2124">校驗和通過。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-2124">The checksum passes.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-2125">當鄰近性300個字元以內時，DLP 原則就會偵測到這種敏感資訊類型的信賴度。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-2125">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-2126">函數 Func_chile_id_card 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-2126">The function Func_chile_id_card finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-2127">校驗和通過。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-2127">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Chile Identity Card Number -->
<Entity id="4e979794-49a0-407e-a0b9-2c536937b925" recommendedConfidence="85" patternsProximity="300">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
     <IdMatch idRef="Func_chile_id_card"/>
     <Match idRef="Keyword_chile_id_card"/>
  </Pattern>
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
     <IdMatch idRef="Func_chile_id_card"/>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="china-resident-identity-card-prc-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-2164">中國居民身分識別卡 (中國) 號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-2164">China resident identity card (PRC) number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-2165">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-2165">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-2166">18位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-2166">18 digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-2167">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-2167">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-2168">18位數：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-2168">18 digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-2169">六位數的位址碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-2169">six digits that are an address code</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-2170">形式為 YYYYMMDD 的八位數，也就是出生日期</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-2170">eight digits in the form YYYYMMDD, which are the date of birth</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-2171">三位數的訂單碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-2171">three digits that are an order code</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-2172">一種檢查碼的數位</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-2172">one digit that is a check digit</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-2173">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-2173">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-2174">是</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-2174">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-2175">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-2175">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-2176">當鄰近性300個字元以內時，DLP 原則就會偵測到這種敏感資訊類型：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-2176">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-2177">函數 Func_china_resident_id 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-2177">The function Func_china_resident_id finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-2178">會找到來自 Keyword_china_resident_id 的關鍵字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-2178">A keyword from Keyword_china_resident_id is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-2179">校驗和通過。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-2179">The checksum passes.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-2180">當鄰近性300個字元以內時，DLP 原則就會偵測到這種敏感資訊類型的信賴度。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-2180">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-2181">函數 Func_china_resident_id 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-2181">The function Func_china_resident_id finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-2182">校驗和通過。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-2182">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- China Resident Identity Card (PRC) Number -->
<Entity id="c92daa86-2d16-4871-901f-816b3f554fc1" recommendedConfidence="85" patternsProximity="300">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
     <IdMatch idRef="Func_china_resident_id"/>
     <Match idRef="Keyword_china_resident_id"/>
  </Pattern>
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
     <IdMatch idRef="Func_china_resident_id"/>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-2183">關鍵字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-2183">Keywords</span></span>

### <a name="keyword_china_resident_id"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-2184">Keyword_china_resident_id</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-2184">Keyword_china_resident_id</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-2185">常駐身分識別卡</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-2185">Resident Identity Card</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-2186">中國</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-2186">PRC</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-2187">全國身分識別卡</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-2187">National Identification Card</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-2188">身份證</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-2188">身份证</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-2189">居民 身份證</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-2189">居民 身份证</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-2190">居民身份證</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-2190">居民身份证</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-2191">鑒定</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-2191">鉴定</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-2192">身分證</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-2192">身分證</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-2193">居民 身份證</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-2193">居民 身份證</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-2194">鑑定</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-2194">鑑定</span></span> 

   
## <a name="credit-card-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-2195">信用卡號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-2195">Credit card number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-2196">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-2196">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-2197">可以格式化或未格式化的14到16位數 (dddddddddddddddd) ，且必須透過 Luhn 測試。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-2197">14 to 16 digits that can be formatted or unformatted (dddddddddddddddd) and that must pass the Luhn test.</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-2198">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-2198">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-2199">複雜且健全的模式，可偵測全球所有主要品牌的卡，包括簽證、MasterCard、探索卡、JCB、美洲 Express、禮品卡和 diner 卡。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-2199">Complex and robust pattern that detects cards from all major brands worldwide, including Visa, MasterCard, Discover Card, JCB, American Express, gift cards, and diner cards.</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-2200">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-2200">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-2201">是，Luhn 檢查碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-2201">Yes, the Luhn checksum</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-2202">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-2202">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-2203">當鄰近性300個字元以內時，DLP 原則就會偵測到這種敏感資訊類型：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-2203">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-2204">函數 Func_credit_card 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-2204">The function Func_credit_card finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-2205">下列其中一項為真：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-2205">One of the following is true:</span></span>
    - <span data-ttu-id="94f34-2206">會找到來自 Keyword_cc_verification 的關鍵字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-2206">A keyword from Keyword_cc_verification is found.</span></span>
    - <span data-ttu-id="94f34-2207">會找到來自 Keyword_cc_name 的關鍵字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-2207">A keyword from Keyword_cc_name is found.</span></span>
    - <span data-ttu-id="94f34-2208">函數 Func_expiration_date 會找到正確日期格式的日期。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-2208">The function Func_expiration_date finds a date in the right date format.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-2209">校驗和通過。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-2209">The checksum passes.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-2210">DLP 原則在接近300個字元以內時，偵測到此敏感資訊類型的信賴度很低：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-2210">A DLP policy has low confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-2211">函數 Func_credit_card 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-2211">The function Func_credit_card finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-2212">校驗和通過。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-2212">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Credit Card Number -->
<Entity id="50842eb7-edc8-4019-85dd-5a5c1f2bb085" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_credit_card" />
        <Any minMatches="1">
          <Match idRef="Keyword_cc_verification" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_cc_name" />
          <Match idRef="Func_expiration_date" />
        </Any>
  </Pattern>
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_credit_card" />
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="croatia-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-2472">克羅地亞駕駛執照號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-2472">Croatia driver's license number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-2473">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-2473">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-2474">不含空格及分隔符號的八位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-2474">eight digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-2475">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-2475">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-2476">八位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-2476">eight digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-2477">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-2477">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-2478">否</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-2478">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-2479">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-2479">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-2480">當鄰近性300個字元以內時，DLP 原則就會偵測到這種敏感資訊類型的信賴度。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-2480">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-2481">正則運算式會  `Regex_croatia_eu_driver's_license_number` 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-2481">The regular expression  `Regex_croatia_eu_driver's_license_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-2482">`Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number`找到或的關鍵字 `Keywords_croatia_eu_driver's_license_number` 。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-2482">A keyword from `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` or `Keywords_croatia_eu_driver's_license_number` is found.</span></span> 

```xml
      <!-- Croatia Driver's License Number -->
      <Entity id="005b3ef1-47dd-4e68-bb02-c6db484d00f2" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_croatia_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_croatia_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="croatia-identity-card-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-2606">克羅地亞身分識別卡號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-2606">Croatia identity card number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="94f34-2607">這種敏感資訊類型實體包含在歐盟國身分識別號碼的敏感資訊類型中。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-2607">This sensitive information type entity is included in the EU National Identification Number sensitive information type.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="94f34-2608">它可以做為獨立的機密資訊類型實體。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-2608">It's available as a stand-alone sensitive information type entity.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-2609">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-2609">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-2610">九位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-2610">nine digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-2611">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-2611">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-2612">九個連續數位</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-2612">nine consecutive digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-2613">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-2613">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-2614">否</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-2614">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-2615">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-2615">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-2616">當鄰近性300個字元以內時，DLP 原則就會偵測到這種敏感資訊類型的信賴度。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-2616">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-2617">函數 Func_croatia_id_card 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-2617">The function Func_croatia_id_card finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-2618">會找到來自 Keyword_croatia_id_card 的關鍵字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-2618">A keyword from Keyword_croatia_id_card is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!--Croatia Identity Card Number-->
<Entity id="ff12f884-c20a-4189-b185-34c8e7258d47" recommendedConfidence="75" patternsProximity="300">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
     <IdMatch idRef="Func_croatia_id_card"/>
     <Match idRef="Keyword_croatia_id_card"/>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="croatia-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-2649">克羅地亞護照號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-2649">Croatia passport number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-2650">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-2650">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-2651">九位數，不含空格及分隔符號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-2651">nine digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-2652">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-2652">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-2653">九位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-2653">nine digits</span></span> 
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-2654">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-2654">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-2655">否</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-2655">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-2656">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-2656">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-2657">當鄰近性300個字元以內時，DLP 原則就會偵測到這種敏感資訊類型：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-2657">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-2658">正則運算式會  `Regex_croatia_eu_passport_number` 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-2658">The regular expression  `Regex_croatia_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-2659">`Keywords_eu_passport_number`找到或的關鍵字 `Keywords_croatia_eu_passport_number` 。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-2659">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_croatia_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-2660">正則運算式 `Regex_eu_passport_date1` 會發現日期格式為 DD YYYY 或關鍵字 from `Keywords_eu_passport_date`</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-2660">The regular expression `Regex_eu_passport_date1` finds date in the format DD.MM.YYYY or a keyword from `Keywords_eu_passport_date` is found</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-2661">當鄰近性300個字元以內時，DLP 原則就會偵測到這種敏感資訊類型的信賴度。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-2661">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-2662">正則運算式會  `Regex_croatia_eu_passport_number` 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-2662">The regular expression  `Regex_croatia_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-2663">`Keywords_eu_passport_number`找到或的關鍵字 `Keywords_croatia_eu_passport_number` 。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-2663">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_croatia_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Croatia Passport Number -->
      <Entity id="7d7a729d-32d8-4204-8d01-d5e6a6c25581" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_croatia_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_croatia_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Regex_eu_passport_date1" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_date" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_croatia_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_croatia_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```
### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-2664">關鍵字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-2664">Keywords</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-2669">護照</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-2669">passports</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-2670">passportno</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-2670">passportno</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-2677">broj putovnice</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-2677">broj putovnice</span></span>

## <a name="croatia-personal-identification-oib-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-2681">克羅地亞個人身分識別 (OIB) 號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-2681">Croatia personal identification (OIB) number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-2682">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-2682">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-2683">11位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-2683">11 digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-2684">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-2684">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-2685">11位數：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-2685">11 digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-2686">10位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-2686">10 digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-2687">最後一個數位是檢查碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-2687">final digit is a check digit</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-2688">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-2688">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-2689">是</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-2689">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-2690">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-2690">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-2691">當鄰近性300個字元以內時，DLP 原則就會偵測到這種敏感資訊類型：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-2691">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-2692">函數 Func_croatia_oib_number 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-2692">The function Func_croatia_oib_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-2693">會找到來自 Keywords_croatia_eu_tax_file_number 的關鍵字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-2693">A keyword from Keywords_croatia_eu_tax_file_number is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-2694">校驗和通過。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-2694">The checksum passes.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-2695">當鄰近性300個字元以內時，DLP 原則就會偵測到這種敏感資訊類型的信賴度。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-2695">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-2696">函數 Func_croatia_oib_number 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-2696">The function Func_croatia_oib_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-2697">校驗和通過。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-2697">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Croatia Personal Identification (OIB) Number -->
      <Entity id="31983b6d-db95-4eb2-a630-b44bd091968d" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_croatia_oib_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_croatia_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_croatia_oib_number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="croatia-social-security-number-or-equivalent-identification"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-2728">克羅地亞社會安全號碼或同等身分識別</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-2728">Croatia social security number or equivalent identification</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="94f34-2729">這個敏感資訊類型實體只有歐盟社會保險號碼或同等識別碼的敏感資訊類型提供。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-2729">This sensitive information type entity is only available in the EU Social Security Number or Equivalent ID sensitive information type.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-2730">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-2730">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-2731">11位數，不含空格及分隔符號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-2731">11 digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-2732">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-2732">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-2733">11位數：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-2733">11 digits:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-2734">10位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-2734">10 digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-2735">一個檢查碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-2735">one check digit</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-2736">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-2736">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-2737">是</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-2737">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-2738">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-2738">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-2739">如果接近300個字元以內，則 DLP 原則偵測到此敏感資訊類型的置信量是85%：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-2739">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-2740">函數  `Func_croatia_eu_ssn_or_equivalent` 會找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-2740">The function  `Func_croatia_eu_ssn_or_equivalent` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-2741">找到來自的關鍵字  `Keywords_croatia_eu_ssn_or_equivalent` 。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-2741">A keyword from  `Keywords_croatia_eu_ssn_or_equivalent` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="94f34-2742">如果接近300個字元以內，則 DLP 原則偵測到此敏感資訊類型的置信量是75%：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-2742">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-2743">函數  `Func_croatia_eu_ssn_or_equivalent` 會找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-2743">The function  `Func_croatia_eu_ssn_or_equivalent` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
 <!-- EU SSN or Equivalent Number -->
<Entity id="d24e32a4-c0bb-4ba8-899d-6303b95742d9" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">

          <Match idRef="Keywords_croatia_eu_ssn_or_equivalent" />
        </Pattern> 
       <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_croatia_eu_ssn_or_equivalent" />
        </Pattern>      
</Entity>
```

## <a name="cyprus-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-2760">賽普勒斯驅動程式授權號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-2760">Cyprus drivers license number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-2761">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-2761">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-2762">12位數，不含空格及分隔符號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-2762">12 digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-2763">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-2763">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-2764">12位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-2764">12 digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-2765">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-2765">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-2766">否</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-2766">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-2767">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-2767">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-2768">當鄰近性300個字元以內時，DLP 原則就會偵測到這種敏感資訊類型的信賴度。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-2768">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-2769">正則運算式會  `Regex_cyprus_eu_driver's_license_number` 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-2769">The regular expression  `Regex_cyprus_eu_driver's_license_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-2770">`Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number`找到或的關鍵字 `Keywords_cyprus_eu_driver's_license_number` 。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-2770">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` or `Keywords_cyprus_eu_driver's_license_number` is found.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Cyprus Driver's License Number -->
      <Entity id="356fa104-f9ac-4aff-a0e4-2e6e65ea06c4" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_cyprus_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_cyprus_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="cyprus-identity-card"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-2895">賽普勒斯身分識別卡片</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-2895">Cyprus identity card</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="94f34-2896">此機密資訊類型僅可用於下列專案：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-2896">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-2897">資料遺失防護原則</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-2897">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-2898">通訊相容性原則</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-2898">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-2899">資訊管理</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-2899">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-2900">記錄管理</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-2900">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-2901">Microsoft cloud app security</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-2901">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-2902">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-2902">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-2903">10位數，不含空格及分隔符號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-2903">10 digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-2904">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-2904">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-2905">10位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-2905">10 digits</span></span> 
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-2906">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-2906">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-2907">不適用</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-2907">not applicable</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-2908">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-2908">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-2909">當鄰近性300個字元以內時，DLP 原則就會偵測到這種敏感資訊類型的信賴度。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-2909">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-2910">正則運算式會  `Regex_cyprus_eu_national_id_card` 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-2910">The regular expression  `Regex_cyprus_eu_national_id_card` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-2911">找到來自的關鍵字  `Keywords_cyprus_eu_national_id_card` 。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-2911">A keyword from  `Keywords_cyprus_eu_national_id_card` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml 
      <!-- Cyprus Identity Card -->
      <Entity id="3ba8afe5-7a6c-4929-8247-0001b6878438" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_cyprus_eu_national_id_card" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_cyprus_eu_national_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-2912">關鍵字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-2912">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keywords_cyprus_eu_national_id_card"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-2913">Keywords_cyprus_eu_national_id_card</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-2913">Keywords_cyprus_eu_national_id_card</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-2914">id 卡號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-2914">id card number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-2915">身分識別卡號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-2915">identity card number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-2916">kimlik karti</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-2916">kimlik karti</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-2917">國家識別號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-2917">national identification number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-2918">個人號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-2918">personal id number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-2919">ταυτοτητασ</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-2919">ταυτοτητασ</span></span>


## <a name="cyprus-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-2920">賽普勒斯護照號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-2920">Cyprus passport number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-2921">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-2921">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-2922">一個字母后接6-8 位數，沒有空格或分隔符號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-2922">one letter followed by 6-8 digits with no spaces or delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-2923">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-2923">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-2924">一個字母后接六個到八位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-2924">one letter followed by six to eight digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-2925">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-2925">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-2926">否</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-2926">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-2927">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-2927">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-2928">當鄰近性300個字元以內時，DLP 原則就會偵測到這種敏感資訊類型：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-2928">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-2929">正則運算式會  `Regex_cyprus_eu_passport_number` 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-2929">The regular expression  `Regex_cyprus_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-2930">`Keywords_eu_passport_number`找到或的關鍵字 `Keywords_cyprus_eu_passport_number` 。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-2930">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_cyprus_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-2931">正則運算式 `Regex_cyprus_eu_passport_date` 會找到日期格式為 DD/MM/YYYY 或找到關鍵字 from `Keywords_cyprus_eu_passport_date`</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-2931">The regular expression `Regex_cyprus_eu_passport_date` finds date in the format DD/MM/YYYY or a keyword from `Keywords_cyprus_eu_passport_date` is found</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-2932">當鄰近性300個字元以內時，DLP 原則就會偵測到這種敏感資訊類型的信賴度。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-2932">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-2933">正則運算式會  `Regex_cyprus_eu_passport_number` 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-2933">The regular expression  `Regex_cyprus_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-2934">`Keywords_eu_passport_number`找到或的關鍵字 `Keywords_cyprus_eu_passport_number` 。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-2934">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_cyprus_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span>  
    
```xml
      <!-- Cyprus Passport Number -->
      <Entity id="9193e2e8-7f8c-43c1-a274-ac40d651936f" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_cyprus_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_cyprus_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Regex_cyprus_eu_passport_date" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_cyprus_eu_passport_date" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_cyprus_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_cyprus_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="cyprus-tax-identification-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-2963">賽普勒斯納稅識別號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-2963">Cyprus tax identification number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="94f34-2964">此機密資訊類型僅可用於下列專案：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-2964">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-2965">資料遺失防護原則</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-2965">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-2966">通訊相容性原則</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-2966">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-2967">資訊管理</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-2967">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-2968">記錄管理</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-2968">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-2969">Microsoft cloud app security</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-2969">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-2970">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-2970">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-2971">指定的模式中的八位數和一個字母</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-2971">eight digits and one letter in the specified pattern</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-2972">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-2972">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-2973">八位數和一個字母：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-2973">eight digits and one letter:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-2974">"0" 或 "9"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-2974">a "0" or "9"</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-2975">七位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-2975">seven digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-2976">一個字母 (不區分大小寫) </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-2976">one letter (not case-sensitive)</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-2977">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-2977">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-2978">不適用</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-2978">not applicable</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-2979">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-2979">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-2980">當鄰近性300個字元以內時，DLP 原則就會偵測到這種敏感資訊類型：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-2980">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-2981">函數  `Func_cyprus_eu_tax_file_number` 會找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-2981">The function  `Func_cyprus_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-2982">找到來自的關鍵字  `Keywords_cyprus_eu_tax_file_number` 。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-2982">A keyword from  `Keywords_cyprus_eu_tax_file_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="94f34-2983">當鄰近性300個字元以內時，DLP 原則就會偵測到這種敏感資訊類型的信賴度。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-2983">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-2984">函數  `Func_cyprus_eu_tax_file_number` 會找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-2984">The function  `Func_cyprus_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Cyprus Tax Identification Number -->
      <Entity id="40e64bd9-55f3-4a09-9bd6-1db18dced9dd" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_cyprus_eu_tax_file_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_cyprus_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_cyprus_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="czech-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-3012">捷克文駕駛執照號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-3012">Czech driver's license number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-3013">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-3013">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-3014">兩個字母后接六位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-3014">two letters followed by six digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-3015">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-3015">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-3016">8個字母和數位：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-3016">eight letters and digits:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-3017">字母 ' E ' (不區分大小寫) </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-3017">letter 'E' (not case-sensitive)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-3018">一個字母</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-3018">a letter</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-3019">空格 (選用) </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-3019">a space (optional)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-3020">六位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-3020">six digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-3021">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-3021">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-3022">否</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-3022">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-3023">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-3023">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-3024">當鄰近性300個字元以內時，DLP 原則就會偵測到這種敏感資訊類型的信賴度。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-3024">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-3025">正則運算式會  `Regex_czech_republic_eu_driver's_license_number` 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-3025">The regular expression  `Regex_czech_republic_eu_driver's_license_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-3026">`Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number`找到或的關鍵字 `Keywords_czech_republic_eu_driver's_license_number` 。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-3026">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` or `Keywords_czech_republic_eu_driver's_license_number` is found.</span></span> 

```xml
      <Entity id="86b40d3b-d8ea-4c36-aab0-ef9416a6769c" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_czech_republic_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_czech_republic_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>

```

## <a name="czech-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-3152">捷克護照號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-3152">Czech passport number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-3153">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-3153">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-3154">不含空格或分隔符號的八位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-3154">eight digits without spaces or delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-3155">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-3155">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-3156">不含空格或分隔符號的八位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-3156">eight digits without spaces or delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-3157">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-3157">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-3158">否</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-3158">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-3159">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-3159">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-3160">當鄰近性300個字元以內時，DLP 原則就會偵測到這種敏感資訊類型：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-3160">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-3161">正則運算式會  `Regex_czech_republic_eu_passport_number` 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-3161">The regular expression  `Regex_czech_republic_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-3162">`Keywords_eu_passport_number`找到或的關鍵字 `Keywords_czech_republic_eu_passport_number` 。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-3162">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_czech_republic_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-3163">正則運算式 `Regex_eu_passport_date1` 會發現日期格式為 DD YYYY 或關鍵字 from `Keywords_eu_passport_date`</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-3163">The regular expression `Regex_eu_passport_date1` finds date in the format DD.MM.YYYY or a keyword from `Keywords_eu_passport_date` is found</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-3164">當鄰近性300個字元以內時，DLP 原則就會偵測到這種敏感資訊類型的信賴度。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-3164">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-3165">正則運算式會  `Regex_czech_republic_eu_passport_number` 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-3165">The regular expression  `Regex_czech_republic_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-3166">`Keywords_eu_passport_number`找到或的關鍵字 `Keywords_czech_republic_eu_passport_number` 。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-3166">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_czech_republic_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Czech Republic Passport Number -->
      <Entity id="7bcd8ce8-5e92-4bbe-bc92-fa669f0369fa" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_czech_republic_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_czech_republic_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Regex_eu_passport_date1" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_date" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_czech_republic_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_czech_republic_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="czech-personal-identity-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-3188">捷克個人身分識別號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-3188">Czech personal identity number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-3189">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-3189">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-3190">具有選用正斜線的九位數 (舊格式) 10 位數，選用正斜線 (新的格式) </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-3190">nine digits with optional forward slash (old format) 10 digits with optional forward slash (new format)</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-3191">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-3191">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-3192"> (舊格式的九位數) ：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-3192">nine digits (old format):</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-3193">六位數代表出生日期</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-3193">six digits that represent date of birth</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-3194">選用的正斜線</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-3194">an optional forward slash</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-3195">三位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-3195">three digits</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-3196">10位數 (新的格式) ：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-3196">10 digits (new format):</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-3197">六位數代表出生日期</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-3197">six digits that represent date of birth</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-3198">選用的正斜線</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-3198">an optional forward slash</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-3199">最後一個數位是檢查碼的四位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-3199">four digits where last digit is a check digit</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-3200">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-3200">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-3201">是</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-3201">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-3202">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-3202">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-3203">當鄰近性300個字元以內時，DLP 原則就會偵測到這種敏感資訊類型：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-3203">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-3204">函數 Func_czech_id_card 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-3204">The function Func_czech_id_card finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-3205">會找到來自 Keyword_czech_id_card 的關鍵字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-3205">A keyword from Keyword_czech_id_card is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-3206">校驗和通過。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-3206">The checksum passes.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-3207">當鄰近性300個字元以內時，DLP 原則就會偵測到這種敏感資訊類型的信賴度。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-3207">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-3208">函數 Func_czech_id_card_new_format 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-3208">The function Func_czech_id_card_new_format finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-3209">校驗和通過。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-3209">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Czech Personal Identity Number -->
      <!-- Czech Personal Identity Number -->
      <Entity id="60c0725a-4eb6-455b-9dda-05d8a7396497" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_czech_id_card" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_czech_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
        <Version minEngineVersion="15.20.3000.000">
          <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
            <IdMatch idRef="Func_czech_id_card_new_format" />
          </Pattern>
        </Version>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="czech-social-security-number-or-equivalent-identification"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-3256">捷克社會安全號碼或同等身分識別</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-3256">Czech social security number or equivalent identification</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-3257">這個敏感資訊類型實體只有歐盟社會保險號碼或同等識別碼的敏感資訊類型提供。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-3257">This sensitive information type entity is only available in the EU Social Security Number or Equivalent ID sensitive information type.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-3258">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-3258">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-3259">在指定的模式中，10位數和反斜線</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-3259">10 digits and a backslash in the specified pattern</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-3260">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-3260">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-3261">10位數和反斜線：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-3261">10 digits and a backslash:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-3262">對應至出生日期 (YYMMDD) 的六位數：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-3262">six digits that correspond to the birth date (YYMMDD):</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-3263">反斜線</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-3263">a backslash</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-3264">三位數的數位，對應至在相同日期出生的人員</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-3264">three digits that correspond to a serial number that separates persons born on the same date</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-3265">一個檢查碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-3265">one check digit</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-3266">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-3266">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-3267">是</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-3267">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-3268">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-3268">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-3269">如果接近300個字元以內，則 DLP 原則偵測到此敏感資訊類型的置信量是85%：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-3269">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-3270">函數  `Func_czech_republic_eu_ssn_or_equivalent` 會找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-3270">The function  `Func_czech_republic_eu_ssn_or_equivalent` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-3271">找到來自的關鍵字  `Keywords_czech_republic_eu_ssn_or_equivalent` 。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-3271">A keyword from  `Keywords_czech_republic_eu_ssn_or_equivalent` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="94f34-3272">如果接近300個字元以內，則 DLP 原則偵測到此敏感資訊類型的置信量是75%：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-3272">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-3273">函數  `Func_czech_republic_eu_ssn_or_equivalent` 會找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-3273">The function  `Func_czech_republic_eu_ssn_or_equivalent` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 

```xml
 <!-- EU SSN or Equivalent Number -->
<Entity id="d24e32a4-c0bb-4ba8-899d-6303b95742d9" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_czech_republic_eu_ssn_or_equivalent" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_czech_republic_eu_ssn_or_equivalent" />
        </Pattern> 
       <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_czech_republic_eu_ssn_or_equivalent" />
        </Pattern>      
</Entity>
```

## <a name="denmark-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-3289">丹麥駕照編號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-3289">Denmark driver's license number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-3290">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-3290">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-3291">不含空格及分隔符號的八位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-3291">eight digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-3292">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-3292">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-3293">八位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-3293">eight digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-3294">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-3294">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-3295">否</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-3295">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-3296">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-3296">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-3297">當鄰近性300個字元以內時，DLP 原則就會偵測到這種敏感資訊類型的信賴度。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-3297">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-3298">正則運算式會  `Regex_denmark_eu_driver's_license_number` 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-3298">The regular expression  `Regex_denmark_eu_driver's_license_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-3299">`Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number`找到或的關鍵字 `Keywords_denmark_eu_driver's_license_number` 。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-3299">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` or `Keywords_denmark_eu_driver's_license_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Denmark Driver's License Number -->
      <Entity id="98a95812-6203-451a-a220-d39870ebef0e" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_denmark_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_denmark_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```
