## <a name="denmark-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-3423">丹麥護照號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-3423">Denmark passport number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-3424">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-3424">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-3425">九位數，不含空格及分隔符號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-3425">nine digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-3426">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-3426">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-3427">九位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-3427">nine digits</span></span> 
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-3428">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-3428">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-3429">否</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-3429">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-3430">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-3430">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-3431">當鄰近性300個字元以內時，DLP 原則就會偵測到這種敏感資訊類型：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-3431">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-3432">正則運算式會  `Regex_denmark_eu_passport_number` 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-3432">The regular expression  `Regex_denmark_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-3433">`Keywords_eu_passport_number`找到或的關鍵字 `Keywords_denmark_eu_passport_number` 。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-3433">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_denmark_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-3434">正則運算式 `Regex_eu_passport_date2` 找到的日期格式為 DD MM YY 或關鍵字 from。 `Keywords_eu_passport_date`</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-3434">The regular expression `Regex_eu_passport_date2` finds date in the format DD MM YY or a keyword from `Keywords_eu_passport_date` is found</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-3435">當鄰近性300個字元以內時，DLP 原則就會偵測到這種敏感資訊類型的信賴度。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-3435">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-3436">正則運算式會  `Regex_denmark_eu_passport_number` 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-3436">The regular expression  `Regex_denmark_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-3437">`Keywords_eu_passport_number`找到或的關鍵字 `Keywords_denmark_eu_passport_number` 。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-3437">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_denmark_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Denmark Passport Number -->
      <Entity id="25e8c47e-e6fe-4884-a211-74898f8c0196" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_denmark_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_denmark_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Regex_eu_passport_date2" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_date" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_denmark_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_denmark_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>

```

## <a name="denmark-personal-identification-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-3457">丹麥個人身分識別號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-3457">Denmark personal identification number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-3458">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-3458">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-3459">10位數包含連字號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-3459">10 digits containing a hyphen</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-3460">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-3460">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-3461">10位數：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-3461">10 digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-3462">DDMMYY 格式的六位數（出生日期）</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-3462">six digits in the format DDMMYY, which are the date of birth</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-3463">連字號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-3463">a hyphen</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-3464">四位數的最後一個數位是檢查碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-3464">four digits where the final digit is a check digit</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-3465">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-3465">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-3466">是</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-3466">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-3467">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-3467">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-3468">當鄰近性300個字元以內時，DLP 原則就會偵測到這種敏感資訊類型的信賴度。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-3468">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-3469">正則運算式 Func_denmark_eu_tax_file_number 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-3469">The regular expression Func_denmark_eu_tax_file_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-3470">會找到來自 Keyword_denmark_id 的關鍵字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-3470">A keyword from Keyword_denmark_id is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-3471">校驗和通過。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-3471">The checksum passes.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-3472">DLP 原則在接近300個字元以內時，偵測到此敏感資訊類型的信賴度很低：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-3472">A DLP policy has low confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-3473">正則運算式 Func_denmark_eu_tax_file_number 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-3473">The regular expression Func_denmark_eu_tax_file_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-3474">校驗和通過。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-3474">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Denmark Personal Identification Number -->
      <!-- Denmark Personal Identification Number -->
      <Entity id="6c4f2fef-56e1-4c00-8093-88d7a01cf460" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_denmark_eu_tax_file_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_denmark_id" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_denmark_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="denmark-social-security-number-or-equivalent-identification"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-3546">丹麥社會安全號碼或對等身分識別</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-3546">Denmark social security number or equivalent identification</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="94f34-3547">這個敏感資訊類型實體只有歐盟社會保險號碼或同等識別碼的敏感資訊類型。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-3547">This sensitive information type entity is only available the EU Social Security Number or Equivalent ID sensitive information type.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-3548">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-3548">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-3549">在指定的模式中，10位數和連字號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-3549">10 digits and a hyphen in the specified pattern</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-3550">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-3550">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-3551">10位數和連字號：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-3551">10 digits and a hyphen:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-3552">對應至出生日期 (DDMMYY 的六位數) </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-3552">six digits that correspond to the birth date (DDMMYY)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-3553">連字號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-3553">a hyphen</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-3554">對應至序號的四位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-3554">four digits that correspond to a sequence number</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-3555">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-3555">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-3556">是</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-3556">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-3557">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-3557">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-3558">如果接近300個字元以內，則 DLP 原則偵測到此敏感資訊類型的置信量是85%：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-3558">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-3559">函數  `Func_denmark_eu_ssn_or_equivalent` 會找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-3559">The function  `Func_denmark_eu_ssn_or_equivalent` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-3560">找到來自的關鍵字  `Keywords_denmark_eu_ssn_or_equivalent` 。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-3560">A keyword from  `Keywords_denmark_eu_ssn_or_equivalent` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="94f34-3561">如果接近300個字元以內，則 DLP 原則偵測到此敏感資訊類型的置信量是75%：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-3561">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-3562">函數  `Func_denmark_eu_ssn_or_equivalent` 會找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-3562">The function  `Func_denmark_eu_ssn_or_equivalent` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
 <!-- EU SSN or Equivalent Number -->
<Entity id="d24e32a4-c0bb-4ba8-899d-6303b95742d9" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_denmark_eu_ssn_or_equivalent" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_denmark_eu_ssn_or_equivalent" />
        </Pattern> 
       <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_denmark_eu_ssn_or_equivalent" />
        </Pattern>      
</Entity>
```

## <a name="drug-enforcement-agency-dea-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-3576">藥物執行代理商 (DEA) 號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-3576">Drug Enforcement Agency (DEA) number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-3577">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-3577">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-3578">兩個字母后接7位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-3578">two letters followed by seven digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-3579">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-3579">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-3580">模式必須包含下列各項：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-3580">Pattern must include all of the following:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-3581">一個字母 (不區分大小寫) 這組可能的字母： abcdefghjklmnprstux，也就是註冊碼程式碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-3581">one letter (not case-sensitive) from this set of possible letters: abcdefghjklmnprstux, which is a registrant code</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-3582">一個字母 (不區分大小寫) ，也就是報名者姓氏或數位 ' 9 ' 的第一個字母。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-3582">one letter (not case-sensitive), which is the first letter of the registrant's last name or digit '9'</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-3583">七位數，最後一個是檢查碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-3583">seven digits, the last of which is the check digit</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-3584">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-3584">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-3585">是</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-3585">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-3586">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-3586">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-3587">當鄰近性300個字元以內時，DLP 原則就會偵測到這種敏感資訊類型：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-3587">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-3588">函數 Func_dea_number 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-3588">The function Func_dea_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-3589">找到來自的關鍵字 `Keyword_dea_number`</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-3589">A keyword from `Keyword_dea_number` is found</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-3590">校驗和通過。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-3590">The checksum passes.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-3591">當鄰近性300個字元以內時，DLP 原則就會偵測到這種敏感資訊類型的信賴度。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-3591">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-3592">函數 Func_dea_number 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-3592">The function Func_dea_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-3593">校驗和通過。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-3593">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
    <!-- DEA Number -->
    <Entity id="9a5445ad-406e-43eb-8bd7-cac17ab6d0e4" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_dea_number" />
      </Pattern>
      <Version minEngineVersion="15.20.1207.000" maxEngineVersion="15.20.3134.000">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_dea_number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Version>
      <Version minEngineVersion="15.20.3135.000">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_dea_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_dea_number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Version>
    </Entity>
```

- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-3598">藥物強制管理</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-3598">drug enforcement administration</span></span>

## <a name="estonia-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-3600">愛沙尼亞駕照編號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-3600">Estonia driver's license number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-3601">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-3601">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-3602">兩個字母后接六位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-3602">two letters followed by six digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-3603">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-3603">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-3604">兩個字母和六位數：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-3604">two letters and six digits:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-3605">字母 "ET" (不區分大小寫) </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-3605">the letters "ET" (not case-sensitive)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-3606">六位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-3606">six digits</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-3607">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-3607">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-3608">否</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-3608">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-3609">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-3609">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-3610">當鄰近性300個字元以內時，DLP 原則就會偵測到這種敏感資訊類型的信賴度。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-3610">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-3611">正則運算式會  `Regex_estonia_eu_driver's_license_number` 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-3611">The regular expression  `Regex_estonia_eu_driver's_license_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-3612">`Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number`找到或的關鍵字 `Keywords_estonia_eu_driver's_license_number` 。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-3612">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` or `Keywords_estonia_eu_driver's_license_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Estonia Driver's License Number -->
      <Entity id="51da8171-da70-4cc1-9d65-055a59ca4f83" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_estonia_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_estonia_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="estonia-personal-identification-code"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-3738">愛沙尼亞個人識別碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-3738">Estonia Personal Identification Code</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="94f34-3739">此機密資訊類型僅可用於下列專案：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-3739">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-3740">資料遺失防護原則</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-3740">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-3741">通訊相容性原則</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-3741">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-3742">資訊管理</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-3742">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-3743">記錄管理</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-3743">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-3744">Microsoft cloud app security</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-3744">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-3745">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-3745">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-3746">11位數，不含空格及分隔符號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-3746">11 digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-3747">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-3747">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-3748">11位數：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-3748">11 digits:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-3749">對應到性別和世紀的一位數 (奇數號碼，甚至號碼女;1-2：19世紀;3-4：20世紀;5-6：21世紀) </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-3749">one digit that corresponds to sex and century of birth (odd number male, even number female; 1-2: 19th century; 3-4: 20th century; 5-6: 21st century)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-3750">對應至出生日期 (YYMMDD 的六位數) </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-3750">six digits that correspond to date of birth (YYMMDD)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-3751">三位數，對應至在相同日期出生的人員的序號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-3751">three digits that correspond to a serial number separating persons born on the same date</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-3752">一個檢查碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-3752">one check digit</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-3753">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-3753">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-3754">是</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-3754">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-3755">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-3755">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-3756">當鄰近性300個字元以內時，DLP 原則就會偵測到這種敏感資訊類型：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-3756">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-3757">函數  `Func_estonia_eu_national_id_card` 會找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-3757">The function  `Func_estonia_eu_national_id_card` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-3758">找到來自的關鍵字  `Keywords_estonia_eu_national_id_card` 。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-3758">A keyword from  `Keywords_estonia_eu_national_id_card` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="94f34-3759">當鄰近性300個字元以內時，DLP 原則就會偵測到這種敏感資訊類型的信賴度。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-3759">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-3760">函數  `Func_estonia_eu_national_id_card` 會找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-3760">The function  `Func_estonia_eu_national_id_card` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Estonia Personal Identification Code -->
      <Entity id="bfb26de6-dad5-4d48-ab72-4789cdd0654c" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_estonia_eu_national_id_card" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_estonia_eu_national_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_estonia_eu_national_id_card" />
          <Any minMatches="0" maxMatches="0">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_estonia_eu_telephone_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_estonia_eu_mobile_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="estonia-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-3793">愛沙尼亞護照號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-3793">Estonia passport number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-3794">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-3794">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-3795">一個字母后接7位數，不含空格或分隔符號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-3795">one letter followed by seven digits with no spaces or delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-3796">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-3796">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-3797">一個字母后接7位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-3797">one letter followed by seven digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-3798">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-3798">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-3799">否</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-3799">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-3800">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-3800">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-3801">當鄰近性300個字元以內時，DLP 原則就會偵測到這種敏感資訊類型：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-3801">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-3802">正則運算式會  `Regex_estonia_eu_passport_number` 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-3802">The regular expression  `Regex_estonia_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-3803">`Keywords_eu_passport_number`找到或的關鍵字 `Keywords_estonia_eu_passport_number` 。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-3803">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_estonia_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-3804">正則運算式 `Regex_eu_passport_date1` 會發現日期格式為 DD YYYY 或關鍵字 from `Keywords_eu_passport_date`</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-3804">The regular expression `Regex_eu_passport_date1` finds date in the format DD.MM.YYYY or a keyword from `Keywords_eu_passport_date` is found</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-3805">當鄰近性300個字元以內時，DLP 原則就會偵測到這種敏感資訊類型的信賴度。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-3805">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-3806">正則運算式會  `Regex_estonia_eu_passport_number` 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-3806">The regular expression  `Regex_estonia_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-3807">`Keywords_eu_passport_number`找到或的關鍵字 `Keywords_estonia_eu_passport_number` 。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-3807">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_estonia_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Estonia Passport Number -->
      <Entity id="61f7073a-509e-425b-a754-bc01bb5d5b8c" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_estonia_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_estonia_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Regex_eu_passport_date1" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_date" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_estonia_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_estonia_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="eu-debit-card-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-3825">歐盟借方卡號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-3825">EU debit card number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-3826">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-3826">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-3827">16位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-3827">16 digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-3828">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-3828">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-3829">複雜且可靠的模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-3829">Complex and robust pattern</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-3830">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-3830">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-3831">是</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-3831">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-3832">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-3832">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-3833">當鄰近性300個字元以內時，DLP 原則就會偵測到這種敏感資訊類型：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-3833">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-3834">函數 Func_eu_debit_card 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-3834">The function Func_eu_debit_card finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-3835">下列專案中至少有一個為真：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-3835">At least one of the following is true:</span></span>
    - <span data-ttu-id="94f34-3836">會找到來自 Keyword_eu_debit_card 的關鍵字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-3836">A keyword from Keyword_eu_debit_card is found.</span></span>
    - <span data-ttu-id="94f34-3837">會找到來自 Keyword_card_terms_dict 的關鍵字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-3837">A keyword from Keyword_card_terms_dict is found.</span></span>
    - <span data-ttu-id="94f34-3838">會找到來自 Keyword_card_security_terms_dict 的關鍵字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-3838">A keyword from Keyword_card_security_terms_dict is found.</span></span>
    - <span data-ttu-id="94f34-3839">會找到來自 Keyword_card_expiration_terms_dict 的關鍵字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-3839">A keyword from Keyword_card_expiration_terms_dict is found.</span></span>
    - <span data-ttu-id="94f34-3840">函數 Func_expiration_date 會找到正確日期格式的日期。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-3840">The function Func_expiration_date finds a date in the right date format.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-3841">校驗和通過。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-3841">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
    <!-- EU Debit Card Number -->
    <Entity id="0e9b3178-9678-47dd-a509-37222ca96b42" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_eu_debit_card" />
        <Any minMatches="1">
          <Match idRef="Keyword_eu_debit_card" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_card_terms_dict" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_card_security_terms_dict" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_card_expiration_terms_dict" />
          <Match idRef="Func_expiration_date" />
        </Any>
      </Pattern>
    </Entity>
```

## <a name="finland-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-4288">芬蘭駕照編號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-4288">Finland driver's license number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-4289">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-4289">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-4290">10位數包含連字號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-4290">10 digits containing a hyphen</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-4291">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-4291">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-4292">10位數包含連字號：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-4292">10 digits containing a hyphen:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-4293">六位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-4293">six digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-4294">連字號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-4294">a hyphen</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-4295">三位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-4295">three digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-4296">一個數位或字母</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-4296">a digit or letter</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-4297">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-4297">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-4298">否</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-4298">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-4299">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-4299">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-4300">當鄰近性300個字元以內時，DLP 原則就會偵測到這種敏感資訊類型的信賴度。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-4300">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-4301">正則運算式會  `Regex_finland_eu_driver's_license_number` 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-4301">The regular expression  `Regex_finland_eu_driver's_license_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-4302">`Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number`找到或的關鍵字 `Keywords_finland_eu_driver's_license_number` 。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-4302">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` or `Keywords_finland_eu_driver's_license_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Finland Driver's License Number -->
      <Entity id="bb3b27a3-79bd-4ac4-81a7-f9fca3c7d1a7" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_finland_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_finland_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="finland-european-health-insurance-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-4433">芬蘭歐洲健康情況保險業號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-4433">Finland european health insurance number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="94f34-4434">此機密資訊類型僅可用於下列專案：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-4434">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-4435">資料遺失防護原則</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-4435">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-4436">通訊相容性原則</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-4436">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-4437">資訊管理</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-4437">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-4438">記錄管理</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-4438">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-4439">Microsoft cloud app security</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-4439">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-4440">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-4440">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-4441">20位數數位</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-4441">20-digit number</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-4442">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-4442">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-4443">20位數數位：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-4443">20-digit number:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-4444">10位數-8024680246</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-4444">10 digits - 8024680246</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-4445">選擇性空格或連字號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-4445">an optional space or hyphen</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-4446">10位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-4446">10 digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-4447">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-4447">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-4448">否</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-4448">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-4449">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-4449">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-4450">當鄰近性300個字元以內時，DLP 原則就會偵測到這種敏感資訊類型的信賴度。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-4450">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-4451">Regex Regex_Finland_European_Health_Insurance_Number 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-4451">The regex Regex_Finland_European_Health_Insurance_Number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-4452">會找到來自 Keyword_Finland_European_Health_Insurance_Number 的關鍵字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-4452">A keyword from Keyword_Finland_European_Health_Insurance_Number is found.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Finland European Health Insurance Number -->
      <Entity id="60f75aed-81bf-4625-89b0-0846b9248ee7" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_Finland_European_Health_Insurance_Number"/>
          <Match idRef="Keyword_Finland_European_Health_Insurance_Number"/>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="finland-national-id"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-4470">芬蘭國 ID</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-4470">Finland national ID</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-4471">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-4471">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-4472">六位數加上一個表示世紀的字元加上三個數字加上檢查碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-4472">six digits plus a character indicating a century plus three digits plus a check digit</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-4473">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-4473">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-4474">模式必須包含下列各項：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-4474">Pattern must include all of the following:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-4475">DDMMYY 格式的六位數，也就是出生日期</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-4475">six digits in the format DDMMYY, which are a date of birth</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-4476">世紀標記 ('-'、' + ' 或 ' a ' ) </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-4476">century marker (either '-', '+' or 'a')</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-4477">三位數的個人身分識別號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-4477">three-digit personal identification number</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-4478">不區分大小寫) （即檢查碼）的數位或字母 (</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-4478">a digit or letter (case insensitive) which is a check digit</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-4479">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-4479">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-4480">是</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-4480">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-4481">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-4481">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-4482">當鄰近性300個字元以內時，DLP 原則就會偵測到這種敏感資訊類型：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-4482">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-4483">函數 Func_finnish_national_id 找到符合模式的內容</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-4483">the function Func_finnish_national_id finds content that matches the pattern</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-4484">找到來自 Keyword_finnish_national_id 的關鍵字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-4484">a keyword from Keyword_finnish_national_id is found</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-4485">checksum 會通過</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-4485">the checksum passes</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-4486">當鄰近性300個字元以內時，DLP 原則就會偵測到這種敏感資訊類型的信賴度。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-4486">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-4487">函數 Func_finnish_national_id 找到符合模式的內容</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-4487">the function Func_finnish_national_id finds content that matches the pattern</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-4488">checksum 會通過</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-4488">the checksum passes</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Finnish National ID-->
      <Entity id="338FD995-4CB5-4F87-AD35-79BD1DD926C1" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_finnish_national_id" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_finnish_national_id" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_finnish_national_id" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="finland-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-4537">芬蘭護照號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-4537">Finland passport number</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-4538">這種機密資訊類型實體可在歐盟護照號碼機密資訊類型中使用，並可做為獨立的機密資訊類型實體。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-4538">This sensitive information type entity is available in the EU Passport Number sensitive information type and is available as a stand-alone sensitive information type entity.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-4539">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-4539">Format</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="94f34-4540">九個字母和數位的組合</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-4540">combination of nine letters and digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-4541">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-4541">Pattern</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="94f34-4542">九個字母和數位的組合：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-4542">combination of nine letters and digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-4543">兩個字母 (不區分大小寫) </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-4543">two letters (not case-sensitive)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-4544">七位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-4544">seven digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-4545">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-4545">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-4546">否</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-4546">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-4547">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-4547">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-4548">當鄰近性300個字元以內時，DLP 原則就會偵測到這種敏感資訊類型：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-4548">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-4549">正則運算式會 `Regex_finland_passport_number` 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-4549">The regular expression `Regex_finland_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-4550">`Keywords_eu_passport_number`找到或的關鍵字 `Keyword_finland_passport_number` 。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-4550">A keyword from `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keyword_finland_passport_number` is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-4551">正則運算式 `Regex_eu_passport_date1` 會發現日期格式為 DD YYYY 或關鍵字 from `Keywords_eu_passport_date`</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-4551">The regular expression `Regex_eu_passport_date1` finds date in the format DD.MM.YYYY or a keyword from `Keywords_eu_passport_date` is found</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-4552">當鄰近性300個字元以內時，DLP 原則就會偵測到這種敏感資訊類型的信賴度。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-4552">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-4553">正則運算式會 `Regex_finland_passport_number` 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-4553">The regular expression `Regex_finland_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-4554">`Keywords_eu_passport_number`找到或的關鍵字 `Keyword_finland_passport_number` 。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-4554">A keyword from `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keyword_finland_passport_number` is found.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Finland Passport Number -->
      <Entity id="d1685ac3-1d3a-40f8-8198-32ef5669c7a5" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_finland_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keyword_finland_passport_number" />
          </Any>
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Regex_eu_passport_date1" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_date" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_finland_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keyword_finland_passport_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="france-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-4578">法國駕駛執照號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-4578">France driver's license number</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-4579">您可以在歐盟駕駛執照號碼的敏感資訊類型中取得此機密資訊類型實體，並以獨立機密資訊類型實體形式提供。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-4579">This sensitive information type entity is available in the EU Driver's License Number sensitive information type and is available as a stand-alone sensitive information type entity.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-4580">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-4580">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-4581">12位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-4581">12 digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-4582">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-4582">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-4583">12位數與折扣類似的模式，例如法國電話號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-4583">12 digits with validation to discount similar patterns such as French telephone numbers</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-4584">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-4584">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-4585">否</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-4585">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-4586">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-4586">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-4587">當鄰近性300個字元以內時，DLP 原則就會偵測到這種敏感資訊類型的信賴度。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-4587">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-4588">函數 Func_french_drivers_license 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-4588">the function Func_french_drivers_license finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-4589">會找到來自 Keyword_french_drivers_license 的關鍵字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-4589">a keyword from Keyword_french_drivers_license is found.</span></span>

```xml
    <!-- France Driver's License Number -->
    <Entity id="18e55a36-a01b-4b0f-943d-dc10282a1824" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_french_drivers_license" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_french_drivers_license" />
      </Pattern>
    </Entity>
```

## <a name="france-health-insurance-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-4716">法國健康保險業號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-4716">France health insurance number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="94f34-4717">此機密資訊類型僅可用於下列專案：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-4717">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-4718">資料遺失防護原則</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-4718">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-4719">通訊相容性原則</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-4719">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-4720">資訊管理</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-4720">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-4721">記錄管理</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-4721">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-4722">Microsoft cloud app security</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-4722">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-4723">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-4723">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-4724">21位數的數位</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-4724">21-digit number</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-4725">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-4725">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-4726">21位數編號：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-4726">21-digit number:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-4727">10位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-4727">10 digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-4728">選擇性的空格</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-4728">an optional space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-4729">10位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-4729">10 digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-4730">選擇性的空格</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-4730">an optional space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-4731">一個數位</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-4731">a digit</span></span>


### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-4732">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-4732">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-4733">否</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-4733">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-4734">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-4734">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-4735">當鄰近性300個字元以內時，DLP 原則就會偵測到這種敏感資訊類型的信賴度。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-4735">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-4736">RegEx Regex_France_Health_Insurance_Number 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-4736">the regex Regex_France_Health_Insurance_Number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-4737">會找到來自 Keyword_France_Health_Insurance_Number 的關鍵字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-4737">a keyword from Keyword_France_Health_Insurance_Number is found.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- France Health Insurance Number -->
      <Entity id="9bc2069e-76df-4ff9-ac02-2f519469e236" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_France_Health_Insurance_Number"/>
          <Match idRef="Keyword_France_Health_Insurance_Number"/>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```
### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-4738">關鍵字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-4738">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_france_health_insurance_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-4739">Keyword_France_health_insurance_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-4739">Keyword_France_health_insurance_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-4740">保險卡</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-4740">insurance card</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-4741">購買 vitale</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-4741">carte vitale</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-4742">d'assuré社交</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-4742">carte d'assuré social</span></span>


## <a name="france-national-id-card-cni"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-4743">法國全國身分識別卡 (CNI) </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-4743">France national id card (CNI)</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-4744">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-4744">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-4745">12位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-4745">12 digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-4746">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-4746">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-4747">12位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-4747">12 digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-4748">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-4748">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-4749">否</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-4749">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-4750">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-4750">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-4751">DLP 原則在接近300個字元以內時，偵測到此敏感資訊類型的信賴度很低：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-4751">A DLP policy has low confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-4752">正則運算式 Regex_france_cni 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-4752">The regular expression Regex_france_cni finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-4753">會找到來自 Keywords_france_eu_national_id_card 的關鍵字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-4753">A keyword from Keywords_france_eu_national_id_card is found.</span></span>

```xml
    <!-- France CNI -->
    <Entity id="f741ac74-1bc0-4665-b69b-f0c7f927c0c4" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="65">
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
        <IdMatch idRef="Regex_france_cni" />
        <Match idRef="Keywords_france_eu_national_id_card" />
      </Pattern>
    </Entity>
```

- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-4758">nationale d'idenite 否</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-4758">carte nationale d'idenite no</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-4759">Cni#</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-4759">cni#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-4760">Cni</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-4760">cni</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-4766">numéro 購買 vitale</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-4766">numéro de carte vitale</span></span>

   
## <a name="france-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-4767">法國護照號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-4767">France passport number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="94f34-4768">在歐盟護照號碼機密資訊類型中提供此機密資訊類型實體。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-4768">This sensitive information type entity is available in the EU Passport Number sensitive information type.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="94f34-4769">它可以做為獨立的機密資訊類型實體。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-4769">It's available as a stand-alone sensitive information type entity.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-4770">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-4770">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-4771">九個數字和字母</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-4771">nine digits and letters</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-4772">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-4772">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-4773">九個數字和字母：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-4773">nine digits and letters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-4774">兩位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-4774">two digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-4775">兩個字母 (不區分大小寫) </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-4775">two letters (not case-sensitive)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-4776">五位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-4776">five digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-4777">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-4777">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-4778">否</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-4778">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-4779">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-4779">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-4780">當鄰近性300個字元以內時，DLP 原則就會偵測到這種敏感資訊類型：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-4780">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-4781">函數 `Func_fr_passport` 會找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-4781">The function `Func_fr_passport` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-4782">`Keywords_eu_passport_number`找到或的關鍵字 `Keywords_france_eu_passport_number` 。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-4782">A keyword from `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_france_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-4783">正則運算式 `Regex_eu_passport_date3` 會找到日期格式為 DD MM YYYY 或關鍵字 from。 `Keywords_eu_passport_date`</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-4783">The regular expression `Regex_eu_passport_date3` finds date in the format DD MM YYYY or a keyword from `Keywords_eu_passport_date` is found</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-4784">當鄰近性300個字元以內時，DLP 原則就會偵測到這種敏感資訊類型的信賴度。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-4784">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-4785">函數 `Func_fr_passport` 會找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-4785">The function `Func_fr_passport` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-4786">`Keywords_eu_passport_number`找到或的關鍵字 `Keywords_france_eu_passport_number` 。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-4786">A keyword from `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_france_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span>


```xml
    <!-- France Passport Number -->
    <Entity id="3008b884-8c8c-4cd8-a289-99f34fc7ff5d" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_fr_passport" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_france_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Regex_eu_passport_date3" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_date" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_fr_passport" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_france_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
    </Entity>
```

## <a name="france-social-security-number-insee-or-equivalent-identification"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-4817">法國社會安全號碼 (INSEE) 或同等身分識別</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-4817">France social security number (INSEE) or equivalent identification</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-4818">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-4818">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-4819">15位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-4819">15 digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-4820">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-4820">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-4821">必須符合下列其中一種模式：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-4821">Must match one of two patterns:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-4822">13位數後接一個空格後接兩位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-4822">13 digits followed by a space followed by two digits</span></span><br/>
<span data-ttu-id="94f34-4823">或</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-4823">or</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-4824">15個連續數位</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-4824">15 consecutive digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-4825">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-4825">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-4826">是</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-4826">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-4827">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-4827">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-4828">當鄰近性300個字元以內時，DLP 原則就會偵測到這種敏感資訊類型：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-4828">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-4829">函數 `Func_french_insee` 會找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-4829">The function `Func_french_insee` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-4830">會找到來自 Keyword_fr_insee 的關鍵字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-4830">A keyword from Keyword_fr_insee is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-4831">校驗和通過。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-4831">The checksum passes.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-4832">當鄰近性300個字元以內時，DLP 原則就會偵測到這種敏感資訊類型的信賴度。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-4832">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-4833">函數 Func_french_insee 或 Func_fr_insee 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-4833">The function Func_french_insee or Func_fr_insee finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-4834">校驗和通過。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-4834">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
    <!-- France INSEE -->
    <Entity id="71f62b97-efe0-4aa1-aa49-e14de253619d" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_french_insee" />
        <Any minMatches="0" maxMatches="0">
          <Match idRef="Keyword_fr_insee" />
        </Any>
      </Pattern>
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_french_insee" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_fr_insee" />
      </Pattern>
    </Entity>
```

## <a name="france-tax-identification-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-4865">法國納稅識別號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-4865">France tax identification number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-4866">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-4866">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-4867">13位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-4867">13 digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-4868">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-4868">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-4869">13位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-4869">13 digits</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-4870">一個位數必須是0、1、2或3</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-4870">One digit that must be 0, 1, 2, or 3</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-4871">一個數位</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-4871">One digit</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-4872">空格 (選用) </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-4872">A space (optional)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-4873">兩位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-4873">Two digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-4874">空格 (選用) </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-4874">A space (optional)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-4875">三位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-4875">Three digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-4876">空格 (選用) </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-4876">A space (optional)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-4877">三位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-4877">Three digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-4878">空格 (選用) </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-4878">A space (optional)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-4879">三個檢查碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-4879">Three check digits</span></span> 

  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-4880">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-4880">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-4881">是</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-4881">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-4882">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-4882">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-4883">當鄰近性300個字元以內時，DLP 原則就會偵測到這種敏感資訊類型：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-4883">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-4884">函數  `Func_france_eu_tax_file_number` 會找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-4884">The function  `Func_france_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-4885">找到來自的關鍵字  `Keywords_france_eu_tax_file_number` 。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-4885">A keyword from  `Keywords_france_eu_tax_file_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="94f34-4886">當鄰近性300個字元以內時，DLP 原則就會偵測到這種敏感資訊類型的信賴度。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-4886">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-4887">函數  `Func_france_eu_tax_file_number` 會找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-4887">The function  `Func_france_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- France Tax Identification Number (numéro SPI.) -->
      <Entity id="ed59e77e-171d-442c-9ec1-88e2ebcb5b0a" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_france_eu_tax_file_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_france_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_france_eu_tax_file_number" />
          <Any minMatches="0" maxMatches="0">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_france_eu_telephone_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_france_eu_mobile_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>

```

- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-4891">納稅識別碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-4891">tax id</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-4892">納稅識別碼否</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-4892">tax identification no</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-4893">納稅識別號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-4893">tax identification number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-4894">納稅否#</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-4894">tax no#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-4895">納稅否</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-4895">tax no</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-4896">納稅號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-4896">tax number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-4897">稅務登記編號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-4897">tax registration number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-4898">taxid#</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-4898">taxid#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-4899">taxidno#</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-4899">taxidno#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-4900">taxidnumber#</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-4900">taxidnumber#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-4901">taxno#</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-4901">taxno#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-4902">taxnumber#</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-4902">taxnumber#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-4903">taxnumber</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-4903">taxnumber</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-4904">納稅人識別碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-4904">tin id</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-4905">tin no</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-4905">tin no</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-4906">錫#</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-4906">tin#</span></span>


## <a name="france-value-added-tax-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-4907">法國加值稅收號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-4907">France value added tax number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="94f34-4908">此機密資訊類型僅可用於下列專案：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-4908">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-4909">資料遺失防護原則</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-4909">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-4910">通訊相容性原則</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-4910">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-4911">資訊管理</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-4911">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-4912">記錄管理</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-4912">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-4913">Microsoft cloud app security</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-4913">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-4914">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-4914">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-4915">13個字元的字母數位模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-4915">13 character alphanumeric pattern</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-4916">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-4916">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-4917">13個字元的字母數位模式：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-4917">13 character alphanumeric pattern:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-4918">兩個字母-FR (不區分大小寫) </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-4918">two letters  - FR (case insensitive)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-4919">選擇性空格或連字號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-4919">an optional space or hyphen</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-4920">兩個字母或數位</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-4920">two letters or digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-4921">選用的空格、點、連字號或逗號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-4921">an optional space, dot, hyphen, or comma</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-4922">三位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-4922">three digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-4923">選用的空格、點、連字號或逗號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-4923">an optional space, dot, hyphen, or comma</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-4924">三位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-4924">three digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-4925">選用的空格、點、連字號或逗號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-4925">an optional space, dot, hyphen, or comma</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-4926">三位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-4926">three digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-4927">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-4927">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-4928">是</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-4928">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-4929">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-4929">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-4930">當鄰近性300個字元以內時，DLP 原則就會偵測到這種敏感資訊類型：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-4930">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-4931">函數 Func_france_value_added_tax_number 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-4931">The function Func_france_value_added_tax_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-4932">會找到來自 Keywords_france_value_added_tax_number 的關鍵字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-4932">A keyword from Keywords_france_value_added_tax_number is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-4933">當鄰近性300個字元以內時，DLP 原則就會偵測到這種敏感資訊類型的信賴度。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-4933">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-4934">函數 Func_france_value_added_tax_number 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-4934">The function Func_france_value_added_tax_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- France Value Added Tax Number -->
      <Entity id="949121e6-ad9f-4379-8731-710342baea78" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_france_value_added_tax_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_france_value_added_tax_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_france_value_added_tax_number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```
### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-4935">關鍵字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-4935">Keywords</span></span>
