## <a name="germany-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-4947">德國駕駛執照號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-4947">Germany driver's license number</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-4948">這種敏感資訊類型實體包含在歐盟駕駛執照號碼的敏感資訊類型中。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-4948">This sensitive information type entity is included in the EU Driver's License Number sensitive information type.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="94f34-4949">它可以做為獨立的機密資訊類型實體。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-4949">It's available as a stand-alone sensitive information type entity.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-4950">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-4950">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-4951">11位數和字母的組合</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-4951">combination of 11 digits and letters</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-4952">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-4952">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-4953">11個數字和字母 (不區分大小寫) ：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-4953">11 digits and letters (not case-sensitive):</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-4954">一個數位或字母</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-4954">a digit or letter</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-4955">兩位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-4955">two digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-4956">六個數字或字母</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-4956">six digits or letters</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-4957">一個數位</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-4957">a digit</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-4958">一個數位或字母</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-4958">a digit or letter</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-4959">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-4959">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-4960">是</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-4960">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-4961">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-4961">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-4962">當鄰近性300個字元以內時，DLP 原則就會偵測到這種敏感資訊類型的信賴度。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-4962">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-4963">函數 Func_german_drivers_license 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-4963">The function Func_german_drivers_license finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-4964">會找到來自 Keyword_german_drivers_license_number 的關鍵字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-4964">A keyword from Keyword_german_drivers_license_number is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-4965">校驗和通過。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-4965">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml

    <Entity id="91da9335-1edb-45b7-a95f-5fe41a16c63c" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_german_drivers_license" />

    </Entity>
```

## <a name="germany-identity-card-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-5114">德國身分識別卡號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5114">Germany identity card number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-5115">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5115">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-5116">自11月2010：9個字母和數位</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5116">since 1 November 2010: Nine letters and digits</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-5117">從1年4月1987至31年10月2010：10位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5117">from 1 April 1987 until 31 October 2010: 10 digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-5118">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5118">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-5119">自11月1日2010：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5119">since 1 November 2010:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-5120">一個字母 (不區分大小寫) </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5120">one letter (not case-sensitive)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-5121">八位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5121">eight digits</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-5122">從1年4月1987至31年10月2010：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5122">from 1 April 1987 until 31 October 2010:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-5123">10位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5123">10 digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-5124">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5124">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-5125">否</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5125">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-5126">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5126">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-5127">DLP 原則在接近300個字元以內時，偵測到此敏感資訊類型的信賴度很低：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5127">A DLP policy has low confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-5128">正則運算式 Regex_germany_id_card 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5128">The regular expression Regex_germany_id_card finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-5129">會找到來自 Keyword_germany_id_card 的關鍵字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5129">A keyword from Keyword_germany_id_card is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Germany Identity Card Number -->
<Entity id="e577372f-c42e-47a0-9d85-bebed1c237d4" recommendedConfidence="65" patternsProximity="300">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
     <IdMatch idRef="Regex_germany_id_card"/>
     <Match idRef="Keyword_germany_id_card"/>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-5130">關鍵字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5130">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_germany_id_card"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-5131">Keyword_germany_id_card</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5131">Keyword_germany_id_card</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-5132">ausweis</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5132">ausweis</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-5133">gpid</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5133">gpid</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-5134">識別</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5134">identification</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-5135">identifikation</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5135">identifikation</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-5136">identifizierungsnummer</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5136">identifizierungsnummer</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-5137">身份證</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5137">identity card</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-5138">身分識別號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5138">identity number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-5139">識別碼-nummer</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5139">id-nummer</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-5140">個人識別碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5140">personal id</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-5141">personalausweis</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5141">personalausweis</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-5142">persönliche 識別碼 nummer</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5142">persönliche id nummer</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-5143">persönliche identifikationsnummer</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5143">persönliche identifikationsnummer</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-5144">persönliche-識別碼-nummer</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5144">persönliche-id-nummer</span></span>


## <a name="germany-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-5145">德國護照號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5145">Germany passport number</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-5146">此機密資訊類型的實體包含在歐盟護照號碼機密資訊類型中，並可做為獨立的機密資訊類型實體。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5146">This sensitive information type entity is included in the EU Passport Number sensitive information type and is available as a stand-alone sensitive information type entity.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-5147">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5147">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-5148">10位數或字母</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5148">10 digits or letters</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-5149">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5149">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-5150">模式必須包含下列各項：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5150">Pattern must include all of the following:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-5151">第一個字元是此集合中的數位或字母。 (C、F、G、H、J、K) </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5151">first character is a digit or a letter from this set (C, F, G, H, J, K)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-5152">三位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5152">three digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-5153">此集合中有五個數字或字母 (C、-H、J-N、P、R、T、V-Z) </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5153">five digits or letters from this set (C, -H, J-N, P, R, T, V-Z)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-5154">一個數位</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5154">a digit</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-5155">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5155">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-5156">是</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5156">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-5157">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5157">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-5158">當鄰近性300個字元以內時，DLP 原則就會偵測到這種敏感資訊類型：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5158">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-5159">函數 Func_german_passport 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5159">The function Func_german_passport finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-5160">`Keyword_german_passport`找到或的關鍵字 `Keywords_eu_passport_number_common` 。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5160">A keyword from `Keyword_german_passport` or `Keywords_eu_passport_number_common` is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-5161">校驗和通過。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5161">The checksum passes.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-5162">當鄰近性300個字元以內時，DLP 原則就會偵測到這種敏感資訊類型的信賴度。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5162">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-5163">函數 Func_german_passport_data 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5163">The function Func_german_passport_data finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-5164">`Keyword_german_passport`找到或的關鍵字 `Keywords_eu_passport_number_common` 。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5164">A keyword from `Keyword_german_passport` or `Keywords_eu_passport_number_common` is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-5165">校驗和通過。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5165">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
    <!-- German Passport Number -->
    <Entity id="2e3da144-d42b-47ed-b123-fbf78604e52c" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_german_passport" />
        <Any minMatches="1">
          <Match idRef="Keyword_german_passport" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number_common" />
        </Any>
      </Pattern>
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_german_passport_data" />
        <Any minMatches="1">
          <Match idRef="Keyword_german_passport" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number_common" />
        </Any>
      </Pattern>
    </Entity>
```

- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-5178">護照#</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5178">passport#</span></span>

## <a name="germany-tax-identification-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-5188">德國納稅識別號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5188">Germany tax identification number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-5189">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5189">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-5190">11位數，不含空格及分隔符號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5190">11 digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-5191">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5191">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-5192">11位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5192">11 digits</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-5193">兩位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5193">Two digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-5194">選擇性的空格</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5194">An optional space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-5195">三位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5195">Three digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-5196">選擇性的空格</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5196">An optional space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-5197">三位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5197">Three digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-5198">選擇性的空格</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5198">An optional space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-5199">兩位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5199">Two digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-5200">一個檢查碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5200">one check digit</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-5201">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5201">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-5202">是</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5202">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-5203">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5203">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-5204">當鄰近性300個字元以內時，DLP 原則就會偵測到這種敏感資訊類型：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5204">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-5205">函數  `Func_germany_eu_tax_file_number` 會找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5205">The function  `Func_germany_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-5206">找到來自的關鍵字  `Keywords_germany_eu_tax_file_number` 。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5206">A keyword from  `Keywords_germany_eu_tax_file_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="94f34-5207">當鄰近性300個字元以內時，DLP 原則就會偵測到這種敏感資訊類型的信賴度。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5207">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-5208">函數  `Func_germany_eu_tax_file_number` 會找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5208">The function  `Func_germany_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Germany Tax Identification Number -->
      <Entity id="43316a89-9880-40cf-b980-04bc7eefcec5" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_germany_eu_tax_file_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_germany_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_germany_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="germany-value-added-tax-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-5234">德國加值稅號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5234">Germany value added tax number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="94f34-5235">此機密資訊類型僅可用於下列專案：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5235">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-5236">資料遺失防護原則</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5236">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-5237">通訊相容性原則</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5237">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-5238">資訊管理</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5238">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-5239">記錄管理</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5239">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-5240">Microsoft cloud app security</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5240">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-5241">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5241">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-5242">11個字元的字母數位模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5242">11 character alphanumeric pattern</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-5243">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5243">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-5244">11個字元的字母數位模式：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5244">11-character alphanumeric pattern:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-5245">字母 D 或 D</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5245">a letter D or d</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-5246">字母 E 或 E</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5246">a letter E or e</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-5247">選擇性的空格</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5247">an optional space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-5248">三位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5248">three digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-5249">選擇性空格或逗號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5249">an optional space or comma</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-5250">三位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5250">three digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-5251">選擇性空格或逗號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5251">an optional space or comma</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-5252">三位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5252">three digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-5253">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5253">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-5254">是</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5254">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-5255">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5255">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-5256">當鄰近性300個字元以內時，DLP 原則就會偵測到這種敏感資訊類型：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5256">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-5257">函數 Func_germany_value_added_tax_number 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5257">The function Func_germany_value_added_tax_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-5258">會找到來自 Keywords_germany_value_added_tax_number 的關鍵字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5258">A keyword from Keywords_germany_value_added_tax_number is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-5259">當鄰近性300個字元以內時，DLP 原則就會偵測到這種敏感資訊類型的信賴度。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5259">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-5260">函數 Func_germany_value_added_tax_number 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5260">The function Func_germany_value_added_tax_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Germany Value Added Tax Number -->
      <Entity id="db177eb2-8811-4842-bffc-128c14aa219f" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_germany_value_added_tax_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_germany_value_added_tax_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_germany_value_added_tax_number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="greece-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-5270">希臘駕駛執照號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5270">Greece driver's license number</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-5271">此機密資訊類型的實體包含在歐盟駕駛執照號碼的敏感資訊類型中，並可做為獨立機密資訊類型實體。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5271">This sensitive information type entity is included in the EU Driver's License Number sensitive information type and is available as a stand-alone sensitive information type entity.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-5272">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5272">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-5273">九位數，不含空格及分隔符號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5273">nine digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-5274">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5274">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-5275">九位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5275">nine digits</span></span> 
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-5276">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5276">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-5277">否</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5277">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-5278">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5278">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-5279">當鄰近性300個字元以內時，DLP 原則就會偵測到這種敏感資訊類型的信賴度。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5279">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-5280">正則運算式會  `Regex_greece_eu_driver's_license_number` 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5280">The regular expression  `Regex_greece_eu_driver's_license_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-5281">`Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number`找到或的關鍵字 `Keywords_greece_eu_driver's_license_number` 。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5281">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` or `Keywords_greece_eu_driver's_license_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Greece Driver's License Number -->
      <Entity id="7a2200b5-aacf-4e3c-ab36-136d3e68b7da" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_greece_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_greece_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="greece-national-id-card"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-5407">希臘國身分識別卡</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5407">Greece national ID card</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-5408">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5408">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-5409">7-8 字母和數位的組合，加上破折號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5409">Combination of 7-8 letters and numbers plus a dash</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-5410">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5410">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-5411"> (舊格式) 有七個字母和數位：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5411">Seven letters and numbers (old format):</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-5412"> (希臘字母的任何字母的一個字母) </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5412">One letter (any letter of the Greek alphabet)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-5413">虛線</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5413">A dash</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-5414">六位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5414">Six digits</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-5415"> (新格式) 為八個字母和數位：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5415">Eight letters and numbers (new format):</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-5416">兩個字母大寫字元會同時出現于希臘字母和拉丁字母表中 (ABEZHIKMNOPTYX) </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5416">Two letters whose uppercase character occurs in both the Greek and Latin alphabets (ABEZHIKMNOPTYX)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-5417">虛線</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5417">A dash</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-5418">六位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5418">Six digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-5419">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5419">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-5420">否</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5420">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-5421">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5421">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-5422">當鄰近性300個字元以內時，DLP 原則就會偵測到這種敏感資訊類型：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5422">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-5423">正則運算式 Regex_greece_id_card 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5423">The regular expression Regex_greece_id_card finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-5424">會找到來自 Keyword_greece_id_card 的關鍵字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5424">A keyword from Keyword_greece_id_card is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-5425">DLP 原則在接近300個字元以內時，偵測到此敏感資訊類型的信賴度很低：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5425">A DLP policy has low confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-5426">正則運算式 Regex_greece_id_card 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5426">The regular expression Regex_greece_id_card finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Greece National ID Card -->
      <Entity id="82568215-1da1-46d3-874a-d2294d81b5ac" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_greece_id_card" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_greece_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_greece_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-5427">關鍵字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5427">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_greece_id_card"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-5428">Keyword_greece_id_card</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5428">Keyword_greece_id_card</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-5429">希臘文識別碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5429">greek id</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-5430">希臘國識別碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5430">greek national id</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-5431">希臘文個人編碼卡</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5431">greek personal id card</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-5432">希臘警方識別碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5432">greek police id</span></span>

## <a name="greece-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-5437">希臘護照號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5437">Greece passport number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-5438">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5438">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-5439">兩個字母后接7位數，不含空格或分隔符號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5439">Two letters followed by seven digits with no spaces or delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-5440">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5440">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-5441">兩個字母后接7位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5441">Two letters followed by seven digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-5442">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5442">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-5443">否</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5443">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-5444">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5444">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-5445">當鄰近性300個字元以內時，DLP 原則就會偵測到這種敏感資訊類型：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5445">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-5446">正則運算式會  `Regex_greece_eu_passport_number` 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5446">The regular expression  `Regex_greece_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-5447">`Keywords_eu_passport_number`找到或的關鍵字 `Keywords_greece_eu_passport_number` 。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5447">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_greece_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-5448">正則運算式 `Regex_greece_eu_passport_date` 會以 DD MMM YY 的格式來找到日期 (範例-28 月19日) 或 `Keywords_greece_eu_passport_date` 找到關鍵字 from</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5448">The regular expression `Regex_greece_eu_passport_date` finds date in the format DD MMM YY (Example - 28 Aug 19) or a keyword from `Keywords_greece_eu_passport_date` is found</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-5449">當鄰近性300個字元以內時，DLP 原則就會偵測到這種敏感資訊類型的信賴度。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5449">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-5450">正則運算式會  `Regex_greece_eu_passport_number` 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5450">The regular expression  `Regex_greece_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-5451">`Keywords_eu_passport_number`找到或的關鍵字 `Keywords_greece_eu_passport_number` 。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5451">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_greece_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Greece Passport Number -->
      <Entity id="7e65eb47-cdf9-4f52-8f90-2a27d5ee67e3" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_greece_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_greece_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Regex_greece_eu_passport_date" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_greece_eu_passport_date" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_greece_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_greece_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="greece-social-security-number-amka"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-5468"> (AMKA) 的希臘社會安全號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5468">Greece Social Security Number (AMKA)</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="94f34-5469">此機密資訊類型僅可用於下列專案：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5469">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-5470">資料遺失防護原則</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5470">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-5471">通訊相容性原則</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5471">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-5472">資訊管理</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5472">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-5473">記錄管理</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5473">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-5474">Microsoft cloud app security</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5474">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-5475">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5475">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-5476">不含空格及分隔符號的11位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5476">Eleven digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-5477">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5477">Pattern</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-5478">六位數的出生日期 YYMMDD</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5478">6 digits as date of birth YYMMDD</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-5479">4位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5479">4 digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-5480">檢查碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5480">a check digit</span></span>
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-5481">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5481">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-5482">是</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5482">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-5483">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5483">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-5484">當鄰近性300個字元以內時，DLP 原則就會偵測到這種敏感資訊類型：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5484">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-5485">函數  `Func_greece_eu_ssn` 會找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5485">The function  `Func_greece_eu_ssn` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-5486">找到來自的關鍵字  `Keywords_greece_eu_ssn_or_equivalent` 。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5486">A keyword from  `Keywords_greece_eu_ssn_or_equivalent` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="94f34-5487">當鄰近性300個字元以內時，DLP 原則就會偵測到這種敏感資訊類型的信賴度。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5487">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-5488">函數  `Func_greece_eu_ssn` 會找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5488">The function  `Func_greece_eu_ssn` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 

```xml
      <!-- Greece Social Security Number (AMKA) -->
      <Entity id="e39b03f4-50ea-41ae-af7a-a4b9539596ad" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_greece_eu_ssn" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_greece_eu_ssn_or_equivalent" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_greece_eu_ssn" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="greece-tax-identification-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-5499">希臘納稅識別號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5499">Greece tax identification number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="94f34-5500">此機密資訊類型僅可用於下列專案：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5500">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-5501">資料遺失防護原則</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5501">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-5502">通訊相容性原則</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5502">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-5503">資訊管理</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5503">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-5504">記錄管理</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5504">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-5505">Microsoft cloud app security</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5505">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-5506">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5506">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-5507">九位數，不含空格及分隔符號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5507">Nine digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-5508">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5508">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-5509">九位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5509">Nine digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-5510">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5510">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-5511">不適用</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5511">Not applicable</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-5512">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5512">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-5513">當鄰近性300個字元以內時，DLP 原則就會偵測到這種敏感資訊類型的信賴度。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5513">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-5514">正則運算式會  `Regex_greece_eu_tax_file_number` 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5514">The regular expression  `Regex_greece_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-5515">找到來自的關鍵字  `Keywords_greece_eu_tax_file_number` 。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5515">A keyword from  `Keywords_greece_eu_tax_file_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Greek Tax Identification Number -->
      <Entity id="15a54a5a-53d4-4080-ad43-a2a4fe1d3bf7" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_greece_eu_tax_file_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_greece_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-5531">taxid#</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5531">taxid#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-5532">taxidno#</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5532">taxidno#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-5533">taxidnumber#</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5533">taxidnumber#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-5534">taxno#</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5534">taxno#</span></span>

## <a name="hong-kong-identity-card-hkid-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-5544">香港身分識別卡 (HKID) 號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5544">Hong Kong identity card (HKID) number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-5545">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5545">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-5546">8-9 字母和數位的組合，以及最後一個字元兩邊的 optional 括弧</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5546">Combination of 8-9 letters and numbers plus optional parentheses around the final character</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-5547">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5547">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-5548">8-9 個字母的組合：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5548">Combination of 8-9 letters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-5549">1-2 字母 (不區分大小寫) </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5549">1-2 letters (not case-sensitive)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-5550">六位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5550">Six digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-5551">最後一個字元 (任何數位或字母 A) ，也就是檢查碼，也可以以括弧括住。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5551">The final character (any digit or the letter A), which is the check digit and is optionally enclosed in parentheses.</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-5552">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5552">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-5553">是</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5553">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-5554">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5554">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-5555">當鄰近性300個字元以內時，DLP 原則就會偵測到這種敏感資訊類型的信賴度。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5555">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-5556">函數 Func_hong_kong_id_card 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5556">The function Func_hong_kong_id_card finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-5557">會找到來自 Keyword_hong_kong_id_card 的關鍵字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5557">A keyword from Keyword_hong_kong_id_card is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-5558">校驗和通過。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5558">The checksum passes.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-5559">DLP 原則在接近300個字元以內時，偵測到此敏感資訊類型的信賴度很低：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5559">A DLP policy has low confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-5560">函數 Func_hong_kong_id_card 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5560">The function Func_hong_kong_id_card finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-5561">校驗和通過。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5561">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Hong Kong Identity Card (HKID) number -->
<Entity id="e63c28a7-ad29-4c17-a41a-3d2a0b70fd9c" recommendedConfidence="75" patternsProximity="300">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
     <IdMatch idRef="Func_hong_kong_id_card"/>
     <Match idRef="Keyword_hong_kong_id_card"/>
  </Pattern>
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
     <IdMatch idRef="Func_hong_kong_id_card"/>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="hungary-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-5601">匈牙利駕照號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5601">Hungary driver's license number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-5602">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5602">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-5603">兩個字母后接六位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5603">Two letters followed by six digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-5604">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5604">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-5605">兩個字母和六位數：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5605">Two letters and six digits:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-5606">兩個字母 (不區分大小寫) </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5606">Two letters (not case-sensitive)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-5607">六位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5607">Six digits</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-5608">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5608">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-5609">否</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5609">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-5610">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5610">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-5611">當鄰近性300個字元以內時，DLP 原則就會偵測到這種敏感資訊類型的信賴度。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5611">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-5612">正則運算式會  `Regex_hungary_eu_driver's_license_number` 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5612">The regular expression  `Regex_hungary_eu_driver's_license_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-5613">`Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number`找到或的關鍵字 `Keywords_hungary_eu_driver's_license_number` 。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5613">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` or `Keywords_hungary_eu_driver's_license_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <Entity id="9d31c46b-6e6b-444c-aeb1-6dd7e604bb24" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_hungary_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_hungary_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="hungary-personal-identification-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-5738">匈牙利個人身分識別號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5738">Hungary personal identification number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="94f34-5739">此機密資訊類型僅可用於下列專案：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5739">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-5740">資料遺失防護原則</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5740">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-5741">通訊相容性原則</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5741">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-5742">資訊管理</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5742">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-5743">記錄管理</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5743">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-5744">Microsoft cloud app security</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5744">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-5745">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5745">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-5746">11位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5746">11 digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-5747">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5747">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-5748">11位數：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5748">11 digits:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-5749">對應于性別 (1-男，2-女，其他號碼的一個數位，也可能是在1900或公民的情況下出生的公民) </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5749">One digit that corresponds to gender (1-male, 2-female, other numbers are also possible for citizens born before 1900 or citizens with double citizenship)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-5750">對應至出生日期 (YYMMDD 的六位數) </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5750">Six digits that correspond to birth date (YYMMDD)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-5751">對應至序列值的三位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5751">Three digits that correspond to a serial number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-5752">一個檢查碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5752">One check digit</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-5753">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5753">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-5754">是</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5754">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-5755">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5755">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-5756">當鄰近性300個字元以內時，DLP 原則就會偵測到這種敏感資訊類型：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5756">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-5757">函數  `Func_hungary_eu_national_id_card` 會找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5757">The function  `Func_hungary_eu_national_id_card` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-5758">找到來自的關鍵字  `Keywords_hungary_eu_national_id_card` 。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5758">A keyword from  `Keywords_hungary_eu_national_id_card` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="94f34-5759">當鄰近性300個字元以內時，DLP 原則就會偵測到這種敏感資訊類型的信賴度。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5759">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-5760">函數  `Func_hungary_eu_national_id_card` 會找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5760">The function  `Func_hungary_eu_national_id_card` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Hungary Personal Identification Number -->
      <Entity id="7b5cc218-7046-47d9-80c9-f325b50896ca" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_hungary_eu_national_id_card" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_hungary_eu_national_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_hungary_eu_national_id_card" />
          <Any minMatches="0" maxMatches="0">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_hungary_eu_telephone_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_hungary_eu_mobile_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

#### <a name="keywords_hungary_eu_national_id_card"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-5762">Keywords_hungary_eu_national_id_card</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5762">Keywords_hungary_eu_national_id_card</span></span>

## <a name="hungary-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-5771">匈牙利護照號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5771">Hungary passport number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-5772">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5772">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-5773">兩個字母后接六個或7位數，不含空格或分隔符號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5773">Two letters followed by six or seven digits with no spaces or delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-5774">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5774">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-5775">兩個字母后接六位數或七位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5775">Two letters followed by six or seven digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-5776">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5776">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-5777">否</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5777">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-5778">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5778">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-5779">當鄰近性300個字元以內時，DLP 原則就會偵測到這種敏感資訊類型：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5779">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-5780">正則運算式會  `Regex_hungary_eu_passport_number` 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5780">The regular expression  `Regex_hungary_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-5781">`Keywords_eu_passport_number`找到或的關鍵字 `Keywords_hungary_eu_passport_number` 。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5781">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_hungary_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-5782">正則運算式 `Regex_hungary_eu_passport_date` 會找到以 DD MMM/MMM YY 格式的日期 (範例-01 MÁR/MAR 12) 或找到關鍵字 `Keywords_eu_passport_date` 。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5782">The regular expression `Regex_hungary_eu_passport_date` finds date in the format  DD MMM/MMM YY (Example - 01 MÁR/MAR 12) or a keyword from `Keywords_eu_passport_date` is found</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-5783">當鄰近性300個字元以內時，DLP 原則就會偵測到這種敏感資訊類型的信賴度。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5783">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-5784">正則運算式會  `Regex_hungary_eu_passport_number` 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5784">The regular expression  `Regex_hungary_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-5785">`Keywords_eu_passport_number`找到或的關鍵字 `Keywords_hungary_eu_passport_number` 。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5785">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_hungary_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Hungary Passport Number -->
      <Entity id="5b483910-9aa7-4c99-9917-f4001464bda7" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_hungary_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_hungary_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Regex_hungary_eu_passport_date" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_date" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_hungary_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_hungary_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="hungary-social-security-number-taj"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-5805">匈牙利社會安全號碼 (TAJ) </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5805">Hungary social security number (TAJ)</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-5806">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5806">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-5807">九位數，不含空格及分隔符號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5807">Nine digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-5808">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5808">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-5809">九位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5809">Nine digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-5810">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5810">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-5811">是</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5811">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-5812">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5812">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-5813">當鄰近性300個字元以內時，DLP 原則就會偵測到這種敏感資訊類型：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5813">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-5814">函數  `Func_hungary_eu_ssn_or_equivalent` 會找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5814">The function  `Func_hungary_eu_ssn_or_equivalent` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-5815">找到來自的關鍵字  `Keywords_hungary_eu_ssn_or_equivalent` 。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5815">A keyword from  `Keywords_hungary_eu_ssn_or_equivalent` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="94f34-5816">當鄰近性300個字元以內時，DLP 原則就會偵測到這種敏感資訊類型的信賴度。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5816">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-5817">函數  `Func_hungary_eu_ssn_or_equivalent` 會找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5817">The function  `Func_hungary_eu_ssn_or_equivalent` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Hungarian Social Security Number (TAJ) -->
      <Entity id="0de78315-9537-47f5-95ab-b3e77eba3993" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_hungary_eu_ssn_or_equivalent" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_hungary_eu_ssn_or_equivalent" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_hungary_eu_ssn_or_equivalent" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="hungary-tax-identification-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-5837">匈牙利納稅識別號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5837">Hungary tax identification number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="94f34-5838">此機密資訊類型僅可用於下列專案：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5838">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-5839">資料遺失防護原則</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5839">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-5840">通訊相容性原則</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5840">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-5841">資訊管理</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5841">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-5842">記錄管理</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5842">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-5843">Microsoft cloud app security</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5843">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-5844">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5844">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-5845">10位數，不含空格或分隔符號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5845">10 digits with no spaces or delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-5846">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5846">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-5847">10位數：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5847">10 digits:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-5848">一個位數，必須是 "8"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5848">One digit that must be "8"</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-5849">八位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5849">Eight digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-5850">一個檢查碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5850">One check digit</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-5851">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5851">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-5852">是</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5852">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-5853">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5853">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-5854">當鄰近性300個字元以內時，DLP 原則就會偵測到這種敏感資訊類型：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5854">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-5855">函數  `Func_hungary_eu_tax_file_number` 會找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5855">The function  `Func_hungary_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-5856">找到來自的關鍵字  `Keywords_hungary_eu_tax_file_number` 。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5856">A keyword from  `Keywords_hungary_eu_tax_file_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="94f34-5857">當鄰近性300個字元以內時，DLP 原則就會偵測到這種敏感資訊類型的信賴度。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5857">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-5858">函數  `Func_hungary_eu_tax_file_number` 會找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5858">The function  `Func_hungary_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Hungary Tax Identification Number -->
      <Entity id="ede42eb4-59d9-49eb-9603-d7853fbda91d" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_hungary_eu_tax_file_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_hungary_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_hungary_eu_tax_file_number" />
          <Any minMatches="0" maxMatches="0">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_hungary_eu_telephone_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_hungary_eu_mobile_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="hungary-value-added-tax-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-5884">匈牙利增值的納稅號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5884">Hungary value added tax number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="94f34-5885">此機密資訊類型僅可用於下列專案：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5885">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-5886">資料遺失防護原則</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5886">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-5887">通訊相容性原則</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5887">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-5888">資訊管理</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5888">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-5889">記錄管理</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5889">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-5890">Microsoft cloud app security</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5890">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-5891">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5891">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-5892">10個字元的字母數位模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5892">10 character alphanumeric pattern</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-5893">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5893">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-5894">10個字元的字母數位模式：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5894">10 character alphanumeric pattern:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-5895">兩個字母-HU 或 hu</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5895">two letters - HU or hu</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-5896">選擇性空格</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5896">optional space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-5897">八位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5897">eight digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-5898">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5898">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-5899">是</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5899">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-5900">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5900">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-5901">當鄰近性300個字元以內時，DLP 原則就會偵測到這種敏感資訊類型：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5901">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-5902">函數 Func_hungarian_value_added_tax_number 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5902">The function Func_hungarian_value_added_tax_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-5903">會找到來自 Keywords_hungarian_value_added_tax_number 的關鍵字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5903">A keyword from Keywords_hungarian_value_added_tax_number is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-5904">當鄰近性300個字元以內時，DLP 原則就會偵測到這種敏感資訊類型的信賴度。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5904">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-5905">函數 Func_hungarian_value_added_tax_number 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5905">The function Func_hungarian_value_added_tax_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Hungarian Value Added Tax Number -->
      <Entity id="976349a0-683b-477a-90f8-ff0a220d5592" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_hungarian_value_added_tax_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_hungarian_value_added_tax_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_hungarian_value_added_tax_number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="india-permanent-account-number-pan"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-5919"> (平移) 的印度永久帳戶號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5919">India permanent account number (PAN)</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-5920">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5920">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-5921">10個字母或數位</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5921">10 letters or digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-5922">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5922">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-5923">10個字母或數位：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5923">10 letters or digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-5924">不區分大小寫的 (三個字母) </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5924">Three letters (not case-sensitive)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-5925">C、P、H、F、A、T、B、L、J、G (不區分大小寫的字母) </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5925">A letter in C, P, H, F, A, T, B, L, J, G (not case-sensitive)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-5926">一個字母</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5926">A letter</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-5927">四位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5927">Four digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-5928">字母檢查碼字母</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5928">A letter that is an alphabetic check digit</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-5929">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5929">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-5930">否</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5930">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-5931">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5931">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-5932">當鄰近性300個字元以內時，DLP 原則就會偵測到這種敏感資訊類型：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5932">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-5933">正則運算式 Regex_india_permanent_account_number 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5933">The regular expression Regex_india_permanent_account_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-5934">會找到來自 Keyword_india_permanent_account_number 的關鍵字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5934">A keyword from Keyword_india_permanent_account_number is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-5935">DLP 原則在接近300個字元以內時，偵測到此敏感資訊類型的信賴度很低：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5935">A DLP policy has low confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-5936">正則運算式 Regex_india_permanent_account_number 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5936">The regular expression Regex_india_permanent_account_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>


```xml
      <!-- India Permanent Account Number -->
      <Entity id="2602bfee-9bb0-47a5-a7a6-2bf3053e2804" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_india_permanent_account_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_india_permanent_account_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Version minEngineVersion="15.20.3520.000">
          <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
            <IdMatch idRef="Regex_india_permanent_account_number" />
          </Pattern>
        </Version>
      </Entity>
```

#### <a name="keyword_india_permanent_account_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-5938">Keyword_india_permanent_account_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5938">Keyword_india_permanent_account_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-5939">永久帳戶號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5939">Permanent Account Number</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-5940">泛</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5940">PAN</span></span> 
   
## <a name="india-unique-identification-aadhaar-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-5941">印度唯一識別碼 (Aadhaar) 號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5941">India unique identification (Aadhaar) number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-5942">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5942">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-5943">12位數包含選擇性空格或短杠</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5943">12 digits containing optional spaces or dashes</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-5944">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5944">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-5945">12位數：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5945">12 digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-5946">不是0或1的數位</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5946">A digit which is not 0 or 1</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-5947">三位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5947">Three digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-5948">選擇性的空格或破折號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5948">An optional space or dash</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-5949">四位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5949">Four digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-5950">選擇性的空格或破折號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5950">An optional space or dash</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-5951">最後一個數位，也就是檢查碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5951">The final digit, which is the check digit</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-5952">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5952">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-5953">是</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5953">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-5954">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5954">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-5955">當鄰近性300個字元以內時，DLP 原則就會偵測到這種敏感資訊類型：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5955">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-5956">函數 Func_india_aadhaar 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5956">The function Func_india_aadhaar finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-5957">會找到來自 Keyword_india_aadhar 的關鍵字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5957">A keyword from Keyword_india_aadhar is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-5958">校驗和通過。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5958">The checksum passes.</span></span>
- 
<span data-ttu-id="94f34-5959">當鄰近性300個字元以內時，DLP 原則就會偵測到這種敏感資訊類型的信賴度。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5959">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-5960">函數 Func_india_aadhaar 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5960">The function Func_india_aadhaar finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-5961">校驗和通過。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5961">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- India Unique Identification (Aadhaar) number -->
<Entity id="1ca46b29-76f5-4f46-9383-cfa15e91048f" recommendedConfidence="85" patternsProximity="300">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
     <IdMatch idRef="Func_india_aadhaar"/>
     <Match idRef="Keyword_india_aadhar"/>
  </Pattern>
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
     <IdMatch idRef="Func_india_aadhaar"/>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```
### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-5962">關鍵字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5962">Keywords</span></span>
   
#### <a name="keyword_india_aadhar"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-5963">Keyword_india_aadhar</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5963">Keyword_india_aadhar</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-5964">aadhaar</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5964">aadhaar</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-5965">aadhar</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5965">aadhar</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-5966">aadhar#</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5966">aadhar#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-5967">Uid</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5967">uid</span></span>
