## <a name="indonesia-identity-card-ktp-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-5970">印尼身分識別卡 (KTP) 號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5970">Indonesia identity card (KTP) number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-5971">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5971">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-5972">包含選用句點的16位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5972">16 digits containing optional periods</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-5973">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5973">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-5974">16位數：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5974">16 digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-5975">兩位數的省碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5975">Two-digit province code</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-5976">期間 (選用) </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5976">A period (optional)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-5977">兩位數攝政或城市碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5977">Two-digit regency or city code</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-5978">兩位數的 subdistrict 程式碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5978">Two-digit subdistrict code</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-5979">期間 (選用) </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5979">A period (optional)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-5980">DDMMYY 格式的六位數（出生日期）</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5980">Six digits in the format DDMMYY, which are the date of birth</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-5981">期間 (選用) </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5981">A period (optional)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-5982">四位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5982">Four digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-5983">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5983">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-5984">否</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5984">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-5985">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5985">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-5986">當鄰近性300個字元以內時，DLP 原則就會偵測到這種敏感資訊類型：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5986">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-5987">正則運算式 Regex_indonesia_id_card 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5987">The regular expression Regex_indonesia_id_card finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-5988">會找到來自 Keyword_indonesia_id_card 的關鍵字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5988">A keyword from Keyword_indonesia_id_card is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Indonesia Identity Card (KTP) Number -->
<Entity id="da68fdb0-f383-4981-8c86-82689d3b7d55" recommendedConfidence="85" patternsProximity="300">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
     <IdMatch idRef="Regex_indonesia_id_card"/>
     <Match idRef="Keyword_indonesia_id_card"/>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-5989">關鍵字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5989">Keywords</span></span>
   
#### <a name="keyword_indonesia_id_card"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-5990">Keyword_indonesia_id_card</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5990">Keyword_indonesia_id_card</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-5991">Ktp</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5991">KTP</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-5992">Kartu Tanda Penduduk</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5992">Kartu Tanda Penduduk</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-5993">Nomor Induk Kependudukan</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5993">Nomor Induk Kependudukan</span></span> 
   
## <a name="international-banking-account-number-iban"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-5994"> (IBAN) 的國際銀行帳戶號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5994">International banking account number (IBAN)</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-5995">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5995">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-5996">國家/地區碼 (兩個字母) 加上檢查位數 (兩位數) 加上 bban 號 (最多30個字元) </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5996">Country code (two letters) plus check digits (two digits) plus bban number (up to 30 characters)</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-5997">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5997">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-5998">模式必須包含下列各項：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5998">Pattern must include all of the following:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-5999">兩個字母的國家/地區碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-5999">Two-letter country code</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-6000">兩個檢查碼位數 (後接一個選擇性的空格) </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6000">Two check digits (followed by an optional space)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-6001">1-7 四個字母或數位的群組可以以空格分隔 () </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6001">1-7 groups of four letters or digits (can be separated by spaces)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-6002">1-3 個字母或數位</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6002">1-3 letters or digits</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-6003">每個國家/地區的格式稍有不同。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6003">The format for each country is slightly different.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="94f34-6004">IBAN 敏感資訊類型涵蓋下列60個國家/地區：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6004">The IBAN sensitive information type covers these 60 countries:</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-6005">ad，ae，al，at，az，ba，a，bg，bh，ch，cr，cy，cz，de，深色，do，ee，es，es，fo，fr，gb，ge，gi，gl，gr，hr，hu，ie，il，為，it，kw，kz，lb，li，lt，lu，lv，mt，mu，nl-nl，no，pl，mt，ro，rs-232c，tn，tr，vg</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6005">ad, ae, al, at, az, ba, be, bg, bh, ch, cr, cy, cz, de, dk, do, ee, es, fi, fo, fr, gb, ge, gi, gl, gr, hr, hu, ie, il, is, it, kw, kz, lb, li, lt, lu, lv, mc, md, me, mk, mr, mt, mu, nl, no, pl, pt, ro, rs, sa, se, si, sk, sm, tn, tr, vg</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-6006">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6006">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-6007">是</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6007">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-6008">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6008">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-6009">當鄰近性300個字元以內時，DLP 原則就會偵測到這種敏感資訊類型：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6009">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-6010">函數 Func_iban 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6010">The function Func_iban finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-6011">校驗和通過。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6011">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
<Entity id="e7dc4711-11b7-4cb0-b88b-2c394a771f0e" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_iban" />
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-6012">關鍵字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6012">Keywords</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-6013">無</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6013">None</span></span>

   
## <a name="international-classification-of-diseases-icd-10-cm"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-6014">國際分類的疾病 (ICD-10-釐米) </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6014">International classification of diseases (ICD-10-CM)</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-6015">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6015">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-6016">Dictionary</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6016">Dictionary</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-6017">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6017">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-6018">關鍵字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6018">Keyword</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-6019">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6019">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-6020">否</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6020">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-6021">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6021">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-6022">當鄰近性300個字元以內時，DLP 原則就會偵測到這種敏感資訊類型：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6022">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-6023">會找到來自 Dictionary_icd_10_updated 的關鍵字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6023">A keyword from Dictionary_icd_10_updated is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-6024">會找到來自 Dictionary_icd_10_codes 的關鍵字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6024">A keyword from Dictionary_icd_10_codes is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-6025">當鄰近性300個字元以內時，DLP 原則就會偵測到這種敏感資訊類型的信賴度。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6025">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-6026">會找到 Dictionary_icd_10_ 更新的關鍵字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6026">A keyword from Dictionary_icd_10_ updated is found.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- ICD-10 CM -->
      <Entity id="3356946c-6bb7-449b-b253-6ffa419c0ce7" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Dictionary_icd_10_updated" />
          <Match idRef="Dictionary_icd_10_codes" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Dictionary_icd_10_updated" />
        </Pattern>

```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-6027">關鍵字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6027">Keywords</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-6028">Dictionary_icd_10_updated 關鍵字字典中的任何字詞，都是以 [國際分類的疾病、第十個修訂版本、臨床修改 (icd-10 釐米) ](https://go.microsoft.com/fwlink/?linkid=852604)為基礎。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6028">Any term from the Dictionary_icd_10_updated keyword dictionary, which is based on the [International Classification of Diseases, Tenth Revision, Clinical Modification (ICD-10-CM)](https://go.microsoft.com/fwlink/?linkid=852604).</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="94f34-6029">這種類型只會尋找字詞，而不是保險碼。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6029">This type looks only for the term, not the insurance codes.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-6030">Dictionary_icd_10_codes 關鍵字字典中的任何字詞，都是以 [國際分類的疾病、第十個修訂版本、臨床修改 (icd-10 釐米) ](https://go.microsoft.com/fwlink/?linkid=852604)為基礎。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6030">Any term from the Dictionary_icd_10_codes keyword dictionary, which is based on the [International Classification of Diseases, Tenth Revision, Clinical Modification (ICD-10-CM)](https://go.microsoft.com/fwlink/?linkid=852604).</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="94f34-6031">這種類型只會查看保險業代碼，而不是描述。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6031">This type looks only for insurance codes, not the description.</span></span>

## <a name="international-classification-of-diseases-icd-9-cm"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-6032">疾病 (ICD-9 釐米) 的國際分類</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6032">International classification of diseases (ICD-9-CM)</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-6033">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6033">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-6034">Dictionary</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6034">Dictionary</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-6035">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6035">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-6036">關鍵字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6036">Keyword</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-6037">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6037">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-6038">否</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6038">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-6039">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6039">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-6040">當鄰近性300個字元以內時，DLP 原則就會偵測到這種敏感資訊類型：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6040">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-6041">會找到來自 Dictionary_icd_9_updated 的關鍵字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6041">A keyword from Dictionary_icd_9_updated is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-6042">會找到來自 Dictionary_icd_9_codes 的關鍵字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6042">A keyword from Dictionary_icd_9_codes is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-6043">當鄰近性300個字元以內時，DLP 原則就會偵測到這種敏感資訊類型的信賴度。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6043">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-6044">會找到來自 Dictionary_icd_9_updated 的關鍵字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6044">A keyword from Dictionary_icd_9_updated is found.</span></span>

```xml
    <Entity id="fa3f9c74-ee07-4c52-b5f2-085d6b2c0ec4" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Dictionary_icd_9_updated" />
          <Match idRef="Dictionary_icd_9_codes" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Dictionary_icd_9_updated" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-6045">關鍵字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6045">Keywords</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-6046">Dictionary_icd_9_updated 關鍵字字典中的任何字詞，都是以 [國際分類的疾病、第九份版本、臨床修改 (icd-9 釐米) ](https://go.microsoft.com/fwlink/?linkid=852605)為基礎。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6046">Any term from the Dictionary_icd_9_updated keyword dictionary, which is based on the [International Classification of Diseases,Ninth Revision, Clinical Modification (ICD-9-CM)](https://go.microsoft.com/fwlink/?linkid=852605).</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="94f34-6047">這種類型只會尋找字詞，而不是保險碼。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6047">This type looks only for the term, not the insurance codes.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-6048">Dictionary_icd_9_codes 關鍵字字典中的任何字詞，都是以 [國際分類的疾病、第九份版本、臨床修改 (icd-9 釐米) ](https://go.microsoft.com/fwlink/?linkid=852605)為基礎。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6048">Any term from the Dictionary_icd_9_codes keyword dictionary, which is based on the [International Classification of Diseases,Ninth Revision, Clinical Modification (ICD-9-CM)](https://go.microsoft.com/fwlink/?linkid=852605).</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="94f34-6049">這種類型只會查看保險業代碼，而不是描述。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6049">This type looks only for insurance codes, not the description.</span></span>

## <a name="ip-address"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-6050">IP 位址</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6050">IP address</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-6051">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6051">Format</span></span>

#### <a name="ipv4"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-6052">IPv4：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6052">IPv4:</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="94f34-6053">用於格式化 (期間的複雜模式) 及未格式化 (不) IPv4 位址的版本</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6053">Complex pattern that accounts for formatted (periods) and unformatted (no periods) versions of the IPv4 addresses</span></span>

#### <a name="ipv6"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-6054">IPv6：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6054">IPv6:</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="94f34-6055">IPv6 數位格式的複雜模式，其中包含冒號 () </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6055">Complex pattern that accounts for formatted IPv6 numbers (which include colons)</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-6056">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6056">Pattern</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-6057">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6057">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-6058">否</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6058">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-6059">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6059">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-6060">針對 IPv6，當鄰近300個字元以內時，DLP 原則就會偵測到這種敏感資訊類型的高可信度：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6060">For IPv6, a DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-6061">正則運算式 Regex_ipv6_address 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6061">The regular expression Regex_ipv6_address finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-6062">找不到 Keyword_ipaddress 的關鍵字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6062">No keyword from Keyword_ipaddress is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-6063">針對 IPv4，如果接近300個字元以內，則 DLP 原則偵測到此敏感資訊類型的置信量是95%：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6063">For IPv4, a DLP policy is 95% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-6064">正則運算式 Regex_ipv4_address 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6064">The regular expression Regex_ipv4_address finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-6065">會找到來自 Keyword_ipaddress 的關鍵字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6065">A keyword from Keyword_ipaddress is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-6066">針對 IPv6，如果接近300個字元以內，則 DLP 原則偵測到此敏感資訊類型的置信量是95%：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6066">For IPv6, a DLP policy is 95% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-6067">正則運算式 Regex_ipv6_address 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6067">The regular expression Regex_ipv6_address finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-6068">找不到 Keyword_ipaddress 的關鍵字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6068">No keyword from Keyword_ipaddress is found.</span></span>

```xml
    <!-- IP Address -->
    <Entity id="1daa4ad5-e2dd-4ca4-a788-54722c09efb2" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
        <IdMatch idRef="Regex_ipv6_address" />
        <Any minMatches="0" maxMatches="0">
          <Match idRef="Keyword_ipaddress" />
        </Any>
      </Pattern>
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="95">
        <IdMatch idRef="Regex_ipv4_address" />
        <Any minMatches="1">
          <Match idRef="Keyword_ipaddress" />
        </Any>
      </Pattern>
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="95">
        <IdMatch idRef="Regex_ipv6_address" />
        <Any minMatches="1">
          <Match idRef="Keyword_ipaddress" />
        </Any>
      </Pattern>
    </Entity>
```

- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-6071">IP (此關鍵字區分大小寫) </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6071">IP (this keyword is case-sensitive)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-6072">ip 位址</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6072">ip address</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-6073">ip 位址</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6073">ip addresses</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-6074">網際網路通訊協定</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6074">internet protocol</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-6075">IP-כתובתה</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6075">IP-כתובת ה</span></span> 

## <a name="ireland-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-6076">愛爾蘭駕照編號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6076">Ireland driver's license number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-6077">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6077">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-6078">六位數後接四個字母</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6078">Six digits followed by four letters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-6079">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6079">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-6080">六位數和四個字母：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6080">Six digits and four letters:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-6081">六位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6081">Six digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-6082">四個字母 (不區分大小寫) </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6082">Four letters (not case-sensitive)</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-6083">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6083">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-6084">否</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6084">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-6085">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6085">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-6086">當鄰近性300個字元以內時，DLP 原則就會偵測到這種敏感資訊類型的信賴度。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6086">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-6087">正則運算式會  `Regex_ireland_eu_driver's_license_number` 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6087">The regular expression  `Regex_ireland_eu_driver's_license_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-6088">`Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number`找到或的關鍵字 `Keywords_ireland_eu_driver's_license_number` 。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6088">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` or `Keywords_ireland_eu_driver's_license_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Ireland Driver's License Number -->
      <Entity id="e01bccd9-eb4d-414f-ace1-e9b6a4c4a2ca" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_ireland_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_ireland_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="ireland-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-6212">愛爾蘭護照號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6212">Ireland passport number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-6213">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6213">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-6214">兩個字母或數位後接7位數，不含空格或分隔符號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6214">Two letters or digits followed by seven digits with no spaces or delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-6215">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6215">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-6216">兩個字母或數位後接7位數：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6216">Two letters or digits followed by seven digits:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-6217">兩位數的數位或字母 (不區分大小寫) </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6217">Two digits or letters (not case-sensitive)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-6218">七位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6218">Seven digits</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-6219">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6219">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-6220">否</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6220">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-6221">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6221">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-6222">當鄰近性300個字元以內時，DLP 原則就會偵測到這種敏感資訊類型：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6222">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-6223">正則運算式會  `Regex_ireland_eu_passport_number` 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6223">The regular expression  `Regex_ireland_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-6224">`Keywords_eu_passport_number`找到或的關鍵字 `Keywords_ireland_eu_passport_number` 。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6224">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_ireland_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-6225">正則運算式 `Regex_ireland_eu_passport_date` 會以 DD MMM/MMM YYYY 的格式尋找日期 (範例-01 BEA/1988) 或找到關鍵字。 `Keywords_eu_passport_date`</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6225">The regular expression `Regex_ireland_eu_passport_date` finds date in the format DD MMM/MMM YYYY (Example - 01 BEA/MAY 1988) or a keyword from `Keywords_eu_passport_date` is found</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-6226">當鄰近性300個字元以內時，DLP 原則就會偵測到這種敏感資訊類型的信賴度。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6226">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-6227">正則運算式會  `Regex_ireland_eu_passport_number` 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6227">The regular expression  `Regex_ireland_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-6228">`Keywords_eu_passport_number`找到或的關鍵字 `Keywords_ireland_eu_passport_number` 。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6228">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_ireland_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span>
    
```xml
      <!-- Ireland Passport Number -->
      <Entity id="a2130f27-9ee2-4103-84f9-a6b1ee7d0cbf" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_ireland_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_ireland_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Regex_ireland_eu_passport_date" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_date" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_ireland_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_ireland_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="ireland-personal-public-service-pps-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-6252">愛爾蘭個人公開服務 (PPS) 號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6252">Ireland personal public service (PPS) number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-6253">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6253">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-6254">舊格式 (直到2012年12月31日) ：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6254">Old format (until 31 December 2012):</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-6255">七位數後接1-2 個字母</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6255">seven digits followed by 1-2 letters</span></span> 

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-6256">新格式 (1 月2013日和之後) ：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6256">New format (1 January 2013 and after):</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-6257">七位數後接兩個字母</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6257">seven digits followed by two letters</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-6258">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6258">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-6259">舊格式 (直到2012年12月31日) ：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6259">Old format (until 31 December 2012):</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-6260">七位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6260">seven digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-6261">一個至兩個字母 (不區分大小寫) </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6261">one to two letters (not case-sensitive)</span></span> 

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-6262">新格式 (1 月2013日和之後) ：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6262">New format (1 January 2013 and after):</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-6263">七位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6263">seven digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-6264">信 (不區分大小寫) （字母檢查碼）</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6264">a letter (not case-sensitive) which is an alphabetic check digit</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-6265">範圍 A-I 或 "W" 中的選用字母</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6265">An optional letter in the range A-I, or “W”</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-6266">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6266">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-6267">是</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6267">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-6268">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6268">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-6269">當鄰近性300個字元以內時，DLP 原則就會偵測到這種敏感資訊類型：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6269">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-6270">函數 Func_ireland_pps 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6270">The function Func_ireland_pps finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-6271">會找到來自 Keywords_ireland_eu_national_id_card 的關鍵字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6271">A keyword from Keywords_ireland_eu_national_id_card is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-6272">校驗和通過。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6272">The checksum passes.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-6273">DLP 原則在接近300個字元以內時，偵測到此敏感資訊類型的信賴度很低：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6273">A DLP policy has low confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-6274">函數 Func_ireland_pps 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6274">The function Func_ireland_pps finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-6275">校驗和通過。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6275">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Ireland Personal Public Service (PPS) Number -->
      <Entity id="1cdb674d-c19a-4fcf-9f4b-7f56cc87345a" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85" relaxProximity="true">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_ireland_pps" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_ireland_eu_national_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_ireland_pps" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-6276">關鍵字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6276">Keywords</span></span>

## <a name="israel-bank-account-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-6320">以色列銀行帳戶號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6320">Israel bank account number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-6321">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6321">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-6322">13位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6322">13 digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-6323">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6323">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-6324">格式 化：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6324">Formatted:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-6325">兩位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6325">two digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-6326">虛線</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6326">a dash</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-6327">三位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6327">three digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-6328">虛線</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6328">a dash</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-6329">八位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6329">eight digits</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-6330">非</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6330">Unformatted:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-6331">13個連續數位</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6331">13 consecutive digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-6332">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6332">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-6333">否</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6333">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-6334">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6334">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-6335">當鄰近性300個字元以內時，DLP 原則就會偵測到這種敏感資訊類型的信賴度。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6335">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-6336">正則運算式 Regex_israel_bank_account_number 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6336">The regular expression Regex_israel_bank_account_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-6337">會找到來自 Keyword_israel_bank_account_number 的關鍵字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6337">A keyword from Keyword_israel_bank_account_number is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Israel Bank Account Number -->
<Entity id="7d08b2ff-a0b9-437f-957c-aeddbf9b2b25" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
    <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Regex_israel_bank_account_number" />
        <Any minMatches="1">
          <Match idRef="Keyword_israel_bank_account_number" />
        </Any>
    </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-6338">關鍵字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6338">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_israel_bank_account_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-6339">Keyword_israel_bank_account_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6339">Keyword_israel_bank_account_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-6340">銀行帳戶號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6340">Bank Account Number</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-6341">銀行帳戶</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6341">Bank Account</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-6342">帳戶號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6342">Account Number</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-6343">מספר חשבון בנק</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6343">מספר חשבון בנק</span></span> 
   
## <a name="israel-national-identification-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-6344">以色列國身分識別號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6344">Israel national identification number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-6345">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6345">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-6346">九位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6346">nine digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-6347">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6347">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-6348">九個連續數位</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6348">nine consecutive digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-6349">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6349">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-6350">是</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6350">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-6351">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6351">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-6352">當鄰近性300個字元以內時，DLP 原則就會偵測到這種敏感資訊類型的信賴度。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6352">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-6353">函數 Func_israeli_national_id_number 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6353">The function Func_israeli_national_id_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-6354">會找到來自 Keyword_Israel_National_ID 的關鍵字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6354">A keyword from Keyword_Israel_National_ID is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-6355">校驗和通過。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6355">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Israel National ID Number -->
<Entity id="e05881f5-1db1-418c-89aa-a3ac5c5277ee" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
    <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_israeli_national_id_number" />
        <Any minMatches="1">
          <Match idRef="Keyword_Israel_National_ID" />
        </Any>
    </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-6356">關鍵字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6356">Keywords</span></span>

-   <span data-ttu-id="94f34-6360">מספר זיהוי ישר אלי</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6360">מספר זיהוי ישר אלי</span></span>      
-   <span data-ttu-id="94f34-6361">זהותישר אלית</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6361">זהותישר אלית</span></span>
-   <span data-ttu-id="94f34-6362">هو ية اسرائيل ية عدد</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6362">هو ية اسرائيل ية عدد</span></span>
-   <span data-ttu-id="94f34-6363">هوية إسرائ يلية</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6363">هوية إسرائ يلية</span></span>
-   <span data-ttu-id="94f34-6364">رقم الهوية</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6364">رقم الهوية</span></span>
-   <span data-ttu-id="94f34-6365">عدد هوية فريدة من نوعها</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6365">عدد هوية فريدة من نوعها</span></span>
-   <span data-ttu-id="94f34-6366">idnumber#</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6366">idnumber#</span></span>
-   <span data-ttu-id="94f34-6367">識別碼號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6367">id number</span></span>
-   <span data-ttu-id="94f34-6368">identity no</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6368">identity no</span></span>        
-   <span data-ttu-id="94f34-6369">identitynumber#</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6369">identitynumber#</span></span>
-   <span data-ttu-id="94f34-6370">身分識別號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6370">identity number</span></span>
-   <span data-ttu-id="94f34-6371">israeliidentitynumber</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6371">israeliidentitynumber</span></span>       
-   <span data-ttu-id="94f34-6372">個人識別碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6372">personal id</span></span>
-   <span data-ttu-id="94f34-6373">唯一識別碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6373">unique id</span></span>  

   
## <a name="italy-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-6374">義大利駕照編號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6374">Italy driver's license number</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-6375">此機密資訊類型的實體包含在歐盟駕駛執照號碼的敏感資訊類型中，並可做為獨立機密資訊類型實體。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6375">This sensitive information type entity is included in the EU Driver's License Number sensitive information type and is available as a stand-alone sensitive information type entity.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-6376">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6376">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-6377">10個字母和數位的組合</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6377">a combination of 10 letters and digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-6378">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6378">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-6379">10個字母和數位的組合：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6379">a combination of 10 letters and digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-6380">一個字母 (不區分大小寫) </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6380">one letter (not case-sensitive)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-6381">字母 "A" 或 "V" (不區分大小寫) </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6381">the letter "A" or "V" (not case-sensitive)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-6382">七位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6382">seven digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-6383">一個字母 (不區分大小寫) </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6383">one letter (not case-sensitive)</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-6384">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6384">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-6385">否</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6385">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-6386">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6386">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-6387">當鄰近性300個字元以內時，DLP 原則就會偵測到這種敏感資訊類型的信賴度。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6387">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-6388">正則運算式會 `Regex_italy_drivers_license_number` 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6388">The regular expression `Regex_italy_drivers_license_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-6389">`Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number`找到或的關鍵字 `Keyword_italy_drivers_license_number` 。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6389">A keyword from `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` or `Keyword_italy_drivers_license_number` is found.</span></span>

```xml
    <!-- Italy Driver's license Number -->
    <Entity id="97d6244f-9157-41bd-8e0c-9d669a5c4d71" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Regex_italy_drivers_license_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keyword_italy_drivers_license_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
    </Entity>
```

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-6523">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6523">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-6524">指定之模式中字母和數位的16個字元組合</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6524">a 16-character combination of letters and digits in the specified pattern</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-6525">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6525">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-6526">字母和數位的16個字元的組合：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6526">A 16-character combination of letters and digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-6527">與系列名稱中的前三個雙子音相對應的三個字母</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6527">three letters that correspond to the first three consonants in the family name</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-6528">與名字中的第一個、第三個和第四個雙子音相對應的三個字母</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6528">three letters that correspond to the first, third, and fourth consonants in the first name</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-6529">與出生年份的最後一個數位相對應的兩位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6529">two digits that correspond to the last digits of the birth year</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-6530">對應至出生月份之字母的一個字母，在字母順序中使用字母，但是只會使用字母 A 到 E、H、L、M、P、P、R (所以，一月份為 A，10月是 R) </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6530">one letter that corresponds to the letter for the month of birth—letters are used in alphabetical order, but only the letters A to E, H, L, M, P, R to T are used (so, January is A and October is R)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-6531">兩位數的出生月份天數，為了區別 genders，40會新增到女士的出生日。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6531">two digits that correspond to the day of the month of birth—in order to differentiate between genders, 40 is added to the day of birth for women</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-6532">相對於 municipality 人員專屬之地區代碼的四位數，在國外國家/地區使用 (全國的碼) </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6532">four digits that correspond to the area code specific to the municipality where the person was born (country-wide codes are used for foreign countries)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-6533">一個同位數位</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6533">one parity digit</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-6534">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6534">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-6535">是</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6535">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-6536">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6536">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-6537">當鄰近性300個字元以內時，DLP 原則就會偵測到這種敏感資訊類型：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6537">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-6538">函數  `Func_italy_eu_national_id_card` 會找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6538">The function  `Func_italy_eu_national_id_card` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-6539">找到來自的關鍵字  `Keywords_italy_eu_national_id_card` 。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6539">A keyword from  `Keywords_italy_eu_national_id_card` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="94f34-6540">當鄰近性300個字元以內時，DLP 原則就會偵測到這種敏感資訊類型的信賴度。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6540">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-6541">函數  `Func_italy_eu_national_id_card` 會找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6541">The function  `Func_italy_eu_national_id_card` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Italy Fiscal Code -->
      <Entity id="4cd79172-8da9-4ff5-9188-98b1e7e2eca6" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_italy_eu_national_id_card" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_italy_eu_national_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_italy_eu_national_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="italy-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-6576">義大利護照號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6576">Italy passport number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-6577">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6577">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-6578">兩個字母或數位後接7位數，不含空格或分隔符號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6578">two letters or digits followed by seven digits with no spaces or delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-6579">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6579">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-6580">兩個字母或數位後接7位數：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6580">two letters or digits followed by seven digits:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-6581">兩位數的數位或字母 (不區分大小寫) </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6581">two digits or letters (not case-sensitive)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-6582">七位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6582">seven digits</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-6583">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6583">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-6584">不適用</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6584">not applicable</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-6585">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6585">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-6586">當鄰近性300個字元以內時，DLP 原則就會偵測到這種敏感資訊類型：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6586">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-6587">正則運算式會  `Regex_italy_eu_passport_number` 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6587">The regular expression  `Regex_italy_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-6588">`Keywords_eu_passport_number`找到或的關鍵字 `Keywords_italy_eu_passport_number` 。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6588">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_italy_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-6589">正則運算式 `Regex_italy_eu_passport_date` 會以 DD MMM/MMM YYYY 的格式來找到日期。 (範例-01 GEN/JAN 1988) 或 `Keywords_eu_passport_date` 找到關鍵字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6589">The regular expression `Regex_italy_eu_passport_date` finds date in the format DD MMM/MMM YYYY (Example - 01 GEN/JAN 1988) or a keyword from `Keywords_eu_passport_date` is found</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-6590">當鄰近性300個字元以內時，DLP 原則就會偵測到這種敏感資訊類型的信賴度。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6590">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-6591">正則運算式會  `Regex_italy_eu_passport_number` 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6591">The regular expression  `Regex_italy_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-6592">`Keywords_eu_passport_number`找到或的關鍵字 `Keywords_italy_eu_passport_number` 。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6592">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_italy_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Italy Passport Number -->
      <Entity id="39811019-4750-445f-b26d-4c0e6c431544" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_italy_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_italy_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Regex_italy_eu_passport_date" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_date" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_italy_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_italy_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="italy-value-added-tax-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-6616">義大利值增加的納稅號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6616">Italy value added tax number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="94f34-6617">此機密資訊類型僅可用於下列專案：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6617">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-6618">資料遺失防護原則</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6618">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-6619">通訊相容性原則</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6619">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-6620">資訊管理</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6620">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-6621">記錄管理</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6621">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-6622">Microsoft cloud app security</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6622">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-6623">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6623">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-6624">13個字元的字母元字母模式，選用分隔符號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6624">13 character alphanumeric pattern with optional delimiters</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-6625">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6625">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-6626">13個字元的字母數位模式，具有選用的分隔符號：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6626">13 character alphanumeric pattern with optional delimiters:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-6627">I 或 i</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6627">I or i</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-6628">T 或 t</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6628">T or t</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-6629">選用空格、點、連字號或逗號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6629">optional space, dot, hyphen, or comma</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-6630">11位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6630">11 digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-6631">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6631">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-6632">是</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6632">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-6633">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6633">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-6634">當鄰近性300個字元以內時，DLP 原則就會偵測到這種敏感資訊類型：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6634">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-6635">函數 Func_italy_value_added_tax_number 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6635">The function Func_italy_value_added_tax_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-6636">會找到來自 Keywords_italy_value_added_tax_number 的關鍵字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6636">A keyword from Keywords_italy_value_added_tax_number is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-6637">當鄰近性300個字元以內時，DLP 原則就會偵測到這種敏感資訊類型的信賴度。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6637">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-6638">函數 Func_italy_value_added_tax_number 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6638">The function Func_italy_value_added_tax_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Italy Value Added Tax -->
      <Entity id="26a8cc07-2283-4a2a-ab1d-4ab643c4c67f" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_italy_value_added_tax_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_italy_value_added_tax_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_italy_value_added_tax_number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

#### <a name="keyword_italy_value_added_tax_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-6640">Keyword_italy_value_added_tax_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6640">Keyword_italy_value_added_tax_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-6641">加值稅號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6641">vat number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-6643">加值稅#</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6643">vat#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-6644">iva</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6644">iva</span></span>

## <a name="japan-bank-account-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-6646">日本銀行帳戶號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6646">Japan bank account number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-6647">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6647">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-6648">7或8位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6648">seven or eight digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-6649">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6649">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-6650">銀行帳戶號碼：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6650">bank account number:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-6651">7或8位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6651">seven or eight digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-6652">銀行帳戶分支程式碼：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6652">bank account branch code:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-6653">四位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6653">four digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-6654">一個空格或破折號 (選用) </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6654">a space or dash (optional)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-6655">三位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6655">three digits</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-6656">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6656">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-6657">否</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6657">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-6658">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6658">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-6659">當鄰近性300個字元以內時，DLP 原則就會偵測到這種敏感資訊類型：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6659">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-6660">函數 Func_jp_bank_account 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6660">The function Func_jp_bank_account finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-6661">會找到來自 Keyword_jp_bank_account 的關鍵字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6661">A keyword from Keyword_jp_bank_account is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-6662">下列其中一項為真：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6662">One of the following is true:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-6663">函數 Func_jp_bank_account_branch_code 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6663">The function Func_jp_bank_account_branch_code finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-6664">會找到來自 Keyword_jp_bank_branch_code 的關鍵字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6664">A keyword from Keyword_jp_bank_branch_code is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-6665">當鄰近性300個字元以內時，DLP 原則就會偵測到這種敏感資訊類型的信賴度。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6665">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-6666">函數 Func_jp_bank_account 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6666">The function Func_jp_bank_account finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-6667">會找到來自 Keyword_jp_bank_account 的關鍵字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6667">A keyword from Keyword_jp_bank_account is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Japan Bank Account Number -->
<Entity id="d354f95b-96ee-4b80-80bc-4377312b55bc" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
  <Version minEngineVersion="15.01.0131.000">
    <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_jp_bank_account" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_jp_bank_account" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Func_jp_bank_account_branch_code" />
            <Match idRef="Keyword_jp_bank_branch_code" />
          </Any>
      </Pattern>
  </Version>    
     <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_jp_bank_account" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_jp_bank_account" />
    </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="japan-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-6714">日本駕照編號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6714">Japan driver's license number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-6715">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6715">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-6716">12位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6716">12 digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-6717">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6717">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-6718">12個連續數位</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6718">12 consecutive digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-6719">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6719">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-6720">否</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6720">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-6721">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6721">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-6722">當鄰近性300個字元以內時，DLP 原則就會偵測到這種敏感資訊類型的信賴度。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6722">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-6723">函數 Func_jp_drivers_license_number 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6723">The function Func_jp_drivers_license_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-6724">會找到來自 Keyword_jp_drivers_license_number 的關鍵字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6724">A keyword from Keyword_jp_drivers_license_number is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Japan Driver's License Number -->
<Entity id="c6011143-d087-451c-8313-7f6d4aed2270" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
    <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_jp_drivers_license_number" />
        <Match idRef ="Keyword_jp_drivers_license_number" />
    </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-6725">關鍵字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6725">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_jp_drivers_license_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-6726">Keyword_jp_drivers_license_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6726">Keyword_jp_drivers_license_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-6727">driverlicense</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6727">driverlicense</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-6728">driverslicense</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6728">driverslicense</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-6729">driver'slicense</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6729">driver'slicense</span></span>

## <a name="japan-my-number---corporate"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-6762">日本我的號碼-公司</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6762">Japan My Number - Corporate</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="94f34-6763">此機密資訊類型僅可用於下列專案：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6763">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-6764">資料遺失防護原則</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6764">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-6765">通訊相容性原則</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6765">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-6766">資訊管理</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6766">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-6767">記錄管理</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6767">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-6768">Microsoft cloud app security</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6768">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-6769">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6769">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-6770">13位數數位</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6770">13-digit number</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-6771">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6771">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-6772">13位數數位：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6772">13-digit number:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-6773">一位數從1到9</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6773">one digit from one to nine</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-6774">12位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6774">12 digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-6775">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6775">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-6776">是</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6776">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-6777">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6777">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-6778">當鄰近性300個字元以內時，DLP 原則就會偵測到這種敏感資訊類型：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6778">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-6779">函數 Func_japanese_my_number_corporate 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6779">The function Func_japanese_my_number_corporate finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-6780">會找到來自 Keywords_japanese_my_number_corporate 的關鍵字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6780">A keyword from Keywords_japanese_my_number_corporate is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-6781">當鄰近性300個字元以內時，DLP 原則就會偵測到這種敏感資訊類型的信賴度。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6781">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-6782">函數 Func_japanese_my_number_corporate 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6782">The function Func_japanese_my_number_corporate finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Japanese My Number – Corporate -->
      <Entity id="9e0eaf79-ff20-4ffb-b3e4-e7368d5db6ff" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_japanese_my_number_corporate" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_japanese_my_number_corporate" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_japanese_my_number_corporate" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-6789">マイナンバーカード番號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6789">マイナンバーカード番号</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-6790">個人番號カード</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6790">個人番号カード</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-6791">個人識別番號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6791">個人識別番号</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-6792">個人識別ナンバー</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6792">個人識別ナンバー</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-6794">指定通知書</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6794">指定通知書</span></span>


## <a name="japan-my-number---personal"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-6795">日本我的號碼-個人</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6795">Japan My Number - Personal</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="94f34-6796">此機密資訊類型僅可用於下列專案：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6796">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-6797">資料遺失防護原則</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6797">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-6798">通訊相容性原則</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6798">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-6799">資訊管理</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6799">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-6800">記錄管理</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6800">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-6801">Microsoft cloud app security</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6801">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-6802">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6802">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-6803">12位數數位</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6803">12-digit number</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-6804">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6804">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-6805">12位數數位：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6805">12-digit number:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-6806">四位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6806">four digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-6807">選擇性的空格、點或連字號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6807">an optional space, dot, or hyphen</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-6808">四位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6808">four digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-6809">選擇性的空格、點或連字號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6809">an optional space, dot, or hyphen</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-6810">四位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6810">four digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-6811">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6811">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-6812">是</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6812">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-6813">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6813">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-6814">當鄰近性300個字元以內時，DLP 原則就會偵測到這種敏感資訊類型：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6814">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-6815">函數 Func_japanese_my_number_personal 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6815">The function Func_japanese_my_number_personal finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-6816">會找到來自 Keywords_japanese_my_number_personal 的關鍵字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6816">A keyword from Keywords_japanese_my_number_personal is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-6817">DLP 原則在接近300個字元以內時，偵測到此敏感資訊類型的信賴度很低：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6817">A DLP policy has low confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-6818">函數 Func_japanese_my_number_personal 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6818">The function Func_japanese_my_number_personal finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Japanese My Number – Personal -->
      <Entity id="98da8e66-7299-4ebd-9f82-c871ab37d3ef" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_japanese_my_number_personal" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_japanese_my_number_personal" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_japanese_my_number_personal" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-6828">個人識別番號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6828">個人識別番号</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-6829">個人識別ナンバー</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6829">個人識別ナンバー</span></span>

## <a name="japan-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-6831">日本護照號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6831">Japan passport number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-6832">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6832">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-6833">兩個字母后接7位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6833">two letters followed by seven digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-6834">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6834">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-6835">兩個字母 (不區分大小寫) 後接7位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6835">two letters (not case-sensitive) followed by seven digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-6836">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6836">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-6837">否</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6837">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-6838">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6838">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-6839">當鄰近性300個字元以內時，DLP 原則就會偵測到這種敏感資訊類型的信賴度。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6839">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-6840">函數 Func_jp_passport 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6840">The function Func_jp_passport finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-6841">會找到來自 Keyword_jp_passport 的關鍵字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6841">A keyword from Keyword_jp_passport is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Japan Passport Number -->
```
