## <a name="japan-residence-card-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-6858">日本住家電話卡號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6858">Japan residence card number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-6859">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6859">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-6860">12個字母和數位</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6860">12 letters and digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-6861">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6861">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-6862">12個字母和數位：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6862">12 letters and digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-6863">兩個字母 (不區分大小寫) </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6863">two letters (not case-sensitive)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-6864">八位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6864">eight digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-6865">兩個字母 (不區分大小寫) </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6865">two letters (not case-sensitive)</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-6866">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6866">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-6867">否</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6867">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-6868">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6868">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-6869">當鄰近性300個字元以內時，DLP 原則就會偵測到這種敏感資訊類型的信賴度。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6869">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-6870">正則運算式 Regex_jp_residence_card_number 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6870">The regular expression Regex_jp_residence_card_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-6871">會找到來自 Keyword_jp_residence_card_number 的關鍵字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6871">A keyword from Keyword_jp_residence_card_number is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!--Japan Residence Card Number-->
-<Entity id="ac36fef2-a289-4e2c-bb48-b02366e89fc0" recommendedConfidence="75" patternsProximity="300">
   -<Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
      <IdMatch idRef="Regex_jp_residence_card_number"/>
      <Match idRef="Keyword_jp_residence_card_number"/>
   </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-6872">關鍵字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6872">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_jp_residence_card_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-6873">Keyword_jp_residence_card_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6873">Keyword_jp_residence_card_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-6874">住家電話卡號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6874">Residence card number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-6875">不含住宅卡片</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6875">Residence card no</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-6876">住宅卡片#</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6876">Residence card #</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-6877">在留カード番號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6877">在留カード番号</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-6878">在留カード</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6878">在留カード</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-6879">在留番號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6879">在留番号</span></span>

## <a name="japan-resident-registration-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-6880">日本居民登記號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6880">Japan resident registration number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-6881">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6881">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-6882">11位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6882">11 digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-6883">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6883">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-6884">11個連續數位</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6884">11 consecutive digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-6885">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6885">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-6886">否</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6886">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-6887">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6887">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-6888">當鄰近性300個字元以內時，DLP 原則就會偵測到這種敏感資訊類型的信賴度。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6888">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-6889">函數 Func_jp_resident_registration_number 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6889">The function Func_jp_resident_registration_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-6890">會找到來自 Keyword_jp_resident_registration_number 的關鍵字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6890">A keyword from Keyword_jp_resident_registration_number is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Japan Resident Registration Number -->
<Entity id="01c1209b-6389-4faf-a5f8-3f7e13899652" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
    <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_jp_resident_registration_number" />
        <Match idRef ="Keyword_jp_resident_registration_number" />
    </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-6891">關鍵字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6891">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_jp_resident_registration_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-6892">Keyword_jp_resident_registration_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6892">Keyword_jp_resident_registration_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-6893">常駐登記編號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6893">Resident Registration Number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-6895">常駐登記編號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6895">Resident Registration No.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-6897">居民基本登錄否。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6897">Residents Basic Registry No.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-6898">基本居民收銀機 No。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6898">Basic Resident Register No.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-6902">外國人登録証</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6902">外国人登録証</span></span>

   
## <a name="japan-social-insurance-number-sin"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-6903">日本社交保險號碼 (SIN) </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6903">Japan social insurance number (SIN)</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-6904">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6904">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-6905">7-12 位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6905">7-12 digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-6906">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6906">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-6907">7-12 位數：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6907">7-12 digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-6908">四位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6908">four digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-6909">連字號 (選用) </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6909">a hyphen (optional)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-6910">六位數或</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6910">six digits OR</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-6911">7-12 連續位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6911">7-12 consecutive digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-6912">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6912">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-6913">否</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6913">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-6914">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6914">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-6915">當鄰近性300個字元以內時，DLP 原則就會偵測到這種敏感資訊類型：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6915">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-6916">函數 Func_jp_sin 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6916">The function Func_jp_sin finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-6917">會找到來自 Keyword_jp_sin 的關鍵字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6917">A keyword from Keyword_jp_sin is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-6918">當鄰近性300個字元以內時，DLP 原則就會偵測到這種敏感資訊類型的信賴度。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6918">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-6919">函數 Func_jp_sin_pre_1997 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6919">The function Func_jp_sin_pre_1997 finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-6920">會找到來自 Keyword_jp_sin 的關鍵字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6920">A keyword from Keyword_jp_sin is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Japan Social Insurance Number -->
<Entity id="c840e719-0896-45bb-84fd-1ed5c95e45ff" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
    <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_jp_sin" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_jp_sin" />
    </Pattern>
    <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_jp_sin_pre_1997" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_jp_sin" />
    </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="latvia-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-6941">拉脫維亞駕駛執照號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6941">Latvia driver's license number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-6942">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6942">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-6943">三個字母后接六位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6943">three letters followed by six digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-6944">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6944">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-6945">三個字母和六位數：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6945">three letters and six digits:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-6946">不區分大小寫的 (三個字母) </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6946">three letters (not case-sensitive)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-6947">六位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6947">six digits</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-6948">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6948">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-6949">否</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6949">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-6950">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6950">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-6951">當鄰近性300個字元以內時，DLP 原則就會偵測到這種敏感資訊類型的信賴度。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6951">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-6952">正則運算式會  `Regex_latvia_eu_driver's_license_number` 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6952">The regular expression  `Regex_latvia_eu_driver's_license_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-6953">`Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number`找到或的關鍵字 `Keywords_latvia_eu_driver's_license_number` 。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-6953">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` or `Keywords_latvia_eu_driver's_license_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Latvia Driver's License Number -->
      <Entity id="ec996de0-30f2-46b1-b192-4d2ff8805fa7" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_latvia_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_latvia_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-7076">autovadītāja apliecības</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-7076">autovadītāja apliecības</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-7077">vadītāja apliecība</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-7077">vadītāja apliecība</span></span>

## <a name="latvia-personal-code"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-7078">拉脫維亞個人程式碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-7078">Latvia personal code</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-7079">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-7079">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-7080">11位數和選擇性連字號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-7080">11 digits and an optional hyphen</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-7081">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-7081">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-7082">舊格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-7082">Old format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-7083">11位數和連字號：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-7083">11 digits and a hyphen:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-7084">對應至出生日期 (DDMMYY 的六位數) </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-7084">six digits that correspond to the birth date (DDMMYY)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-7085">連字號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-7085">a hyphen</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-7086">一個數位，對應至出生的世紀 ( "0"，第5個世紀，"1" 表示20世紀，而 "2" 表示21世紀) </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-7086">one digit that corresponds to the century of birth ("0" for 19th century, "1" for 20th century, and "2" for 21st century)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-7087">四位數（隨機產生）</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-7087">four digits, randomly generated</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-7088">新格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-7088">New format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-7089">11位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-7089">11 digits</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-7090">兩位數 "32"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-7090">Two digits "32"</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-7091">九位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-7091">Nine digits</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-7092">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-7092">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-7093">是</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-7093">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-7094">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-7094">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-7095">當鄰近性300個字元以內時，DLP 原則就會偵測到這種敏感資訊類型：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-7095">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-7096">函數  `Func_latvia_eu_national_id_card` 或正則運算式 `Regex_latvia_eu_national_id_card_new_format` 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-7096">The function  `Func_latvia_eu_national_id_card` or the regex `Regex_latvia_eu_national_id_card_new_format` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-7097">找到來自的關鍵字  `Keywords_latvia_eu_national_id_card` 。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-7097">A keyword from  `Keywords_latvia_eu_national_id_card` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="94f34-7098">當鄰近性300個字元以內時，DLP 原則就會偵測到這種敏感資訊類型的信賴度。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-7098">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-7099">函數  `Func_latvia_eu_national_id_card` 或正則運算式 `Regex_latvia_eu_national_id_card_new_format` 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-7099">The function  `Func_latvia_eu_national_id_card` or the regex `Regex_latvia_eu_national_id_card_new_format` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Latvia Personal Code -->
      <Entity id="03fcf763-27c2-49ed-9422-2641c6c895c9" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_latvia_eu_national_id_card" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_latvia_eu_national_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_latvia_eu_national_id_card" />
          <Any minMatches="0" maxMatches="0">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_latvia_eu_telephone_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_latvia_eu_mobile_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_latvia_eu_national_id_card_new_format" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_latvia_eu_national_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_latvia_eu_national_id_card_new_format" />
          <Any minMatches="0" maxMatches="0">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_latvia_eu_telephone_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_latvia_eu_mobile_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>

```

## <a name="latvia-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-7162">拉脫維亞護照號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-7162">Latvia passport number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-7163">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-7163">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-7164">兩個字母或數位後接7位數，不含空格或分隔符號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-7164">two letters or digits followed by seven digits with no spaces or delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-7165">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-7165">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-7166">兩個字母或數位後接7位數：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-7166">two letters or digits followed by seven digits:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-7167">兩位數的數位或字母 (不區分大小寫) </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-7167">two digits or letters (not case-sensitive)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-7168">七位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-7168">seven digits</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-7169">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-7169">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-7170">否</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-7170">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-7171">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-7171">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-7172">當鄰近性300個字元以內時，DLP 原則就會偵測到這種敏感資訊類型：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-7172">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-7173">正則運算式會  `Regex_latvia_eu_passport_number` 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-7173">The regular expression  `Regex_latvia_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-7174">`Keywords_eu_passport_number`找到或的關鍵字 `Keywords_latvia_eu_passport_number` 。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-7174">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_latvia_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-7175">正則運算式 `Regex_eu_passport_date1` 會發現日期格式為 DD YYYY 或關鍵字 from `Keywords_eu_passport_date`</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-7175">The regular expression `Regex_eu_passport_date1` finds date in the format DD.MM.YYYY or a keyword from `Keywords_eu_passport_date` is found</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-7176">當鄰近性300個字元以內時，DLP 原則就會偵測到這種敏感資訊類型的信賴度。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-7176">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-7177">正則運算式會  `Regex_latvia_eu_passport_number` 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-7177">The regular expression  `Regex_latvia_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-7178">`Keywords_eu_passport_number`找到或的關鍵字 `Keywords_latvia_eu_passport_number` 。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-7178">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_latvia_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Latvia Passport Number -->
      <Entity id="23ae25ec-cc28-421b-b77a-3054eadf1ede" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_latvia_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_latvia_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Regex_eu_passport_date1" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_date" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_latvia_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
```

## <a name="lithuania-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-7201">立陶宛駕照編號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-7201">Lithuania driver's license number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-7202">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-7202">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-7203">不含空格及分隔符號的八位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-7203">eight digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-7204">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-7204">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-7205">八位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-7205">eight digits</span></span> 
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-7206">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-7206">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-7207">否</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-7207">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-7208">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-7208">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-7209">當鄰近性300個字元以內時，DLP 原則就會偵測到這種敏感資訊類型的信賴度。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-7209">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-7210">正則運算式會  `Regex_lithuania_eu_driver's_license_number` 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-7210">The regular expression  `Regex_lithuania_eu_driver's_license_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-7211">`Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number`找到或的關鍵字 `Keywords_lithuania_eu_driver's_license_number` 。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-7211">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` or `Keywords_lithuania_eu_driver's_license_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Lithuania Driver's License Number -->
      <Entity id="86f7628b-e0f4-4dc3-9fbc-e4300e4c7d78" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_lithuania_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_lithuania_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="lithuania-personal-code"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-7336">立陶宛個人程式碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-7336">Lithuania personal code</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="94f34-7337">此機密資訊類型僅可用於下列專案：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-7337">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-7338">資料遺失防護原則</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-7338">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-7339">通訊相容性原則</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-7339">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-7340">資訊管理</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-7340">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-7341">記錄管理</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-7341">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-7342">Microsoft cloud app security</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-7342">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-7343">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-7343">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-7344">11位數，不含空格及分隔符號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-7344">11 digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-7345">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-7345">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-7346">11位數，不含空格及分隔符號：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-7346">11 digits without spaces and delimiters:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-7347">對應至人員性別和出生世紀的一個數位 (1-6) </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-7347">one digit (1-6) that corresponds to the person's gender and century of birth</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-7348">對應至出生日期 (YYMMDD 的六位數) </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-7348">six digits that correspond to birth date (YYMMDD)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-7349">對應至出生日期之序號的三位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-7349">three digits that correspond to the serial number of the date of birth</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-7350">一個檢查碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-7350">one check digit</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-7351">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-7351">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-7352">是</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-7352">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-7353">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-7353">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-7354">當鄰近性300個字元以內時，DLP 原則就會偵測到這種敏感資訊類型：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-7354">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-7355">函數  `Func_lithuania_eu_tax_file_number` 會找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-7355">The function  `Func_lithuania_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-7356">找到來自的關鍵字  `Keywords_lithuania_eu_tax_file_number` 。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-7356">A keyword from  `Keywords_lithuania_eu_tax_file_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="94f34-7357">當鄰近性300個字元以內時，DLP 原則就會偵測到這種敏感資訊類型的信賴度。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-7357">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-7358">函數  `Func_lithuania_eu_tax_file_number` 會找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-7358">The function  `Func_lithuania_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Lithuania Personal Code -->
      <Entity id="cd6d3786-8ec3-4524-a2cf-1e0095379171" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_lithuania_eu_tax_file_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_lithuania_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_lithuania_eu_tax_file_number" />
          <Any minMatches="0" maxMatches="0">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_lithuania_eu_telephone_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_lithuania_eu_mobile_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="lithuania-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-7393">立陶宛護照號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-7393">Lithuania passport number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-7394">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-7394">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-7395">八位數的數位或字母，不含空格或分隔符號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-7395">eight digits or letters with no spaces or delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-7396">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-7396">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-7397">八位數的數位或字母 (不區分大小寫) </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-7397">eight digits or letters (not case-sensitive)</span></span>
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-7398">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-7398">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-7399">不適用</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-7399">not applicable</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-7400">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-7400">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-7401">當鄰近性300個字元以內時，DLP 原則就會偵測到這種敏感資訊類型：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-7401">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-7402">正則運算式會  `Regex_lithuania_eu_passport_number` 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-7402">The regular expression  `Regex_lithuania_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-7403">`Keywords_eu_passport_number`找到或的關鍵字 `Keywords_lithuania_eu_passport_number` 。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-7403">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_lithuania_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-7404">正則運算式 `Regex_eu_passport_date3` 會找到日期格式為 DD MM YYYY 或關鍵字 from。 `Keywords_eu_passport_date`</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-7404">The regular expression `Regex_eu_passport_date3` finds date in the format DD MM YYYY or a keyword from `Keywords_eu_passport_date` is found</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-7405">當鄰近性300個字元以內時，DLP 原則就會偵測到這種敏感資訊類型的信賴度。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-7405">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-7406">正則運算式會  `Regex_lithuania_eu_passport_number` 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-7406">The regular expression  `Regex_lithuania_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-7407">`Keywords_eu_passport_number`找到或的關鍵字 `Keywords_lithuania_eu_passport_number` 。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-7407">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_lithuania_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Lithuania Passport Number -->
      <Entity id="1b79900f-047b-4c3f-846f-7d73b5534bce" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_lithuania_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_lithuania_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Regex_eu_passport_date3" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_date" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_lithuania_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_lithuania_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="luxemburg-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-7427">Luxemburg 駕駛執照號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-7427">Luxemburg driver's license number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-7428">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-7428">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-7429">六位數，不含空格及分隔符號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-7429">six digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-7430">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-7430">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-7431">六位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-7431">six digits</span></span> 
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-7432">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-7432">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-7433">否</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-7433">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-7434">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-7434">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-7435">當鄰近性300個字元以內時，DLP 原則就會偵測到這種敏感資訊類型的信賴度。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-7435">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-7436">正則運算式會  `Regex_luxemburg_eu_driver's_license_number` 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-7436">The regular expression  `Regex_luxemburg_eu_driver's_license_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-7437">`Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number`找到或的關鍵字 `Keywords_luxemburg_eu_driver's_license_number` 。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-7437">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` or `Keywords_luxemburg_eu_driver's_license_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Luxemburg Driver's License Number -->
      <Entity id="89daf717-1544-4860-9a2e-fc9166dd8852" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_luxemburg_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_luxemburg_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="luxemburg-national-identification-number-natural-persons"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-7561">Luxemburg (自然個人的國家識別號碼) </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-7561">Luxemburg national identification number (natural persons)</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="94f34-7562">此機密資訊類型僅可用於下列專案：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-7562">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-7563">資料遺失防護原則</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-7563">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-7564">通訊相容性原則</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-7564">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-7565">資訊管理</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-7565">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-7566">記錄管理</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-7566">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-7567">Microsoft cloud app security</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-7567">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-7568">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-7568">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-7569">13位數沒有空格或分隔符號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-7569">13 digits with no spaces or delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-7570">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-7570">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-7571">13位數：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-7571">13 digits:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-7572">11位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-7572">11 digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-7573">兩個檢查碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-7573">two check digits</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-7574">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-7574">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-7575">是</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-7575">yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-7576">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-7576">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-7577">當鄰近性300個字元以內時，DLP 原則就會偵測到這種敏感資訊類型：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-7577">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-7578">函數  `Func_luxemburg_eu_tax_file_number` 會找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-7578">The function  `Func_luxemburg_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-7579">找到來自的關鍵字  `Keywords_luxemburg_eu_national_id_card` 。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-7579">A keyword from  `Keywords_luxemburg_eu_national_id_card` is found.</span></span> 

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-7580">當鄰近性300個字元以內時，DLP 原則就會偵測到這種敏感資訊類型的信賴度。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-7580">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-7581">函數  `Func_luxemburg_eu_tax_file_number` 會找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-7581">The function  `Func_luxemburg_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 


```xml
      <!-- Luxemburg National Identification Number (Natural persons) -->
      <Entity id="aaf661ed-29ec-426d-8bf9-880cad298ebb" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_luxemburg_eu_tax_file_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_luxemburg_eu_national_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_luxemburg_eu_tax_file_number" />
          <Any minMatches="0" maxMatches="0">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_luxemburg_eu_telephone_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_luxemburg_eu_mobile_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="luxemburg-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-7604">Luxemburg 護照號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-7604">Luxemburg passport number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-7605">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-7605">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-7606">八位數的數位或字母，不含空格或分隔符號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-7606">eight digits or letters with no spaces or delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-7607">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-7607">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-7608">八位數的數位或字母 (不區分大小寫) </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-7608">eight digits or letters (not case-sensitive)</span></span>
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-7609">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-7609">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-7610">否</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-7610">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-7611">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-7611">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-7612">當鄰近性300個字元以內時，DLP 原則就會偵測到這種敏感資訊類型：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-7612">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-7613">正則運算式會  `Regex_luxemburg_eu_passport_number` 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-7613">The regular expression  `Regex_luxemburg_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-7614">`Keywords_eu_passport_number`找到或的關鍵字 `Keywords_luxemburg_eu_passport_number` 。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-7614">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_luxemburg_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-7615">正則運算式 `Regex_eu_passport_date3` 會找到日期格式為 DD MM YYYY 或關鍵字 from。 `Keywords_eu_passport_date`</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-7615">The regular expression `Regex_eu_passport_date3` finds date in the format DD MM YYYY or a keyword from `Keywords_eu_passport_date` is found</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-7616">當鄰近性300個字元以內時，DLP 原則就會偵測到這種敏感資訊類型的信賴度。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-7616">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-7617">正則運算式會  `Regex_luxemburg_eu_passport_number` 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-7617">The regular expression  `Regex_luxemburg_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-7618">`Keywords_eu_passport_number`找到或的關鍵字 `Keywords_luxemburg_eu_passport_number` 。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-7618">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_luxemburg_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Luxemburg Passport Number -->
      <Entity id="81d5c027-bed9-4421-91a0-3b2e55b3eb85" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_luxemburg_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_luxemburg_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Regex_eu_passport_date3" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_date" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_luxemburg_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_luxemburg_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="luxemburg-national-identification-number-non-natural-persons"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-7650">Luxemburg 非自然人員 (的本國識別碼) </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-7650">Luxemburg national identification number (non-natural persons)</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-7651">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-7651">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-7652">11位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-7652">11 digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-7653">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-7653">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-7654">11位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-7654">11 digits</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-7655">兩位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-7655">two digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-7656">選擇性的空格</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-7656">an optional space</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-7657">三位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-7657">three digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-7658">選擇性的空格</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-7658">an optional space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-7659">三位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-7659">three digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-7660">選擇性的空格</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-7660">an optional space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-7661">兩位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-7661">two digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-7662">一個檢查碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-7662">one check digit</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-7663">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-7663">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-7664">是</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-7664">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-7665">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-7665">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-7666">當鄰近性300個字元以內時，DLP 原則就會偵測到這種敏感資訊類型：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-7666">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-7667">函數  `Func_luxemburg_eu_tax_file_number_non_natural` 會找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-7667">The function  `Func_luxemburg_eu_tax_file_number_non_natural` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-7668">找到來自的關鍵字  `Keywords_luxemburg_eu_tax_file_number` 。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-7668">A keyword from  `Keywords_luxemburg_eu_tax_file_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="94f34-7669">當鄰近性300個字元以內時，DLP 原則就會偵測到這種敏感資訊類型的信賴度。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-7669">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-7670">函數  `Func_luxemburg_eu_tax_file_number_non_natural` 會找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-7670">The function  `Func_luxemburg_eu_tax_file_number_non_natural` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Luxemburg National Identification Number (Non-natural persons) -->
      <Entity id="84bffa3a-d805-4788-a613-b1e4df3804cf" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_luxemburg_eu_tax_file_number_non_natural" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_luxemburg_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_luxemburg_eu_tax_file_number_non_natural" />
          <Any minMatches="0" maxMatches="0">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_luxemburg_eu_telephone_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_luxemburg_eu_mobile_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="malaysia-identification-card-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-7710">馬來西亞身分識別卡號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-7710">Malaysia identification card number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-7711">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-7711">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-7712">12位數包含選擇性連字號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-7712">12 digits containing optional hyphens</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-7713">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-7713">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-7714">12位數：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-7714">12 digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-7715">YYMMDD 格式的六位數（出生日期）</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-7715">six digits in the format YYMMDD, which are the date of birth</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-7716">虛線 (選用) </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-7716">a dash (optional)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-7717">兩個字母的出生代碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-7717">two-letter place-of-birth code</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-7718">虛線 (選用) </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-7718">a dash (optional)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-7719">三個亂數字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-7719">three random digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-7720">一位數的性別碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-7720">one-digit gender code</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-7721">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-7721">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-7722">否</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-7722">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-7723">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-7723">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-7724">當鄰近性300個字元以內時，DLP 原則就會偵測到這種敏感資訊類型：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-7724">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-7725">正則運算式 Regex_malaysia_id_card_number 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-7725">The regular expression Regex_malaysia_id_card_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-7726">會找到來自 Keyword_malaysia_id_card_number 的關鍵字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-7726">A keyword from Keyword_malaysia_id_card_number is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Malaysia ID Card Number -->
</Entity>
      <Entity id="7f0e921c-9677-435b-aba2-bb8f1013c749" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
            <IdMatch idRef="Regex_malaysia_id_card_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keyword_malaysia_id_card_number" />
        </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="malta-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-7753">馬爾他駕照編號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-7753">Malta driver's license number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-7754">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-7754">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-7755">兩個字元的組合，並在指定的模式中包含六位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-7755">Combination of two characters and six digits in the specified pattern</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-7756">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-7756">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-7757">兩個字元和六位數的組合：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-7757">combination of two characters and six digits:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-7758"> (位數或字母的兩個字元，而不區分大小寫) </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-7758">two characters (digits or letters, not case-sensitive)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-7759">空格 (選用) </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-7759">a space (optional)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-7760">三位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-7760">three digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-7761">空格 (選用) </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-7761">a space (optional)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-7762">三位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-7762">three digits</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-7763">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-7763">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-7764">否</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-7764">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-7765">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-7765">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-7766">當鄰近性300個字元以內時，DLP 原則就會偵測到這種敏感資訊類型的信賴度。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-7766">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-7767">正則運算式會  `Regex_malta_eu_driver's_license_number` 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-7767">The regular expression  `Regex_malta_eu_driver's_license_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-7768">`Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number`找到或的關鍵字 `Keywords_malta_eu_driver's_license_number` 。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-7768">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` or `Keywords_malta_eu_driver's_license_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Malta Driver's License Number -->
      <Entity id="a3bdaa4a-8371-4735-8fa5-56ee0fb4afc4" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_malta_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_malta_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="malta-identity-card-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-7892">馬爾他身分識別卡號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-7892">Malta identity card number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="94f34-7893">此機密資訊類型僅可用於下列專案：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-7893">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-7894">資料遺失防護原則</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-7894">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-7895">通訊相容性原則</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-7895">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-7896">資訊管理</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-7896">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-7897">記錄管理</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-7897">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-7898">Microsoft cloud app security</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-7898">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-7899">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-7899">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-7900">七位數後接一個字母</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-7900">seven digits followed by one letter</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-7901">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-7901">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-7902">七位數後接一個字母：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-7902">seven digits followed by one letter:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-7903">七位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-7903">seven digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-7904">"M，G，A，P，L，H，B，Z" (不區分大小寫的一個字母) </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-7904">one letter in "M, G, A, P, L, H, B, Z" (case insensitive)</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-7905">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-7905">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-7906">不適用</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-7906">Not applicable</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-7907">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-7907">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-7908">當鄰近性300個字元以內時，DLP 原則就會偵測到這種敏感資訊類型的信賴度。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-7908">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-7909">正則運算式會  `Regex_malta_eu_national_id_card` 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-7909">The regular expression  `Regex_malta_eu_national_id_card` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-7910">找到來自的關鍵字  `Keywords_malta_eu_national_id_card` 。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-7910">A keyword from  `Keywords_malta_eu_national_id_card` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="94f34-7911">DLP 原則在接近300個字元以內時，偵測到此敏感資訊類型的信賴度很低：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-7911">A DLP policy has low confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-7912">正則運算式會  `Regex_malta_eu_national_id_card` 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-7912">The regular expression  `Regex_malta_eu_national_id_card` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Malta Identity Card Number -->
      <Entity id="854b36b3-a388-4ac8-a4ec-677c2b5e4356" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_malta_eu_national_id_card" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_malta_eu_national_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_malta_eu_national_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-7921">numru ta ' identifikazzjoni uniku</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-7921">numru ta 'identifikazzjoni uniku</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-7922">numru ta ' identità uniku</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-7922">numru ta' identità uniku</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-7923">numru tas-servizz taċ-ċittadin</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-7923">numru tas-servizz taċ-ċittadin</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-7924">numru tat-taxxa</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-7924">numru tat-taxxa</span></span>

## <a name="malta-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-7929">馬爾他護照號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-7929">Malta passport number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-7930">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-7930">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-7931">七位數，不含空格或分隔符號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-7931">seven digits without spaces or delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-7932">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-7932">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-7933">七位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-7933">seven digits</span></span> 
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-7934">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-7934">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-7935">否</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-7935">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-7936">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-7936">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-7937">當鄰近性300個字元以內時，DLP 原則就會偵測到這種敏感資訊類型：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-7937">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-7938">正則運算式會  `Regex_malta_eu_passport_number` 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-7938">The regular expression  `Regex_malta_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-7939">`Keywords_eu_passport_number`找到或的關鍵字 `Keywords_malta_eu_passport_number` 。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-7939">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_malta_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-7940">找到來自的關鍵字 `Keywords_eu_passport_date`</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-7940">A keyword from `Keywords_eu_passport_date` is found</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-7941">當鄰近性300個字元以內時，DLP 原則就會偵測到這種敏感資訊類型的信賴度。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-7941">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-7942">正則運算式會  `Regex_malta_eu_passport_number` 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-7942">The regular expression  `Regex_malta_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-7943">`Keywords_eu_passport_number`找到或的關鍵字 `Keywords_malta_eu_passport_number` 。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-7943">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_malta_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Malta Passport Number -->
      <Entity id="b2b21198-48f9-4d13-b2a5-03969bff0fb8" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_malta_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_malta_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
          <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_date" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_malta_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_malta_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="malta-tax-identification-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-7963">馬爾他納稅識別號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-7963">Malta tax identification number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-7964">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-7964">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-7965">針對馬爾他 nationals：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-7965">For Maltese nationals:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-7966">指定的模式中的七位數和一個字母</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-7966">seven digits and one letter in the specified pattern</span></span>
  
<span data-ttu-id="94f34-7967">非馬爾他 nationals 及馬爾他式實體：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-7967">Non-Maltese nationals and Maltese entities:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-7968">九位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-7968">nine digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-7969">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-7969">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-7970">馬爾他 nationals：7位數和一個字母</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-7970">Maltese nationals: seven digits and one letter</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-7971">七位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-7971">seven digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-7972">一個字母 (不區分大小寫) </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-7972">one letter (not case-sensitive)</span></span>
    
<span data-ttu-id="94f34-7973">非馬爾他 nationals 和馬爾他圖元：九位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-7973">Non-Maltese nationals and Maltese entities: nine digits</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-7974">九位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-7974">nine digits</span></span> 
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-7975">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-7975">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-7976">不適用</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-7976">Not applicable</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-7977">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-7977">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-7978">當鄰近性300個字元以內時，DLP 原則就會偵測到這種敏感資訊類型的信賴度。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-7978">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-7979">Regex  `Regex_malta_eu_tax_file_number`  或 `Regex_malta_eu_tax_file_number_non_maltese_national` 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-7979">The regex  `Regex_malta_eu_tax_file_number`  or `Regex_malta_eu_tax_file_number_non_maltese_national` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-7980">找到來自的關鍵字  `Keywords_malta_eu_tax_file_number` 。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-7980">A keyword from  `Keywords_malta_eu_tax_file_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="94f34-7981">DLP 原則在接近300個字元以內時，偵測到此敏感資訊類型的信賴度很低：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-7981">A DLP policy has low confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-7982">Regex  `Regex_malta_eu_tax_file_number` 或 `Regex_malta_eu_tax_file_number_non_maltese_national` 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-7982">The regex  `Regex_malta_eu_tax_file_number` or `Regex_malta_eu_tax_file_number_non_maltese_national` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Malta Tax ID Number -->
      <Entity id="ec830c63-65f4-45d0-9d8c-910dc8334b20" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_malta_eu_tax_file_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_malta_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_malta_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_malta_eu_tax_file_number_non_maltese_national" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_malta_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_malta_eu_tax_file_number_non_maltese_national" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="netherlands-citizens-service-bsn-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-8015">荷蘭公民服務 (BSN) 號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8015">Netherlands citizen's service (BSN) number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-8016">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8016">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-8017">8或9位數包含選擇性空格</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8017">eight or nine digits containing optional spaces</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-8018">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8018">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-8019">八-九位數：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8019">eight-nine digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-8020">三位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8020">three digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-8021">空格 (選用) </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8021">a space (optional)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-8022">三位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8022">three digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-8023">空格 (選用) </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8023">a space (optional)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-8024">兩個三位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8024">two-three digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-8025">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8025">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-8026">是</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8026">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-8027">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8027">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-8028">當鄰近性300個字元以內時，DLP 原則就會偵測到這種敏感資訊類型：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8028">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-8029">函數 Func_netherlands_bsn 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8029">The function Func_netherlands_bsn finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-8030">會找到來自 Keyword_netherlands_bsn 的關鍵字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8030">A keyword from Keyword_netherlands_bsn is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-8031">校驗和通過。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8031">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Netherlands Citizen's Service (BSN) Number -->
      <Entity id="c5f54253-ef7e-44f6-a578-440ed67e946d" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_netherlands_bsn" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_netherlands_eu_national_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="netherlands-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-8055">荷蘭駕駛執照號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8055">Netherlands driver's license number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-8056">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8056">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-8057">10位數，不含空格及分隔符號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8057">ten digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-8058">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8058">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-8059">10位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8059">ten digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-8060">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8060">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-8061">否</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8061">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-8062">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8062">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-8063">當鄰近性300個字元以內時，DLP 原則就會偵測到這種敏感資訊類型的信賴度。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8063">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-8064">正則運算式會  `Regex_netherlands_eu_driver's_license_number` 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8064">The regular expression  `Regex_netherlands_eu_driver's_license_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-8065">`Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number`找到或的關鍵字 `Keywords_netherlands_eu_driver's_license_number` 。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8065">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` or `Keywords_netherlands_eu_driver's_license_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Netherlands Driver's License Number -->
      <Entity id="6247fbea-ab80-4be5-8233-308b7c031401" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_netherlands_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_netherlands_eu_driver's_license_number" />
            </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```
