## <a name="netherlands-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-8193">荷蘭護照號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8193">Netherlands passport number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-8194">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8194">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-8195">不含空格或分隔符號的九個字母或數位</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8195">nine letters or digits with no spaces or delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-8196">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8196">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-8197">九個字母或數位</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8197">nine letters or digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-8198">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8198">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-8199">不適用</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8199">not applicable</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-8200">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8200">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-8201">當鄰近性300個字元以內時，DLP 原則就會偵測到這種敏感資訊類型：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8201">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-8202">正則運算式會  `Regex_netherlands_eu_passport_number` 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8202">The regular expression  `Regex_netherlands_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-8203">`Keywords_eu_passport_number`找到或的關鍵字 `Keywords_netherlands_eu_passport_number` 。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8203">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_netherlands_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-8204">正則運算式會 `Regex_netherlands_eu_passport_date` 以 DD MMM/MMM YYYY 的格式來找到日期 (範例-26 MAA/3 月 2012) </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8204">The regular expression `Regex_netherlands_eu_passport_date` finds date in the format  DD MMM/MMM YYYY (Example - 26 MAA/MAR 2012)</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-8205">當鄰近性300個字元以內時，DLP 原則就會偵測到這種敏感資訊類型的信賴度。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8205">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-8206">正則運算式會  `Regex_netherlands_eu_passport_number` 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8206">The regular expression  `Regex_netherlands_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-8207">`Keywords_eu_passport_number`找到或的關鍵字 `Keywords_netherlands_eu_passport_number` 。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8207">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_netherlands_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Netherlands Passport Number -->
      <Entity id="61786727-bafd-45f6-94d9-888d815e228e" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_netherlands_eu_passport_number" />
          <Match idRef="Regex_netherlands_eu_passport_date" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_netherlands_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_netherlands_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_netherlands_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="netherlands-tax-identification-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-8225">荷蘭稅務識別號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8225">Netherlands tax identification number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="94f34-8226">此機密資訊類型僅可用於下列專案：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8226">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-8227">資料遺失防護原則</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8227">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-8228">通訊相容性原則</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8228">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-8229">資訊管理</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8229">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-8230">記錄管理</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8230">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-8231">Microsoft cloud app security</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8231">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-8232">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8232">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-8233">九位數，不含空格或分隔符號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8233">nine digits without spaces or delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-8234">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8234">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-8235">九位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8235">nine digits</span></span> 
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-8236">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8236">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-8237">是</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8237">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-8238">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8238">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-8239">當鄰近性300個字元以內時，DLP 原則就會偵測到這種敏感資訊類型：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8239">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-8240">函數  `Func_netherlands_eu_tax_file_number` 會找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8240">The function  `Func_netherlands_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-8241">找到來自的關鍵字  `Keywords_netherlands_eu_tax_file_number` 。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8241">A keyword from  `Keywords_netherlands_eu_tax_file_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="94f34-8242">DLP 原則在接近300個字元以內時，偵測到此敏感資訊類型的信賴度很低：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8242">A DLP policy has low confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-8243">函數  `Func_netherlands_eu_tax_file_number` 會找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8243">The function  `Func_netherlands_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Netherlands Tax Identification Number -->
      <Entity id="01f42a64-eba7-4892-a67b-398237e4ade2" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_netherlands_eu_tax_file_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_netherlands_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_netherlands_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="netherlands-value-added-tax-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-8281">荷蘭增值納稅號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8281">Netherlands value added tax number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="94f34-8282">此機密資訊類型僅可用於下列專案：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8282">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-8283">資料遺失防護原則</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8283">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-8284">通訊相容性原則</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8284">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-8285">資訊管理</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8285">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-8286">記錄管理</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8286">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-8287">Microsoft cloud app security</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8287">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-8288">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8288">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-8289">14個字元的字母數位模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8289">14 character alphanumeric pattern</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-8290">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8290">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-8291">14個字元的字母數位模式：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8291">14-character alphanumeric pattern:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-8292">N 或 n</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8292">N or n</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-8293">L 或 l</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8293">L or l</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-8294">選用的空格、點或連字號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8294">optional space, dot, or hyphen</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-8295">九位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8295">nine digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-8296">選用的空格、點或連字號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8296">optional space, dot, or hyphen</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-8297">B 或 b</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8297">B or b</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-8298">兩位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8298">two digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-8299">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8299">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-8300">是</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8300">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-8301">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8301">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-8302">當鄰近性300個字元以內時，DLP 原則就會偵測到這種敏感資訊類型：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8302">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-8303">函數 Func_netherlands_value_added_tax_number 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8303">The function Func_netherlands_value_added_tax_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-8304">會找到來自 Keywords_netherlands_value_added_tax_number 的關鍵字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8304">A keyword from Keywords_netherlands_value_added_tax_number is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-8305">當鄰近性300個字元以內時，DLP 原則就會偵測到這種敏感資訊類型的信賴度。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8305">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-8306">函數 Func_netherlands_value_added_tax_number 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8306">The function Func_netherlands_value_added_tax_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Netherlands Value Added Tax Number -->
      <Entity id="4f320d9b-4972-41ae-b337-88d499bb1ade" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_netherlands_value_added_tax_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_netherlands_value_added_tax_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_netherlands_value_added_tax_number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-8316">此機密資訊類型僅可用於下列專案：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8316">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-8317">資料遺失防護原則</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8317">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-8318">通訊相容性原則</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8318">communication compliance policies</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-8320">記錄管理</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8320">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-8321">Microsoft cloud app security</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8321">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-8322">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8322">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-8323">14位數至16位數的模式，具有選用的分隔符號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8323">14-digit to 16-digit pattern with optional delimiter</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-8324">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8324">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-8325">14位數至16位數的模式，具有選用的分隔符號：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8325">14-digit to 16-digit pattern with optional delimiter:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-8326">兩位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8326">two digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-8327">選用的連字號或空格</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8327">an optional hyphen or space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-8328">三至四位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8328">three to four digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-8329">選用的連字號或空格</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8329">an optional hyphen or space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-8330">七位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8330">seven digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-8331">選用的連字號或空格</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8331">an optional hyphen or space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-8332">二到三位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8332">two to three digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-8333">選項連字號或空格</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8333">an options hyphen or space</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-8334">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8334">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-8335">是</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8335">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-8336">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8336">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-8337">當鄰近性300個字元以內時，DLP 原則就會偵測到這種敏感資訊類型：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8337">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-8338">函數 Func_new_zealand_bank_account_number 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8338">The function Func_new_zealand_bank_account_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-8339">會找到來自 Keywords_new_zealand_bank_account_number 的關鍵字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8339">A keyword from Keywords_new_zealand_bank_account_number is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-8340">當鄰近性300個字元以內時，DLP 原則就會偵測到這種敏感資訊類型的信賴度。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8340">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-8341">函數 Func_new_zealand_bank_account_number 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8341">The function Func_new_zealand_bank_account_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- New Zealand Bank Account Number -->
      <Entity id="1a97fc2b-dd2f-48f1-bc4e-2ddf25813956" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_new_zealand_bank_account_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_new_zFealand_bank_account_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_new_zealand_bank_account_number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="new-zealand-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-8349">紐西蘭駕駛執照號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8349">New Zealand driver's license number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="94f34-8350">此機密資訊類型僅可用於下列專案：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8350">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-8351">資料遺失防護原則</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8351">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-8352">通訊相容性原則</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8352">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-8353">資訊管理</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8353">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-8354">記錄管理</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8354">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-8355">Microsoft cloud app security</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8355">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-8356">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8356">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-8357">八個字元的字母數位模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8357">eight character alphanumeric pattern</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-8358">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8358">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-8359">八個字元的字母數位模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8359">eight character alphanumeric pattern</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-8360">兩個字母</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8360">two letters</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-8361">六位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8361">six digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-8362">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8362">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-8363">是</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8363">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-8364">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8364">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-8365">當鄰近性300個字元以內時，DLP 原則就會偵測到這種敏感資訊類型：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8365">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-8366">函數 Func_newzealand_driver_license_number 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8366">The function Func_newzealand_driver_license_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-8367">會找到來自 Keywords_newzealand_driver_license_number 的關鍵字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8367">A keyword from Keywords_newzealand_driver_license_number is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-8368">DLP 原則在接近300個字元以內時，偵測到此敏感資訊類型的信賴度很低：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8368">A DLP policy has low confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-8369">函數 Func_newzealand_driver_license_number 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8369">The function Func_newzealand_driver_license_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- New Zealand Driver License Number -->
      <Entity id="1924b377-d287-49c9-a737-cfe7a8a2615a" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_newzealand_driver_license_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_newzealand_driver_license_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_newzealand_driver_license_number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-8435">紐西蘭汽車協會</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8435">new zealand automobile association</span></span>


## <a name="new-zealand-inland-revenue-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-8436">紐西蘭 inland 收入數目</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8436">New Zealand inland revenue number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="94f34-8437">此機密資訊類型僅可用於下列專案：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8437">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-8438">資料遺失防護原則</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8438">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-8439">通訊相容性原則</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8439">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-8440">資訊管理</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8440">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-8441">記錄管理</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8441">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-8442">Microsoft cloud app security</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8442">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-8443">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8443">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-8444">8或9位數（選用分隔符號）</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8444">eight or nine digits with optional delimiters</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-8445">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8445">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-8446">8或9位數（選用分隔符號）</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8446">eight or nine digits with optional delimiters</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-8447">兩位數或三位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8447">two or three digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-8448">選擇性空格或連字號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8448">an optional space or hyphen</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-8449">三位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8449">three digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-8450">選擇性空格或連字號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8450">an optional space or hyphen</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-8451">三位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8451">three digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-8452">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8452">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-8453">是</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8453">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-8454">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8454">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-8455">當鄰近性300個字元以內時，DLP 原則就會偵測到這種敏感資訊類型：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8455">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-8456">函數 Func_new_zealand_inland_revenue_number 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8456">The function Func_new_zealand_inland_revenue_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-8457">會找到來自 Keywords_new_zealand_inland_revenue_number 的關鍵字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8457">A keyword from Keywords_new_zealand_inland_revenue_number is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-8458">當鄰近性300個字元以內時，DLP 原則就會偵測到這種敏感資訊類型的信賴度。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8458">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-8459">函數 Func_new_zealand_inland_revenue_number 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8459">The function Func_new_zealand_inland_revenue_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- New Zealand Inland Revenue Number -->
      <Entity id="dd0fe2bc-7bcf-455f-bac1-83b1e3eb25fd" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_new_zealand_inland_revenue_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_new_zealand_inland_revenue_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_new_zealand_inland_revenue_number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-8460">關鍵字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8460">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_new_zealand_inland_revenue_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-8461">Keyword_new_zealand_inland_revenue_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8461">Keyword_new_zealand_inland_revenue_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-8462">ird 編號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8462">ird no.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-8463">ird 否#</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8463">ird no#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-8464">紐西蘭 ird</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8464">nz ird</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-8465">紐西蘭 ird</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8465">new zealand ird</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-8466">ird 編號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8466">ird number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-8467">inland 收入數目</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8467">inland revenue number</span></span>


## <a name="new-zealand-ministry-of-health-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-8468">紐西蘭健康情況號碼的部</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8468">New Zealand ministry of health number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-8469">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8469">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-8470">三個字母、一個空格 (選用) 及四位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8470">three letters, a space (optional), and four digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-8471">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8471">Pattern</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-8472">三個字母 (不區分大小寫) 「I ' 和「O ' 除外</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8472">three letters (not case-sensitive) except 'I' and 'O'</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-8473">空格 (選用) </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8473">a space (optional)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-8474">四位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8474">four digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-8475">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8475">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-8476">是</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8476">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-8477">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8477">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-8478">當鄰近性300個字元以內時，DLP 原則就會偵測到這種敏感資訊類型：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8478">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-8479">函數 Func_new_zealand_ministry_of_health_number 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8479">The function Func_new_zealand_ministry_of_health_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-8480">會找到來自 Keyword_nz_terms 的關鍵字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8480">A keyword from Keyword_nz_terms is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-8481">校驗和通過。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8481">The checksum passes.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-8482">當鄰近性300個字元以內時，DLP 原則就會偵測到這種敏感資訊類型的信賴度。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8482">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-8483">函數 Func_new_zealand_ministry_of_health_number 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8483">The function Func_new_zealand_ministry_of_health_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-8484">校驗和通過。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8484">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
    <!-- New Zealand Health Number -->
    <Entity id="2b71c1c8-d14e-4430-82dc-fd1ed6bf05c7" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_new_zealand_ministry_of_health_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_nz_terms" />
      </Pattern>
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_new_zealand_ministry_of_health_number" />
       </Pattern>
    </Entity>
```

#### <a name="keyword_nz_terms"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-8486">Keyword_nz_terms</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8486">Keyword_nz_terms</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-8487">NHI</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8487">NHI</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-8488">紐西蘭</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8488">New Zealand</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-8489">健康情況</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8489">Health</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-8490">治療</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8490">treatment</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-8491">本國健康情況索引編號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8491">National Health Index Number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-8492">nhi 編號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8492">nhi number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-8493">nhi 編號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8493">nhi no.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-8496">本國健康情況索引識別碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8496">National Health Index Id</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-8497">本國健康情況索引#</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8497">National Health Index #</span></span>

## <a name="new-zealand-social-welfare-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-8498">紐西蘭社交 welfare 號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8498">New Zealand social welfare number</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-8499">此機密資訊類型僅可用於下列專案：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8499">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-8500">資料遺失防護原則</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8500">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-8501">通訊相容性原則</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8501">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-8502">資訊管理</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8502">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-8503">記錄管理</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8503">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-8504">Microsoft cloud app security</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8504">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-8505">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8505">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-8506">九位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8506">nine digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-8507">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8507">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-8508">九位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8508">nine digits</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-8509">三位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8509">three digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-8510">選用的連字號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8510">an optional hyphen</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-8511">三位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8511">three digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-8512">選用的連字號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8512">an optional hyphen</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-8513">三位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8513">three digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-8514">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8514">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-8515">是</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8515">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-8516">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8516">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-8517">當鄰近性300個字元以內時，DLP 原則就會偵測到這種敏感資訊類型：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8517">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-8518">函數 Func_newzealand_social_welfare_number 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8518">The function Func_newzealand_social_welfare_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-8519">會找到來自 Keywords_newzealand_social_welfare_number 的關鍵字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8519">A keyword from Keywords_newzealand_social_welfare_number is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-8520">DLP 原則在接近300個字元以內時，偵測到此敏感資訊類型的信賴度很低：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8520">A DLP policy has low confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-8521">函數 Func_newzealand_social_welfare_number 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8521">The function Func_newzealand_social_welfare_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Newzealand Social Welfare Number -->
      <Entity id="20f3c48d-4ac1-4cd2-86bd-34ecc1826e9d" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_newzealand_social_welfare_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_newzealand_social_welfare_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_newzealand_social_welfare_number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
    </Version>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-8522">關鍵字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8522">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_new_zealand_social_welfare_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-8523">Keyword_new_zealand_social_welfare_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8523">Keyword_new_zealand_social_welfare_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-8524">社交 welfare#</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8524">social welfare #</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-8526">社交 welfare 編號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8526">social welfare No.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-8527">社交 welfare 號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8527">social welfare number</span></span>

## <a name="norway-identification-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-8529">挪威身分識別號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8529">Norway identification number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-8530">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8530">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-8531">11位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8531">11 digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-8532">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8532">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-8533">11位數：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8533">11 digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-8534">DDMMYY 之日期格式的六位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8534">six digits in the format DDMMYY which are the date of birth</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-8535">三位數個人號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8535">three-digit individual number</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-8536">兩個檢查碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8536">two check digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-8537">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8537">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-8538">是</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8538">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-8539">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8539">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-8540">當鄰近性300個字元以內時，DLP 原則就會偵測到這種敏感資訊類型：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8540">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-8541">函數 Func_norway_id_number 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8541">The function Func_norway_id_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-8542">會找到來自 Keyword_norway_id_number 的關鍵字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8542">A keyword from Keyword_norway_id_number is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-8543">校驗和通過。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8543">The checksum passes.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-8544">當鄰近性300個字元以內時，DLP 原則就會偵測到這種敏感資訊類型的信賴度。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8544">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-8545">函數 Func_norway_id_numbe 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8545">The function Func_norway_id_numbe finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-8546">校驗和通過。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8546">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Norway Identification Number -->
<Entity id="d4c8a798-e9f2-4bd3-9652-500d24080fc3" recommendedConfidence="85" patternsProximity="300">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
     <IdMatch idRef="Func_norway_id_number"/>
     <Match idRef="Keyword_norway_id_number"/>
  </Pattern>
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
     <IdMatch idRef="Func_norway_id_number"/>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-8551">識別碼號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8551">ID Number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-8552">識別</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8552">Identification</span></span>

## <a name="philippines-unified-multi-purpose-identification-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-8555">菲律賓統一多用途識別號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8555">Philippines unified multi-purpose identification number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-8556">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8556">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-8557">以連字號隔開的12位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8557">12 digits separated by hyphens</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-8558">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8558">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-8559">12位數：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8559">12 digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-8560">四位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8560">four digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-8561">連字號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8561">a hyphen</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-8562">七位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8562">seven digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-8563">連字號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8563">a hyphen</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-8564">一個數位</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8564">one digit</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-8565">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8565">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-8566">否</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8566">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-8567">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8567">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-8568">當鄰近性300個字元以內時，DLP 原則就會偵測到這種敏感資訊類型的信賴度。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8568">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-8569">正則運算式 Regex_philippines_unified_id 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8569">The regular expression Regex_philippines_unified_id finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-8570">會找到來自 Keyword_philippines_id 的關鍵字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8570">A keyword from Keyword_philippines_id is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Philippines Unified Multi-Purpose ID number -->
<Entity id="019b39dd-8c25-4765-91a3-d9c6baf3c3b3" recommendedConfidence="75" patternsProximity="300">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
     <IdMatch idRef="Regex_philippines_unified_id"/>
     <Match idRef="Keyword_philippines_id"/>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-8571">關鍵字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8571">Keywords</span></span>
   
#### <a name="keyword_philippines_id"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-8572">Keyword_philippines_id</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8572">Keyword_philippines_id</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-8573">統一的多重用途識別碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8573">Unified Multi-Purpose ID</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-8574">UMID</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8574">UMID</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-8575">身份證</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8575">Identity Card</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-8576">Pinag-isang 多 Layunin 識別碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8576">Pinag-isang Multi-Layunin ID</span></span>

## <a name="poland-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-8577">波蘭駕照編號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8577">Poland driver's license number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-8578">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8578">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-8579">包含兩個正斜線的14位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8579">14 digits containing two forward slashes</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-8580">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8580">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-8581">14位數和兩個正斜線：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8581">14 digits and two forward slashes:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-8582">五位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8582">five digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-8583">一個正斜線</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8583">a forward slash</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-8584">兩位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8584">two digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-8585">一個正斜線</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8585">a forward slash</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-8586">七位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8586">seven digits</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-8587">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8587">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-8588">否</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8588">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-8589">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8589">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-8590">當鄰近性300個字元以內時，DLP 原則就會偵測到這種敏感資訊類型的信賴度。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8590">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-8591">正則運算式會  `Regex_poland_eu_driver's_license_number` 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8591">The regular expression  `Regex_poland_eu_driver's_license_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-8592">`Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number`找到或的關鍵字 `Keywords_poland_eu_driver's_license_number` 。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8592">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` or `Keywords_poland_eu_driver's_license_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Poland Driver's License Number -->
      <Entity id="24d51f99-ee9e-4060-a077-cae58cab1ee4" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_poland_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_poland_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="poland-identity-card"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-8716">波蘭身分識別卡片</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8716">Poland identity card</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-8717">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8717">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-8718">三個字母和六位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8718">three letters and six digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-8719">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8719">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-8720">三個字母 (不區分大小寫) 後接六位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8720">three letters (not case-sensitive) followed by six digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-8721">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8721">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-8722">是</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8722">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-8723">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8723">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-8724">當鄰近性300個字元以內時，DLP 原則就會偵測到這種敏感資訊類型的信賴度。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8724">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-8725">函數 Func_polish_national_id 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8725">The function Func_polish_national_id finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-8726">會找到來自 Keyword_polish_national_id_passport_number 的關鍵字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8726">A keyword from Keyword_polish_national_id_passport_number is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-8727">校驗和通過。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8727">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Poland Identity Card-->
<Entity id="25E64989-ED5D-40CA-A939-6C14183BB7BF" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_polish_national_id" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_polish_national_id_passport_number" />
      </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-8728">關鍵字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8728">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_poland_national_id_passport_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-8729">Keyword_poland_national_id_passport_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8729">Keyword_poland_national_id_passport_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-8730">Dowód osobisty</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8730">Dowód osobisty</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-8731">轉寄 dowodu osobistego</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8731">Numer dowodu osobistego</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-8732">Nazwa i 轉寄 dowodu osobistego</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8732">Nazwa i numer dowodu osobistego</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-8733">Nazwa i nr dowodu osobistego</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8733">Nazwa i nr dowodu osobistego</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-8734">Nazwa i nr dowodu tożsamości</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8734">Nazwa i nr dowodu tożsamości</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-8735">Dowód Tożsamości</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8735">Dowód Tożsamości</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-8736">道鐘斯指數。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8736">dow.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="94f34-8737">作業系統。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8737">os.</span></span>

   
## <a name="poland-national-id-pesel"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-8738">波蘭國家識別碼 (PESEL) </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8738">Poland national ID (PESEL)</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-8739">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8739">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-8740">11位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8740">11 digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-8741">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8741">Pattern</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-8742">六位數代表出生日期格式 YYMMDD</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8742">six digits representing date of birth in the format YYMMDD</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-8743">四位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8743">four digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-8744">一個檢查碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8744">one check digit</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-8745">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8745">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-8746">是</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8746">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-8747">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8747">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-8748">當鄰近性300個字元以內時，DLP 原則就會偵測到這種敏感資訊類型：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8748">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-8749">函數 Func_pesel_identification_number 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8749">The function Func_pesel_identification_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-8750">會找到來自 Keyword_pesel_identification_number 的關鍵字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8750">A keyword from Keyword_pesel_identification_number is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-8751">校驗和通過。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8751">The checksum passes.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-8752">當鄰近性300個字元以內時，DLP 原則就會偵測到這種敏感資訊類型的信賴度。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8752">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-8753">函數 Func_pesel_identification_number 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8753">The function Func_pesel_identification_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-8754">校驗和通過。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8754">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Poland National ID (PESEL) -->
      <Entity id="E3AAF206-4297-412F-9E06-BA8487E22456" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_pesel_identification_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_pesel_identification_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_pesel_identification_number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="poland-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-8766">波蘭護照號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8766">Poland passport number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="94f34-8767">這個敏感資訊類型實體包含在歐盟護照號碼機密資訊類型中。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8767">This sensitive information type entity is included in the EU Passport Number sensitive information type.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="94f34-8768">它可以做為獨立的機密資訊類型實體。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8768">It's available as a stand-alone sensitive information type entity.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-8769">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8769">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-8770">兩個字母和七位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8770">two letters and seven digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-8771">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8771">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-8772">兩個字母 (不區分大小寫) 後接7位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8772">Two letters (not case-sensitive) followed by seven digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-8773">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8773">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-8774">是</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8774">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-8775">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8775">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-8776">當鄰近性300個字元以內時，DLP 原則就會偵測到這種敏感資訊類型：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8776">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-8777">函數 `Func_polish_passport_number_v2` 會找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8777">The function `Func_polish_passport_number_v2` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-8778">校驗和通過。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8778">The checksum passes.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-8779">`Keywords_eu_passport_number`找到或的關鍵字 `Keyword_polish_national_passport_number` 。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8779">A keyword from `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keyword_polish_national_passport_number` is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-8780">找到來自的關鍵字 `Keywords_eu_passport_date` 。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8780">A keyword from `Keywords_eu_passport_date` is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-8781">當鄰近性300個字元以內時，DLP 原則就會偵測到這種敏感資訊類型的信賴度。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8781">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-8782">函數 `Func_polish_passport_number_v2` 會找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8782">The function `Func_polish_passport_number_v2` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-8783">校驗和通過。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8783">The checksum passes.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-8784">`Keywords_eu_passport_number`找到或的關鍵字 `Keyword_polish_national_passport_number` 。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8784">A keyword from `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keyword_polish_national_passport_number` is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-8785">DLP 原則在接近300個字元以內時，偵測到此敏感資訊類型的信賴度很低：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8785">A DLP policy has low confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-8786">函數 `Func_polish_passport_number_v2` 會找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8786">The function `Func_polish_passport_number_v2` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-8787">校驗和通過。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8787">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Poland Passport Number -->
      <Entity id="03937FB5-D2B6-4487-B61F-0F8BFF7C3517" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_polish_passport_number_v2" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_date" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keyword_polish_national_passport_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_polish_passport_number_v2" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keyword_polish_national_passport_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_polish_passport_number_v2" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="poland-regon-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-8813">波蘭 REGON 編號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8813">Poland REGON number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="94f34-8814">此機密資訊類型僅可用於下列專案：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8814">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-8815">資料遺失防護原則</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8815">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-8816">通訊相容性原則</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8816">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-8817">資訊管理</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8817">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-8818">記錄管理</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8818">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-8819">Microsoft cloud app security</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8819">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-8820">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8820">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-8821">9位數或14位數的數位</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8821">9-digit or 14-digit number</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-8822">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8822">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-8823">九位數數位或14位數：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8823">nine digit or 14-digit number:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-8824">九位數或</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8824">nine digits or</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-8825">九位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8825">nine digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-8826">字元</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8826">hyphen</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-8827">五位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8827">five digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-8828">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8828">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-8829">是</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8829">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-8830">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8830">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-8831">當鄰近性300個字元以內時，DLP 原則就會偵測到這種敏感資訊類型：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8831">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-8832">函數 Func_polish_regon_number 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8832">The function Func_polish_regon_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-8833">會找到來自 Keywords_polish_regon_number 的關鍵字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8833">A keyword from Keywords_polish_regon_number is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-8834">DLP 原則在接近300個字元以內時，偵測到此敏感資訊類型的信賴度很低：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8834">A DLP policy has low confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-8835">函數 Func_polish_regon_number 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8835">The function Func_polish_regon_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Polish REGON Number  -->
      <Entity id="fc87b421-f437-4f8b-b739-29a735ead0d9" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_polish_regon_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_polish_regon_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_polish_regon_number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-8841">統計否</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8841">statistical no</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-8842">regon 編號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8842">regon number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-8849">numeru regon</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8849">numeru regon</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-8850">numerstatystyczny#</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8850">numerstatystyczny#</span></span>

## <a name="poland-tax-identification-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-8852">波蘭納稅識別號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8852">Poland tax identification number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="94f34-8853">此機密資訊類型僅可用於下列專案：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8853">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-8854">資料遺失防護原則</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8854">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-8855">通訊相容性原則</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8855">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-8856">資訊管理</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8856">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-8857">記錄管理</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8857">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-8858">Microsoft cloud app security</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8858">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-8859">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8859">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-8860">11位數，不含空格或分隔符號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8860">11 digits with no spaces or delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-8861">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8861">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-8862">11位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8862">11 digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-8863">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8863">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-8864">是</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8864">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-8865">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8865">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-8866">當鄰近性300個字元以內時，DLP 原則就會偵測到這種敏感資訊類型：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8866">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-8867">函數  `Func_poland_eu_tax_file_number` 會找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8867">The function  `Func_poland_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-8868">找到來自的關鍵字  `Keywords_poland_eu_tax_file_number` 。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8868">A keyword from  `Keywords_poland_eu_tax_file_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
  
```xml
      <!-- Poland Tax Identification Number -->
      <Entity id="1ff28b4d-40f2-49e9-b677-9606a88e2bca" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_poland_eu_tax_file_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_poland_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-8869">關鍵字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8869">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keywords_poland_eu_tax_file_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-8870">Keywords_poland_eu_tax_file_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8870">Keywords_poland_eu_tax_file_number</span></span>

## <a name="portugal-citizen-card-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-8898">葡萄牙公民卡片號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8898">Portugal citizen card number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-8899">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8899">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-8900">八位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8900">eight digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-8901">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8901">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-8902">八位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8902">eight digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-8903">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8903">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-8904">否</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8904">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-8905">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8905">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-8906">當鄰近性300個字元以內時，DLP 原則就會偵測到這種敏感資訊類型：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8906">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-8907">正則運算式 Regex_portugal_citizen_card 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8907">The regular expression Regex_portugal_citizen_card finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-8908">會找到來自 Keyword_portugal_citizen_card 的關鍵字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8908">A keyword from Keyword_portugal_citizen_card is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Portugal Citizen Card Number -->
<Entity id="91a7ece2-add4-4986-9a15-c84544d81ecd" recommendedConfidence="85" patternsProximity="300">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
     <IdMatch idRef="Regex_portugal_citizen_card"/>
     <Match idRef="Keyword_portugal_citizen_card"/>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="portugal-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-8928">葡萄牙駕駛執照號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8928">Portugal driver's license number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-8929">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8929">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-8930">兩個模式：兩個字母，後面加上以特殊字元顯示的5-8 位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8930">two patterns - two letters followed by 5-8 digits with special characters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-8931">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8931">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-8932">模式1：兩個字母后接以特殊字元的5/6：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8932">Pattern 1: Two letters followed by 5/6 with special characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-8933">兩個字母 (不區分大小寫) </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8933">Two letters (not case-sensitive)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-8934">連字號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8934">A hyphen</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-8935">五或六位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8935">Five or Six digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-8936">一個空格</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8936">A space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-8937">一個數位</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8937">One digit</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-8938">模式2：一個字母后接6/8 位數，含特殊字元：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8938">Pattern 2: One letter followed by 6/8 digits with special characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-8939">一個字母 (不區分大小寫) </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8939">One letter (not case-sensitive)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-8940">連字號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8940">A hyphen</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-8941">六位數或八位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8941">Six or eight digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-8942">一個空格</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8942">A space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-8943">一個數位</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8943">One digit</span></span>

    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-8944">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8944">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-8945">否</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8945">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-8946">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8946">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-8947">當鄰近性300個字元以內時，DLP 原則就會偵測到這種敏感資訊類型的信賴度。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8947">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-8948">正則運算式會  `Regex_portugal_eu_driver's_license_number` 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8948">The regular expression  `Regex_portugal_eu_driver's_license_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-8949">`Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number`找到或的關鍵字 `Keywords_portugal_eu_driver's_license_number` 。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-8949">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` or `Keywords_portugal_eu_driver's_license_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Portugal Driver's License Number -->
      <Entity id="977f1e5a-2c33-4bcc-b516-95bb275cff23" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_portugal_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_portugal_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```
