## <a name="portugal-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-9081">葡萄牙護照號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-9081">Portugal passport number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-9082">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-9082">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-9083">一個字母后接六位數，不含空格或分隔符號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-9083">one letter followed by six digits with no spaces or delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-9084">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-9084">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-9085">一個字母后接六位數：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-9085">one letter followed by six digits:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-9086">一個字母 (不區分大小寫) </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-9086">one letter (not case-sensitive)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-9087">六位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-9087">six digits</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-9088">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-9088">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-9089">否</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-9089">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-9090">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-9090">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-9091">當鄰近性300個字元以內時，DLP 原則就會偵測到這種敏感資訊類型：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-9091">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-9092">正則運算式會  `Regex_portugal_eu_passport_number` 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-9092">The regular expression  `Regex_portugal_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-9093">`Keywords_eu_passport_number`找到或的關鍵字 `Keywords_portugal_eu_passport_number` 。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-9093">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_portugal_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-9094">正則運算式 `Regex_eu_passport_date1` 會發現日期格式為 DD YYYY 或關鍵字 from `Keywords_eu_passport_date`</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-9094">The regular expression `Regex_eu_passport_date1` finds date in the format DD.MM.YYYY or a keyword from `Keywords_eu_passport_date` is found</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-9095">當鄰近性300個字元以內時，DLP 原則就會偵測到這種敏感資訊類型的信賴度。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-9095">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-9096">正則運算式會  `Regex_portugal_eu_passport_number` 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-9096">The regular expression  `Regex_portugal_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-9097">`Keywords_eu_passport_number`找到或的關鍵字 `Keywords_portugal_eu_passport_number` 。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-9097">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_portugal_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span>
    
```xml
      <!-- Portugal Passport Number -->
      <Entity id="080a52fd-a7bc-431e-b54d-51f08f59db11" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_portugal_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_portugal_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Regex_eu_passport_date1" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_date" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_portugal_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_portugal_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="portugal-tax-identification-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-9124">葡萄牙納稅識別號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-9124">Portugal tax identification number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-9125">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-9125">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-9126">包含選擇性空格的九位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-9126">nine digits with optional spaces</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-9127">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-9127">Pattern</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-9128">三位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-9128">three digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-9129">選擇性的空格</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-9129">an optional space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-9130">三位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-9130">three digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-9131">選擇性的空格</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-9131">an optional space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-9132">三位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-9132">three digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-9133">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-9133">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-9134">是</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-9134">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-9135">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-9135">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-9136">當鄰近性300個字元以內時，DLP 原則就會偵測到這種敏感資訊類型：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-9136">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-9137">函數  `Func_portugal_eu_tax_file_number` 會找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-9137">The function  `Func_portugal_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-9138">找到來自的關鍵字  `Keywords_portugal_eu_tax_file_number` 。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-9138">A keyword from  `Keywords_portugal_eu_tax_file_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="94f34-9139">DLP 原則在接近300個字元以內時，偵測到此敏感資訊類型的信賴度很低：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-9139">A DLP policy has low confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-9140">函數  `Func_portugal_eu_tax_file_number` 會找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-9140">The function  `Func_portugal_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Portugal Tax Identification Number -->
      <Entity id="65372402-3131-4f1e-9983-4439841d1f15" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_portugal_eu_tax_file_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_portugal_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_portugal_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="romania-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-9165">羅馬尼亞駕照編號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-9165">Romania driver's license number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-9166">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-9166">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-9167">一個字元後接八位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-9167">one character followed by eight digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-9168">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-9168">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-9169">一個字元後接八位數：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-9169">one character followed by eight digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-9170">一個字母 (不區分大小寫) 或數位</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-9170">one letter (not case-sensitive) or digit</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-9171">八位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-9171">eight digits</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-9172">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-9172">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-9173">否</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-9173">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-9174">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-9174">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-9175">當鄰近性300個字元以內時，DLP 原則就會偵測到這種敏感資訊類型的信賴度。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-9175">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-9176">正則運算式會  `Regex_romania_eu_driver's_license_number` 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-9176">The regular expression  `Regex_romania_eu_driver's_license_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-9177">`Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number`找到或的關鍵字 `Keywords_romania_eu_driver's_license_number` 。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-9177">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` or `Keywords_romania_eu_driver's_license_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Romania Driver's License Number -->
      <Entity id="b5511ace-2fd8-4ae4-b6fc-c7c6e4689e3c" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_romania_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_romania_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="romania-personal-numeric-code-cnp"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-9305">羅馬尼亞個人數位代碼 (CNP) </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-9305">Romania personal numeric code (CNP)</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="94f34-9306">此機密資訊類型僅可用於下列專案：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-9306">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-9307">資料遺失防護原則</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-9307">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-9308">通訊相容性原則</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-9308">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-9309">資訊管理</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-9309">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-9310">記錄管理</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-9310">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-9311">Microsoft cloud app security</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-9311">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-9312">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-9312">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-9313">13位數，不含空格及分隔符號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-9313">13 digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-9314">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-9314">Pattern</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-9315">1-9 的一個數位</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-9315">one digit from 1-9</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-9316">六位數代表出生日期 (YYMMDD) </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-9316">six digits representing date of birth (YYMMDD)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-9317">兩位數，可以是01-52 或99</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-9317">two digits, which can be 01-52 or 99</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-9318">四位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-9318">four digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-9319">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-9319">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-9320">是</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-9320">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-9321">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-9321">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-9322">當鄰近性300個字元以內時，DLP 原則就會偵測到這種敏感資訊類型：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-9322">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-9323">函數  `Func_romania_eu_national_id_card` 會找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-9323">The function  `Func_romania_eu_national_id_card` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-9324">找到來自的關鍵字  `Keywords_romania_eu_national_id_card` 。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-9324">A keyword from  `Keywords_romania_eu_national_id_card` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="94f34-9325">當鄰近性300個字元以內時，DLP 原則就會偵測到這種敏感資訊類型的信賴度。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-9325">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-9326">函數  `Func_romania_eu_national_id_card` 會找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-9326">The function  `Func_romania_eu_national_id_card` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Romania Personal Numerical Code (CNP) -->
      <Entity id="eb5fa399-fe28-4c67-8188-d63a616ed89c" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_romania_eu_national_id_card" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_romania_eu_national_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_romania_eu_national_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="romania-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-9377">羅馬尼亞護照號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-9377">Romania passport number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-9378">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-9378">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-9379">8或9位數，不含空格及分隔符號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-9379">eight or nine digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-9380">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-9380">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-9381">8或9位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-9381">eight or nine digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-9382">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-9382">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-9383">否</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-9383">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-9384">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-9384">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-9385">當鄰近性300個字元以內時，DLP 原則就會偵測到這種敏感資訊類型：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-9385">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-9386">正則運算式會  `Regex_romania_eu_passport_number` 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-9386">The regular expression  `Regex_romania_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-9387">`Keywords_eu_passport_number`找到或的關鍵字 `Keywords_romania_eu_passport_number` 。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-9387">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_romania_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-9388">正則運算式 `Regex_romania_eu_passport_date` 會以 DD MMM/MMM YY 的格式來尋找日期 (範例-01 年2月/2 月 10) 或找到關鍵字]。 `Keywords_eu_passport_date`</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-9388">The regular expression `Regex_romania_eu_passport_date` finds date in the format DD MMM/MMM YY (Example- 01 FEB/FEB 10) or a keyword from `Keywords_eu_passport_date` is found</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-9389">當鄰近性300個字元以內時，DLP 原則就會偵測到這種敏感資訊類型的信賴度。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-9389">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-9390">正則運算式會  `Regex_romania_eu_passport_number` 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-9390">The regular expression  `Regex_romania_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-9391">`Keywords_eu_passport_number`找到或的關鍵字 `Keywords_romania_eu_passport_number` 。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-9391">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_romania_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Romania Passport Number -->
      <Entity id="5d31b90c-7fe2-4a76-a14b-767b8fd19d6c" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_romania_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_romania_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Regex_romania_eu_passport_date" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_date" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_romania_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_romania_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-9418">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-9418">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-9428">當鄰近性300個字元以內時，DLP 原則就會偵測到這種敏感資訊類型的信賴度。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-9428">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-9429">Regex Regex_Russian_Passport_Number_Domestic 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-9429">The regex Regex_Russian_Passport_Number_Domestic finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-9430">會找到來自 Keyword_Russian_Passport_Number 的關鍵字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-9430">A keyword from Keyword_Russian_Passport_Number is found.</span></span>

```xml
      <Entity id="76ec2f5d-cedb-48e1-8070-1998794af445" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">

          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_Russian_Passport_Number_Domestic" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_Russian_Passport_Number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-9450">通訊相容性原則</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-9450">communication compliance policies</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-9456">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-9456">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-9457">九位數數位：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-9457">nine-digit number:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-9458">兩位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-9458">two digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-9459">選擇性空格或連字號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-9459">an optional space or hyphen</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-9460">七位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-9460">seven digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-9461">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-9461">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-9462">否</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-9462">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-9463">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-9463">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-9464">當鄰近性300個字元以內時，DLP 原則就會偵測到這種敏感資訊類型的信賴度。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-9464">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-9465">Regex Regex_Russian_Passport_Number_International 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-9465">The regex Regex_Russian_Passport_Number_International finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-9466">會找到來自 Keyword_Russian_Passport_Number 的關鍵字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-9466">A keyword from Keyword_Russian_Passport_Number is found.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Russian Passport Number International -->
      <Entity id="ac5f4878-75e4-4b82-af2d-02e13ea9f411" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_Russian_Passport_Number_International" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_Russian_Passport_Number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="saudi-arabia-national-id"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-9483">沙烏地阿拉伯國際身分識別</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-9483">Saudi Arabia National ID</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-9484">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-9484">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-9485">10位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-9485">10 digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-9486">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-9486">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-9487">10個連續數位</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-9487">10 consecutive digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-9488">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-9488">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-9489">否</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-9489">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-9490">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-9490">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-9491">當鄰近性300個字元以內時，DLP 原則就會偵測到這種敏感資訊類型的信賴度。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-9491">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-9492">正則運算式 Regex_saudi_arabia_national_id 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-9492">The regular expression Regex_saudi_arabia_national_id finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-9493">會找到來自 Keyword_saudi_arabia_national_id 的關鍵字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-9493">A keyword from Keyword_saudi_arabia_national_id is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Saudi Arabia National ID -->
<Entity id="8c5a0ba8-404a-41a3-8871-746aa21ee6c0" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
    <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Regex_saudi_arabia_national_id" />
        <Any minMatches="1">
          <Match idRef="Keyword_saudi_arabia_national_id" />
        </Any>
    </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-9498">識別碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-9498">ID number</span></span>

## <a name="singapore-national-registration-identity-card-nric-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-9500">新加坡國家註冊身分識別卡 (NRIC) 號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-9500">Singapore national registration identity card (NRIC) number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-9501">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-9501">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-9502">九個字母和數位</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-9502">nine letters and digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-9503">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-9503">Pattern</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-9504">九個字母和數位：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-9504">nine letters and digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-9505">字母 "F"、"G"、"S" 或 "T" (不區分大小寫) </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-9505">the letter "F", "G", "S", or "T" (not case-sensitive)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-9506">七位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-9506">seven digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-9507">字母檢查碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-9507">an alphabetic check digit</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-9508">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-9508">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-9509">是</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-9509">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-9510">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-9510">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-9511">當鄰近性300個字元以內時，DLP 原則就會偵測到這種敏感資訊類型：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-9511">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-9512">正則運算式 Regex_singapore_nric 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-9512">The regular expression Regex_singapore_nric finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-9513">會找到來自 Keyword_singapore_nric 的關鍵字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-9513">A keyword from Keyword_singapore_nric is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-9514">校驗和通過。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-9514">The checksum passes.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-9515">當鄰近性300個字元以內時，DLP 原則就會偵測到這種敏感資訊類型的信賴度。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-9515">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-9516">正則運算式 Regex_singapore_nric 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-9516">The regular expression Regex_singapore_nric finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-9517">校驗和通過。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-9517">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Singapore National Registration Identity Card (NRIC) Number -->
<Entity id="cead390a-dd83-4856-9751-fb6dc98c34da" recommendedConfidence="75" patternsProximity="300">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
     <IdMatch idRef="Regex_singapore_nric"/>
     <Match idRef="Keyword_singapore_nric"/>
  </Pattern>
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
     <IdMatch idRef="Regex_singapore_nric"/>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-9518">關鍵字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-9518">Keywords</span></span>

## <a name="slovakia-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-9528">斯洛伐克駕照編號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-9528">Slovakia driver's license number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-9529">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-9529">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-9530">一個字元後接7位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-9530">one character followed by seven digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-9531">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-9531">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-9532">一個字元後接7位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-9532">one character followed by seven digits</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-9533">一個字母 (不區分大小寫) 或數位</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-9533">one letter (not case-sensitive) or digit</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-9534">七位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-9534">seven digits</span></span> 
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-9535">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-9535">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-9536">否</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-9536">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-9537">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-9537">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-9538">當鄰近性300個字元以內時，DLP 原則就會偵測到這種敏感資訊類型的信賴度。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-9538">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-9539">正則運算式會  `Regex_slovakia_eu_driver's_license_number` 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-9539">The regular expression  `Regex_slovakia_eu_driver's_license_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-9540">`Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number`找到或的關鍵字 `Keywords_slovakia_eu_driver's_license_number` 。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-9540">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` or `Keywords_slovakia_eu_driver's_license_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Slovakia Driver's License Number -->
      <Entity id="14240c22-b6de-4ce5-a90b-137f74252513" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_slovakia_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_slovakia_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="slovakia-personal-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-9666">斯洛伐克個人號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-9666">Slovakia personal number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="94f34-9667">此機密資訊類型僅可用於下列專案：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-9667">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-9668">資料遺失防護原則</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-9668">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-9669">通訊相容性原則</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-9669">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-9670">資訊管理</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-9670">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-9671">記錄管理</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-9671">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-9672">Microsoft cloud app security</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-9672">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-9673">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-9673">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-9674">包含選擇性反斜線的九位數或十位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-9674">nine or ten digits containing optional backslash</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-9675">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-9675">Pattern</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-9676">六位數代表出生日期</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-9676">six digits representing date of birth</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-9677">選用斜線 (/) </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-9677">optional slash (/)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-9678">三位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-9678">three digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-9679">一個選擇性檢查碼碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-9679">one optional check digit</span></span>
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-9680">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-9680">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-9681">是</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-9681">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-9682">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-9682">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-9683">當鄰近性300個字元以內時，DLP 原則就會偵測到這種敏感資訊類型：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-9683">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-9684">函數  `Func_slovakia_eu_national_id_card` 會找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-9684">The function  `Func_slovakia_eu_national_id_card` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-9685">找到來自的關鍵字  `Keywords_slovakia_eu_national_id_card` 。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-9685">A keyword from  `Keywords_slovakia_eu_national_id_card` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="94f34-9686">DLP 原則在接近300個字元以內時，偵測到此敏感資訊類型的信賴度很低：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-9686">A DLP policy has low confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-9687">函數  `Func_slovakia_eu_national_id_card` 會找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-9687">The function  `Func_slovakia_eu_national_id_card` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Slovakia Personal Number -->
      <Entity id="951c26b7-3b35-4f73-924b-15dd599cb9ab" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_slovakia_eu_national_id_card" />

```

## <a name="slovakia-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-9734">斯洛伐克護照號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-9734">Slovakia passport number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-9735">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-9735">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-9736">一個數位或字母后接7位數，不含空格或分隔符號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-9736">one digit or letter followed by seven digits with no spaces or delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-9737">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-9737">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-9738">一個數位或字母 (不區分大小寫) 後接7位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-9738">one digit or letter (not case-sensitive) followed by seven digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-9739">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-9739">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-9740">否</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-9740">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-9741">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-9741">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-9742">當鄰近性300個字元以內時，DLP 原則就會偵測到這種敏感資訊類型：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-9742">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-9743">正則運算式會  `Regex_slovakia_eu_passport_number` 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-9743">The regular expression  `Regex_slovakia_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-9744">`Keywords_eu_passport_number`找到或的關鍵字 `Keywords_slovakia_eu_passport_number` 。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-9744">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_slovakia_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-9745">正則運算式 `Regex_eu_passport_date1` 會發現日期格式為 DD YYYY 或關鍵字 from `Keywords_eu_passport_date`</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-9745">The regular expression `Regex_eu_passport_date1` finds date in the format DD.MM.YYYY or a keyword from `Keywords_eu_passport_date` is found</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-9746">當鄰近性300個字元以內時，DLP 原則就會偵測到這種敏感資訊類型的信賴度。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-9746">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-9747">正則運算式會  `Regex_slovakia_eu_passport_number` 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-9747">The regular expression  `Regex_slovakia_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-9748">`Keywords_eu_passport_number`找到或的關鍵字 `Keywords_slovakia_eu_passport_number` 。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-9748">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_slovakia_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Slovakia Passport Number -->
      <Entity id="238e1f08-d80e-4793-af33-9b57918335b7" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_slovakia_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_slovakia_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Regex_eu_passport_date1" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_date" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_slovakia_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_slovakia_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-9771">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-9771">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-9772">九位數，不含空格及分隔符號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-9772">nine digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-9773">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-9773">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-9774">九位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-9774">nine digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-9775">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-9775">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-9778">當鄰近性300個字元以內時，DLP 原則就會偵測到這種敏感資訊類型的信賴度。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-9778">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-9779">正則運算式會  `Regex_slovenia_eu_driver's_license_number` 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-9779">The regular expression  `Regex_slovenia_eu_driver's_license_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-9780">`Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number`找到或的關鍵字 `Keywords_slovenia_eu_driver's_license_number` 。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-9780">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` or `Keywords_slovenia_eu_driver's_license_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Slovenia Driver's License Number -->
      <Entity id="d5bc089a-f2ee-433d-a6b1-5c253051d6f2" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">

```

## <a name="slovenia-unique-master-citizen-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-9907">斯洛維尼亞唯一主公民號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-9907">Slovenia Unique Master Citizen Number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="94f34-9908">此機密資訊類型僅可用於下列專案：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-9908">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-9909">資料遺失防護原則</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-9909">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-9910">通訊相容性原則</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-9910">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-9911">資訊管理</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-9911">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-9912">記錄管理</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-9912">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-9913">Microsoft cloud app security</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-9913">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-9914">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-9914">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-9915">13位數，不含空格或分隔符號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-9915">13 digits without spaces or delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-9916">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-9916">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-9917">指定的模式中的13位數：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-9917">13 digits in the specified pattern:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-9918">對應至出生日期 (DDMMLLL) （其中 "LLL" 會對應至出生年份的後三位數）的7位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-9918">seven digits that correspond to the birth date (DDMMLLL) where "LLL" corresponds to the last three digits of the birth year</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-9919">對應至出生 "50" 區域的兩位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-9919">two digits that correspond to the area of birth "50"</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-9920">對應至同一天出生的人的性別和序陣列合的三位數 (000-499 （適用于雌雄) 的男和500-999）</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-9920">three digits that correspond to a combination of gender and serial number for persons born on the same day (000-499 for male and 500-999 for female)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-9921">一個檢查碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-9921">one check digit</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-9922">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-9922">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-9923">是</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-9923">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-9924">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-9924">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-9925">當鄰近性300個字元以內時，DLP 原則就會偵測到這種敏感資訊類型：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-9925">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-9926">函數  `Func_slovenia_eu_national_id_card` 會找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-9926">The function  `Func_slovenia_eu_national_id_card` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-9927">找到來自的關鍵字  `Keywords_slovenia_eu_national_id_card` 。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-9927">A keyword from  `Keywords_slovenia_eu_national_id_card` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="94f34-9928">當鄰近性300個字元以內時，DLP 原則就會偵測到這種敏感資訊類型的信賴度。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-9928">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-9929">函數  `Func_slovenia_eu_national_id_card` 會找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-9929">The function  `Func_slovenia_eu_national_id_card` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Slovenia Unique Master Citizen Number -->
      <Entity id="68948b27-803d-41e4-adf1-13e05eb541bb" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_slovenia_eu_national_id_card" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_slovenia_eu_national_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_slovenia_eu_national_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="slovenia-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-9957">斯洛維尼亞護照號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-9957">Slovenia passport number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-9958">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-9958">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-9959">兩個字母后接7位數，不含空格或分隔符號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-9959">two letters followed by seven digits with no spaces or delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-9960">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-9960">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-9961">兩個字母后接7位數：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-9961">two letters followed by seven digits:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-9962">字母 "P"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-9962">the letter "P"</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-9963">單一大寫字母</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-9963">one uppercase letter</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-9964">七位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-9964">seven digits</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-9965">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-9965">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-9966">否</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-9966">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-9967">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-9967">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-9968">當鄰近性300個字元以內時，DLP 原則就會偵測到這種敏感資訊類型：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-9968">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-9969">正則運算式會  `Regex_slovenia_eu_passport_number` 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-9969">The regular expression  `Regex_slovenia_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-9970">`Keywords_eu_passport_number`找到或的關鍵字 `Keywords_slovenia_eu_passport_number` 。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-9970">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_slovenia_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-9971">正則運算式 `Regex_eu_passport_date1` 會發現日期格式為 DD YYYY 或關鍵字 from `Keywords_eu_passport_date`</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-9971">The regular expression `Regex_eu_passport_date1` finds date in the format DD.MM.YYYY or a keyword from `Keywords_eu_passport_date` is found</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-9972">當鄰近性300個字元以內時，DLP 原則就會偵測到這種敏感資訊類型的信賴度。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-9972">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-9973">正則運算式會  `Regex_slovenia_eu_passport_number` 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-9973">The regular expression  `Regex_slovenia_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-9974">`Keywords_eu_passport_number`找到或的關鍵字 `Keywords_slovenia_eu_passport_number` 。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-9974">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_slovenia_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Slovenia Passport Number -->
      <Entity id="235b7976-7bbe-4df5-bb40-08678e749d1a" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_slovenia_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_slovenia_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Regex_eu_passport_date1" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_date" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_slovenia_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_slovenia_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="slovenia-tax-identification-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-9997">斯洛維尼亞納稅識別號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-9997">Slovenia tax identification number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="94f34-9998">此機密資訊類型僅可用於下列專案：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-9998">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-9999">資料遺失防護原則</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-9999">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-10000">通訊相容性原則</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10000">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-10001">資訊管理</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10001">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-10002">記錄管理</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10002">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-10003">Microsoft cloud app security</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10003">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-10004">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10004">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-10005">八位數沒有空格或分隔符號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10005">eight digits with no spaces or delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-10006">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10006">Pattern</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-10007">1-9 的一個數位</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10007">one digit from 1-9</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-10008">六位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10008">six digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-10009">一個檢查碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10009">one check digit</span></span>
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-10010">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10010">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-10011">是</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10011">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-10012">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10012">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-10013">當鄰近性300個字元以內時，DLP 原則就會偵測到這種敏感資訊類型：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10013">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-10014">函數  `Func_slovenia_eu_tax_file_number` 會找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10014">The function  `Func_slovenia_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-10015">找到來自的關鍵字  `Keywords_slovenia_eu_tax_file_number` 。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10015">A keyword from  `Keywords_slovenia_eu_tax_file_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="94f34-10016">DLP 原則在接近300個字元以內時，偵測到此敏感資訊類型的信賴度很低：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10016">A DLP policy has low confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-10017">函數  `Func_slovenia_eu_tax_file_number` 會找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10017">The function  `Func_slovenia_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Slovenia Tax Identification Number -->
      <Entity id="e47b071e-c352-4d70-8241-8c215ad65505" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_slovenia_eu_tax_file_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_slovenia_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_slovenia_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-10018">關鍵字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10018">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keywords_slovenia_eu_tax_file_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-10019">Keywords_slovenia_eu_tax_file_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10019">Keywords_slovenia_eu_tax_file_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-10020">davčna številka</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10020">davčna številka</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-10022">številka davčne datoteke</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10022">številka davčne datoteke</span></span>

## <a name="south-africa-identification-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-10041">南非識別號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10041">South Africa identification number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-10042">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10042">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-10043">可以包含空格的13位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10043">13 digits that may contain spaces</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-10044">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10044">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-10045">13位數：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10045">13 digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-10046">YYMMDD 格式的六位數（出生日期）</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10046">six digits in the format YYMMDD, which are the date of birth</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-10047">四位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10047">four digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-10048">單一數位的公民指示器</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10048">a single-digit citizenship indicator</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-10049">數位 "8" 或 "9"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10049">the digit "8" or "9"</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-10050">一位數，也就是校驗和位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10050">one digit, which is a checksum digit</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-10051">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10051">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-10052">是</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10052">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-10053">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10053">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-10054">當鄰近性300個字元以內時，DLP 原則就會偵測到這種敏感資訊類型：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10054">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-10055">函數 Func_south_africa_identification_number 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10055">The function Func_south_africa_identification_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-10056">會找到來自 Keyword_south_africa_identification_number 的關鍵字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10056">A keyword from Keyword_south_africa_identification_number is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-10057">校驗和通過。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10057">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- South Africa Identification Number -->
<Entity id="e2adf7cb-8ea6-4048-a2ed-d89eb65f2780" recommendedConfidence="85" patternsProximity="300">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
     <IdMatch idRef="Func_south_africa_identification_number"/>
     <Match idRef="Keyword_south_africa_identification_number"/>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-10062">識別</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10062">Identification</span></span> 
   
## <a name="south-korea-resident-registration-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-10063">韓國居民登記號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10063">South Korea resident registration number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-10064">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10064">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-10065">13位數包含連字號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10065">13 digits containing a hyphen</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-10066">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10066">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-10067">13位數：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10067">13 digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-10068">YYMMDD 格式的六位數（出生日期）</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10068">six digits in the format YYMMDD, which are the date of birth</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-10069">連字號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10069">a hyphen</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-10070">一個數位是由世紀和性別決定</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10070">one digit determined by the century and gender</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-10071">四位數的出生區功能變數代碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10071">four-digit region-of-birth code</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-10072">一種用來區分先前號碼相同之人員的數位</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10072">one digit used to differentiate people for whom the preceding numbers are identical</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-10073">檢查碼。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10073">a check digit.</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-10074">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10074">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-10075">是</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10075">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-10076">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10076">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-10077">當鄰近性300個字元以內時，DLP 原則就會偵測到這種敏感資訊類型：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10077">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-10078">函數 Func_south_korea_resident_number 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10078">The function Func_south_korea_resident_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-10079">會找到來自 Keyword_south_korea_resident_number 的關鍵字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10079">A keyword from Keyword_south_korea_resident_number is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-10080">校驗和通過。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10080">The checksum passes.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-10081">當鄰近性300個字元以內時，DLP 原則就會偵測到這種敏感資訊類型的信賴度。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10081">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-10082">函數 Func_south_korea_resident_number 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10082">The function Func_south_korea_resident_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-10083">校驗和通過。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10083">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- South Korea Resident Registration Number -->
<Entity id="5b802e18-ba80-44c4-bc83-bf2ad36ae36a" recommendedConfidence="85" patternsProximity="300">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
     <IdMatch idRef="Func_south_korea_resident_number"/>
     <Match idRef="Keyword_south_korea_resident_number"/>
  </Pattern>
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
     <IdMatch idRef="Func_south_korea_resident_number"/>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-10084">關鍵字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10084">Keywords</span></span>
   
#### <a name="keyword_south_korea_resident_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-10085">Keyword_south_korea_resident_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10085">Keyword_south_korea_resident_number</span></span>

## <a name="spain-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-10091">西班牙駕照編號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10091">Spain driver's license number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-10092">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10092">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-10093">八位數後接一個字元</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10093">eight digits followed by one character</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-10094">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10094">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-10095">八位數後接一個字元：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10095">eight digits followed by one character:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-10096">八位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10096">eight digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-10097">一個數位或字母 (不區分大小寫) </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10097">one digit or letter (not case-sensitive)</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-10098">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10098">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-10099">是</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10099">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-10100">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10100">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-10101">當鄰近性300個字元以內時，DLP 原則就會偵測到這種敏感資訊類型：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10101">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-10102">函數  `Func_spain_eu_DL_and_NI_number_citizen` 或 `Func_spain_eu_DL_and_NI_number_foreigner` 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10102">The function  `Func_spain_eu_DL_and_NI_number_citizen` or `Func_spain_eu_DL_and_NI_number_foreigner` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-10103">`Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number`找到或的關鍵字 `Keywords_spain_eu_driver's_license_number` 。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10103">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` or `Keywords_spain_eu_driver's_license_number` is found.</span></span> 

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-10104">當鄰近性300個字元以內時，DLP 原則就會偵測到這種敏感資訊類型的信賴度。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10104">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-10105">函數  `Func_spain_eu_DL_and_NI_number_citizen` 或 `Func_spain_eu_DL_and_NI_number_foreigner` 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10105">The function  `Func_spain_eu_DL_and_NI_number_citizen` or `Func_spain_eu_DL_and_NI_number_foreigner` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Spain Driver's License Number -->
      <Entity id="d5a82922-b501-4f40-8868-341321146aa2" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_spain_eu_DL_and_NI_number_citizen" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_spain_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_spain_eu_DL_and_NI_number_citizen" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_spain_eu_DL_and_NI_number_foreigner" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_spain_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_spain_eu_DL_and_NI_number_foreigner" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-10122">driverslicence</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10122">driverslicence</span></span>

## <a name="spain-dni"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-10239">西班牙 DNI</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10239">Spain DNI</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="94f34-10240">此機密資訊類型僅可用於下列專案：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10240">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-10241">資料遺失防護原則</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10241">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-10242">通訊相容性原則</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10242">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-10243">資訊管理</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10243">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-10244">記錄管理</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10244">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-10245">Microsoft cloud app security</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10245">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-10246">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10246">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-10247">八位數後接一個字元</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10247">eight digits followed by one character</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-10248">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10248">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-10249">七位數後接一個字元</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10249">seven digits followed by one character</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-10250">八位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10250">eight digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-10251">選擇性空格或連字號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10251">An optional space or hyphen</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-10252">一個檢查信件 (不區分大小寫) </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10252">one check letter (not case-sensitive)</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-10253">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10253">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-10254">是</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10254">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-10255">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10255">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-10256">當鄰近性300個字元以內時，DLP 原則就會偵測到這種敏感資訊類型：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10256">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-10257">函數  `Func_spain_eu_DL_and_NI_number_citizen` 或 `Func_spain_eu_DL_and_NI_number_foreigner` 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10257">The function  `Func_spain_eu_DL_and_NI_number_citizen` or `Func_spain_eu_DL_and_NI_number_foreigner` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-10258">找到來自的關鍵字  `Keywords_spain_eu_national_id_card"` 。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10258">A keyword from  `Keywords_spain_eu_national_id_card"` is found.</span></span> 

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-10259">當鄰近性300個字元以內時，DLP 原則就會偵測到這種敏感資訊類型的信賴度。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10259">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-10260">函數  `Func_spain_eu_DL_and_NI_number_citizen` 或 `Func_spain_eu_DL_and_NI_number_foreigner` 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10260">The function  `Func_spain_eu_DL_and_NI_number_citizen` or `Func_spain_eu_DL_and_NI_number_foreigner` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 

    
```xml
      <!-- Spain DNI -->
      <Entity id="8e6251b9-47b4-40e8-a42b-0f80876be192" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_spain_eu_DL_and_NI_number_citizen" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_spain_eu_national_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_spain_eu_DL_and_NI_number_citizen" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_spain_eu_DL_and_NI_number_foreigner" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_spain_eu_national_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_spain_eu_DL_and_NI_number_foreigner" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="spain-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-10284">西班牙護照號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10284">Spain passport number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-10285">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10285">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-10286">8或9個字元組合的字母和數位，不含空格或分隔符號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10286">an eight- or nine-character combination of letters and numbers with no spaces or delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-10287">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10287">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-10288">字母和數位的8或9個字元組合：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10288">an eight- or nine-character combination of letters and numbers:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-10289">兩位數或字母</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10289">two digits or letters</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-10290">一個數位或字母 (選用) </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10290">one digit or letter (optional)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-10291">六位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10291">six digits</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-10292">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10292">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-10293">不適用</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10293">Not applicable</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-10294">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10294">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-10295">當鄰近性300個字元以內時，DLP 原則就會偵測到這種敏感資訊類型：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10295">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-10296">正則運算式會  `Regex_spain_eu_passport_number` 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10296">The regular expression  `Regex_spain_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-10297">`Keywords_eu_passport_number`找到或的關鍵字 `Keywords_spain_eu_passport_number` 。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10297">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_spain_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-10298">正則運算式 `Regex_spain_eu_passport_date` 會找到日期格式為 DD-MM-YYYY 或關鍵字 from。 `Keywords_eu_passport_date`</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10298">The regular expression `Regex_spain_eu_passport_date` finds date in the format DD-MM-YYYY or a keyword from `Keywords_eu_passport_date` is found</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-10299">當鄰近性300個字元以內時，DLP 原則就會偵測到這種敏感資訊類型的信賴度。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10299">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-10300">正則運算式會  `Regex_spain_eu_passport_number` 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10300">The regular expression  `Regex_spain_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-10301">`Keywords_eu_passport_number`找到或的關鍵字 `Keywords_spain_eu_passport_number` 。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10301">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_spain_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span>
    
```xml
      <!-- Spain Passport Number -->
      <Entity id="d17a57de-9fa5-4e9f-85d3-85c26d89686e" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_spain_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_spain_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Regex_spain_eu_passport_date" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_date" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_spain_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_spain_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```
