## <a name="spain-social-security-number-ssn"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-10330"> (SSN) 的西班牙社會安全號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10330">Spain social security number (SSN)</span></span>


### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-10331">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10331">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-10332">11-12 位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10332">11-12 digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-10333">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10333">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-10334">11-12 位數：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10334">11-12 digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-10335">兩位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10335">two digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-10336">轉寄斜線 (選用) </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10336">a forward slash (optional)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-10337">七到八位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10337">seven to eight digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-10338">轉寄斜線 (選用) </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10338">a forward slash (optional)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-10339">兩位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10339">two digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-10340">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10340">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-10341">是</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10341">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-10342">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10342">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-10343">當鄰近性300個字元以內時，DLP 原則就會偵測到這種敏感資訊類型：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10343">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-10344">函數 Func_spanish_social_security_number 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10344">The function Func_spanish_social_security_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-10345">校驗和通過。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10345">The checksum passes.</span></span>
- - <span data-ttu-id="94f34-10346">找到來自的關鍵字  `Keywords_spain_eu_ssn_or_equivalent` 。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10346">A keyword from  `Keywords_spain_eu_ssn_or_equivalent` is found.</span></span> 

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-10347">當鄰近性300個字元以內時，DLP 原則就會偵測到這種敏感資訊類型的信賴度。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10347">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-10348">函數 Func_spanish_social_security_number 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10348">The function Func_spanish_social_security_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-10349">校驗和通過。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10349">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
    <!-- Spain SSN -->
    <Entity id="5df987c0-8eae-4bce-ace7-b316347f3070" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85" relaxProximity="true" >
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_spanish_social_security_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_spain_eu_ssn_or_equivalent" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_spanish_social_security_number" />
        </Pattern>
    </Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-10350">關鍵字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10350">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keywords_spain_eu_passport_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-10351">Keywords_spain_eu_passport_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10351">Keywords_spain_eu_passport_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-10352">Ssn</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10352">ssn</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-10353">Ssn#</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10353">ssn#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-10354">socialsecurityno</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10354">socialsecurityno</span></span>

## <a name="spain-tax-identification-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-10358">西班牙納稅識別號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10358">Spain tax identification number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="94f34-10359">此機密資訊類型僅可用於下列專案：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10359">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-10360">資料遺失防護原則</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10360">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-10361">通訊相容性原則</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10361">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-10362">資訊管理</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10362">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-10363">記錄管理</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10363">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-10364">Microsoft cloud app security</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10364">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-10365">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10365">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-10366">指定的模式中的7或8位數，以及一或兩個字母</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10366">seven or eight digits and one or two letters in the specified pattern</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-10367">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10367">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-10368">具有西班牙國身分識別卡的西班牙文自然人員：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10368">Spanish Natural Persons with a Spain National Identity Card:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-10369">八位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10369">eight digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-10370">單一大寫字母 (區分大小寫) </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10370">one uppercase letter (case-sensitive)</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="94f34-10371">沒有西班牙國身分身分身分識別卡的非居民 Spaniards</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10371">Non-resident Spaniards without a Spain National Identity Card</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-10372">一個大寫的字母 "L" (區分大小寫) </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10372">one uppercase letter "L" (case-sensitive)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-10373">七位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10373">seven digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-10374">單一大寫字母 (區分大小寫) </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10374">one uppercase letter (case-sensitive)</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="94f34-10375">在沒有西班牙國身分識別卡的14年年齡底下的居民 Spaniards：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10375">Resident Spaniards under the age of 14 years without a Spain National Identity Card:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-10376">一個大寫的字母 "K" (區分大小寫) </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10376">one uppercase letter "K" (case-sensitive)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-10377">七位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10377">seven digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-10378">單一大寫字母 (區分大小寫) </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10378">one uppercase letter (case-sensitive)</span></span>
    
<span data-ttu-id="94f34-10379">Foreigners 與 Foreigner 的識別號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10379">Foreigners with a Foreigner's Identification Number</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-10380">一個大寫的字母，為 "X"、"Y" 或 "Z" (區分大小寫) </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10380">one uppercase letter that is "X", "Y", or "Z" (case-sensitive)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-10381">七位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10381">seven digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-10382">單一大寫字母 (區分大小寫) </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10382">one uppercase letter (case-sensitive)</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="94f34-10383">沒有 Foreigner 識別碼的 Foreigners</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10383">Foreigners without a Foreigner's Identification Number</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-10384">一個大寫的字母，為 "M" (區分大小寫) </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10384">one uppercase letter that is "M" (case-sensitive)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-10385">七位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10385">seven digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-10386">單一大寫字母 (區分大小寫) </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10386">one uppercase letter (case-sensitive)</span></span> 
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-10387">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10387">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-10388">是</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10388">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-10389">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10389">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-10390">當鄰近性300個字元以內時，DLP 原則就會偵測到這種敏感資訊類型：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10390">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-10391">函數  `Func_spain_eu_tax_file_number` 或 `Func_spain_eu_DL_and_NI_number_citizen` 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10391">The function  `Func_spain_eu_tax_file_number` or `Func_spain_eu_DL_and_NI_number_citizen` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-10392">找到來自的關鍵字  `Keywords_spain_eu_tax_file_number` 。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10392">A keyword from  `Keywords_spain_eu_tax_file_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="94f34-10393">當鄰近性300個字元以內時，DLP 原則就會偵測到這種敏感資訊類型的信賴度。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10393">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-10394">函數  `Func_spain_eu_tax_file_number` 或 `Func_spain_eu_DL_and_NI_number_citizen` 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10394">The function  `Func_spain_eu_tax_file_number` or `Func_spain_eu_DL_and_NI_number_citizen` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Spain Tax Identification Number -->
      <Entity id="10f0d113-b0e1-47dc-872a-a4f45b9376a3" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_spain_eu_tax_file_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_spain_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_spain_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_spain_eu_DL_and_NI_number_citizen" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_spain_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_spain_eu_DL_and_NI_number_citizen" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="sql-server-connection-string"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-10425">SQL Server 連接字串</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10425">SQL Server connection string</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-10426">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10426">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-10427">字串 "User Id"、"User ID"、"uid" 或 "UserId"，後面加上下列模式中所述的字元及字串。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10427">The string "User Id", "User ID", "uid", or "UserId" followed by the characters and strings outlined in the pattern below.</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-10428">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10428">Pattern</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-10429">字串 "User Id"、"User ID"、"uid" 或 "UserId"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10429">the string "User Id", "User ID", "uid", or "UserId"</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-10430">介於1-200 小寫或大寫字母、數位、符號、特殊字元或空格之間的任何組合</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10430">any combination of between 1-200 lower- or uppercase letters, digits, symbols, special characters, or spaces</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-10431">字串 "Password" 或 "pwd"，其中 "pwd" 前面不是小寫字母</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10431">the string "Password" or "pwd" where "pwd" isn't preceded by a lowercase letter</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-10432">等號 (=) </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10432">an equal sign (=)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-10433">不是貨幣符號的任何字元 ($) ，百分比符號 (% ) ，大於符號 (>) ，符號 ( @ ) ，引號 ( ") ，分號 (; ) ，左大括弧 ( [) ，或左中括弧 ( {) </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10433">any character that isn't a dollar sign ($), percent symbol (%), greater than symbol (>), at symbol (@), quotation mark ("), semicolon (;), left brace([), or left bracket ({)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-10434">任何7-128 個字元的組合不是分號 (; ) 、正斜線 (/) 或引號 ( ") </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10434">any combination of 7-128 characters that are not a semicolon (;), forward slash (/), or quotation mark (")</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-10435">分號 (; ) 或引號 ( ") </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10435">a semicolon (;) or quotation mark (")</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-10436">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10436">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-10437">否</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10437">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-10438">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10438">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-10439">當鄰近性300個字元以內時，DLP 原則就會偵測到這種敏感資訊類型：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10439">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-10440">正則運算式 CEP_Regex_SQLServerConnectionString 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10440">The regular expression CEP_Regex_SQLServerConnectionString finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-10441">找不到來自 CEP_GlobalFilter 的關鍵字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10441">A keyword from CEP_GlobalFilter isn't found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-10442">正則運算式 CEP_PasswordPlaceHolder 找不到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10442">The regular expression CEP_PasswordPlaceHolder doesn't find content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-10443">正則運算式 CEP_CommonExampleKeywords 找不到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10443">The regular expression CEP_CommonExampleKeywords doesn't find content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```sql
<!---SQL Server Connection String>
<Entity id="e76b6205-d3cb-46f2-bd63-c90153f2f97d" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
        <IdMatch idRef="CEP_Regex_SQLServerConnectionString" />
        <Any minMatches="0" maxMatches="0">
            <Match idRef="CEP_GlobalFilter" />
            <Match idRef="CEP_PasswordPlaceHolder" />
            <Match idRef="CEP_CommonExampleKeywords" />
        </Any>
    </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-10444">關鍵字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10444">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="cep_globalfilter"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-10445">CEP_GlobalFilter</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10445">CEP_GlobalFilter</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-10446">部分密碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10446">some-password</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-10447">somepassword</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10447">somepassword</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-10448">secretPassword</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10448">secretPassword</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-10449">樣品</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10449">sample</span></span>

#### <a name="cep_passwordplaceholder"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-10450">CEP_PasswordPlaceHolder</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10450">CEP_PasswordPlaceHolder</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-10451"> (請注意，在技術上而言，這個敏感資訊類型是使用正則運算式來識別這些關鍵字，而不是關鍵字清單。 ) </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10451">(Note that technically, this sensitive information type identifies these keywords by using a regular expression, not a keyword list.)</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-10452">密碼或密碼後接0-2 個空格、等號 (=) 、0-2 空間，以及星號 ( \* ) -OR-</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10452">Password or pwd followed by 0-2 spaces, an equal sign (=), 0-2 spaces, and an asterisk (\*) -OR-</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-10453">密碼或密碼，接著：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10453">Password or pwd followed by:</span></span>
    - <span data-ttu-id="94f34-10454">等號 (=) </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10454">Equal sign (=)</span></span>
    - <span data-ttu-id="94f34-10455">小於符號 (<) </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10455">Less than symbol (<)</span></span>
    - <span data-ttu-id="94f34-10456">1-200 個字元的任意組合（大小寫字母、數位、星號 ( \* ) 、連字號 ( ) 、底線 (_) 或空白字元）</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10456">Any combination of 1-200 characters that are upper- or lowercase letters, digits, an asterisk (\*), hyphen (-), underline (_), or whitespace character</span></span>
    - <span data-ttu-id="94f34-10457">大於符號 (>) </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10457">Greater than symbol (>)</span></span>

## <a name="sweden-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-10471">瑞典駕駛執照號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10471">Sweden driver's license number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-10472">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10472">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-10473">10位數包含連字號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10473">ten digits containing a hyphen</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-10474">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10474">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-10475">10位數包含連字號：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10475">ten digits containing a hyphen:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-10476">六位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10476">six digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-10477">連字號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10477">a hyphen</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-10478">四位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10478">four digits</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-10479">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10479">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-10480">否</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10480">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-10481">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10481">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-10482">當鄰近性300個字元以內時，DLP 原則就會偵測到這種敏感資訊類型的信賴度。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10482">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-10483">正則運算式會  `Regex_sweden_eu_driver's_license_number` 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10483">The regular expression  `Regex_sweden_eu_driver's_license_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-10484">`Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number`找到或的關鍵字 `Keywords_sweden_eu_driver's_license_number` 。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10484">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` or `Keywords_sweden_eu_driver's_license_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Sweden Driver's License Number -->
      <Entity id="70088720-90dd-47f5-805e-5525f3567391" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_sweden_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_sweden_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="sweden-national-id"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-10617">瑞典國家識別碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10617">Sweden national ID</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-10618">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10618">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-10619">10或12位數和選擇性分隔符號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10619">10 or 12 digits and an optional delimiter</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-10620">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10620">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-10621">10或12位數和選用的分隔符號：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10621">10 or 12 digits and an optional delimiter:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-10622">兩位數 (選用) </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10622">two digits (optional)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-10623">日期格式 YYMMDD 的六位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10623">Six digits in date format YYMMDD</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-10624">"-" 或 "+" 的分隔符號 (選用) </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10624">delimiter of "-" or "+" (optional)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-10625">四位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10625">four digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-10626">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10626">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-10627">是</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10627">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-10628">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10628">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-10629">當鄰近性300個字元以內時，DLP 原則就會偵測到這種敏感資訊類型：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10629">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-10630">函數 `Func_swedish_national_identifier` 會找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10630">The function `Func_swedish_national_identifier` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-10631">找到來自的關鍵字 `Keywords_swedish_national_identifier`</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10631">A keyword from `Keywords_swedish_national_identifier` is found</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-10632">校驗和通過。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10632">The checksum passes.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-10633">當鄰近性300個字元以內時，DLP 原則就會偵測到這種敏感資訊類型的信賴度。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10633">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-10634">函數 `Func_swedish_national_identifier` 會找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10634">The function `Func_swedish_national_identifier` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-10635">校驗和通過。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10635">The checksum passes.</span></span>


```xml
    <!-- Sweden National ID -->
    <Entity id="f69aaf40-79be-4fac-8f05-fd1910d272c8" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_swedish_national_identifier" />
        <Match idRef="Keywords_swedish_national_identifier" />
      </Pattern>
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_swedish_national_identifier" />
      </Pattern>
    </Entity>
```

## <a name="sweden-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-10654">瑞典護照號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10654">Sweden passport number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-10655">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10655">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-10656">八位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10656">eight digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-10657">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10657">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-10658">八個連續數位</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10658">eight consecutive digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-10659">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10659">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-10660">否</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10660">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-10661">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10661">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-10662">當鄰近性300個字元以內時，DLP 原則就會偵測到這種敏感資訊類型：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10662">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-10663">正則運算式 Regex_sweden_passport_number 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10663">the regular expression Regex_sweden_passport_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-10664">`Keywords_eu_passport_number`找到或的關鍵字 `Keyword_sweden_passport` 。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10664">a keyword from `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keyword_sweden_passport` is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-10665">正則運算式 `Regex_sweden_eu_passport_date` 會找到以 DD MMM/MMM YY 格式 (01 JAN/JAN 12) 或找到關鍵字的日期 `Keywords_eu_passport_date` 。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10665">the regular expression `Regex_sweden_eu_passport_date` finds a date in the format DD MMM/MMM YY (01 JAN/JAN 12) or a keyword from `Keywords_eu_passport_date` is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-10666">當鄰近性300個字元以內時，DLP 原則就會偵測到這種敏感資訊類型的信賴度。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10666">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-10667">正則運算式 Regex_sweden_passport_number 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10667">the regular expression Regex_sweden_passport_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-10668">`Keywords_eu_passport_number`找到或的關鍵字 `Keyword_sweden_passport` 。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10668">a keyword from `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keyword_sweden_passport` is found.</span></span>


```xml
    <!-- Sweden Passport Number -->
    <Entity id="ba4e7456-55a9-4d89-9140-c33673553526" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_sweden_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keyword_sweden_passport" />
          </Any>
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Regex_sweden_eu_passport_date" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_date" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_sweden_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keyword_sweden_passport" />
          </Any>
      </Pattern>
    </Entity>
```

## <a name="sweden-social-security-number-or-equivalent-identification"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-10704">瑞典社會安全號碼或對等身分識別</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10704">Sweden social security number or equivalent identification</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="94f34-10705">這個敏感資訊類型實體只有歐盟社會保險號碼或同等識別碼的敏感資訊類型提供。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10705">This sensitive information type entity is only available in the EU Social Security Number or Equivalent ID sensitive information type.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-10706">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10706">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-10707">12位數，不含空格及分隔符號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10707">12 digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-10708">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10708">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-10709">12位數：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10709">12 digits:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-10710">對應至出生日期 (YYYYMMDD) 的八位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10710">eight digits that correspond to the birth date (YYYYMMDD)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-10711">對應至序數的三位數，其中：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10711">three digits that correspond to a serial number where:</span></span> 
  - <span data-ttu-id="94f34-10712">序數中的最後一個數位是由為男指派的奇數和偶數的女數位來表示性別</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10712">the last digit in the serial number indicates gender by the assignment of an odd number for male and an even number for female</span></span>
  - <span data-ttu-id="94f34-10713">在1990之前，將 corresponded 的持有者的序號為出生的縣編號。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10713">Before 1990, the assignment of a serial number corresponded to the county where the bearer of the number was born.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="94f34-10714">或 (如果在 1947) （如有）的使用中，則根據稅收記錄在年1月 1 1947 日的納稅記錄中 (，以特殊的程式碼通常為 immigrants 的第七位數) 9。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10714">Or (if born before 1947) where they had been living, according to tax records, on January 1, 1947, with a special code (usually 9 as the seventh digit) for immigrants.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-10715">一個檢查碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10715">one check digit</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-10716">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10716">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-10717">是</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10717">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-10718">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10718">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-10719">如果接近300個字元以內，則 DLP 原則偵測到此敏感資訊類型的置信量是85%：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10719">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-10720">函數  `Func_sweden_eu_ssn_or_equivalent` 會找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10720">The function  `Func_sweden_eu_ssn_or_equivalent` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-10721">找到來自的關鍵字  `Keywords_sweden_eu_ssn_or_equivalent` 。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10721">A keyword from  `Keywords_sweden_eu_ssn_or_equivalent` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="94f34-10722">如果接近300個字元以內，則 DLP 原則偵測到此敏感資訊類型的置信量是75%：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10722">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-10723">函數  `Func_sweden_eu_ssn_or_equivalent` 會找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10723">The function  `Func_sweden_eu_ssn_or_equivalent` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
 <!-- EU SSN or Equivalent Number -->
<Entity id="d24e32a4-c0bb-4ba8-899d-6303b95742d9" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_sweden_eu_ssn_or_equivalent" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_sweden_eu_ssn_or_equivalent" />
        </Pattern> 
       <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_sweden_eu_ssn_or_equivalent" />
        </Pattern>      
</Entity>
```

## <a name="sweden-tax-identification-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-10739">瑞典納稅識別號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10739">Sweden tax identification number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="94f34-10740">此機密資訊類型僅可用於下列專案：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10740">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-10741">資料遺失防護原則</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10741">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-10742">通訊相容性原則</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10742">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-10743">資訊管理</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10743">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-10744">記錄管理</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10744">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-10745">Microsoft cloud app security</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10745">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-10746">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10746">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-10747">在指定的模式中，10位數和符號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10747">10 digits and a symbol in the specified pattern</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-10748">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10748">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-10749">10位數和符號：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10749">10 digits and a symbol:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-10750">對應至出生日期 (YYMMDD 的六位數) </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10750">six digits that correspond to the birth date (YYMMDD)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-10751">加號或減號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10751">a plus sign or minus sign</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-10752">在下列情況下，識別號碼唯一的三位數：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10752">three digits that make the identification number unique where:</span></span> 
  - <span data-ttu-id="94f34-10753">若為1990之前所簽發的號碼，第七和第八位數識別出生的縣或對外出生的人員</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10753">for numbers issued before 1990, the seventh and eighth digit identify the county of birth or foreign-born people</span></span>
  - <span data-ttu-id="94f34-10754">第九個位置中的位數會以奇數為單位表示，甚至是對女的性別</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10754">the digit in the ninth position indicates gender by either odd for male or even for female</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-10755">一個檢查碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10755">one check digit</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-10756">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10756">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-10757">是</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10757">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-10758">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10758">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-10759">當鄰近性300個字元以內時，DLP 原則就會偵測到這種敏感資訊類型：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10759">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-10760">函數  `Func_sweden_eu_tax_file_number` 會找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10760">The function  `Func_sweden_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-10761">找到來自的關鍵字  `Keywords_sweden_eu_tax_file_number` 。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10761">A keyword from  `Keywords_sweden_eu_tax_file_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="94f34-10762">當鄰近性300個字元以內時，DLP 原則就會偵測到這種敏感資訊類型的信賴度。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10762">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-10763">函數  `Func_sweden_eu_tax_file_number` 會找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10763">The function  `Func_sweden_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Sweden Tax Identification Number -->
      <Entity id="139acba0-a5bc-4fbb-876d-f7a493ae8a40" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_sweden_eu_tax_file_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_sweden_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_sweden_eu_tax_file_number" />
          <Any minMatches="0" maxMatches="0">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_sweden_eu_telephone_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_sweden_eu_mobile_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="swift-code"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-10789">SWIFT 程式碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10789">SWIFT code</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-10790">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10790">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-10791">四個字母后接5-31 個字母或數位</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10791">four letters followed by 5-31 letters or digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-10792">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10792">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-10793">四個字母后接5-31 個字母或數位：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10793">four letters followed by 5-31 letters or digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-10794">四個字母的銀行程式碼 (不區分大小寫) </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10794">four-letter bank code (not case-sensitive)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-10795">選擇性的空格</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10795">an optional space</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-10796"> ( (BBAN) ) 基本銀行帳戶號碼的4-28 字母或數位</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10796">4-28 letters or digits (the Basic Bank Account Number (BBAN))</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-10797">選擇性的空格</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10797">an optional space</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-10798">BBAN 的其餘部分 (一到三個字母或數位) </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10798">one to three letters or digits (remainder of the BBAN)</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-10799">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10799">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-10800">否</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10800">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-10801">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10801">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-10802">當鄰近性300個字元以內時，DLP 原則就會偵測到這種敏感資訊類型的信賴度。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10802">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-10803">正則運算式 Regex_swift 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10803">The regular expression Regex_swift finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-10804">會找到來自 Keyword_swift 的關鍵字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10804">A keyword from Keyword_swift is found.</span></span>

```xml
<Entity id="cb2ab58c-9cb8-4c81-baf8-a4e106791df4" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
<Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Regex_swift" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_swift" />
    </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="switzerland-ssn-ahv-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-10841">瑞士 SSN AHV 號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10841">Switzerland SSN AHV number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="94f34-10842">此機密資訊類型僅可用於下列專案：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10842">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-10843">資料遺失防護原則</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10843">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-10844">通訊相容性原則</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10844">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-10845">資訊管理</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10845">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-10846">記錄管理</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10846">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-10847">Microsoft cloud app security</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10847">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-10848">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10848">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-10849">13位數數位</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10849">13-digit number</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-10850">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10850">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-10851">13位數數位：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10851">13-digit number:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-10852">三位數-756</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10852">three digits - 756</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-10853">選用點</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10853">an optional dot</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-10854">四位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10854">four digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-10855">選用點</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10855">an optional dot</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-10856">四位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10856">four digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-10857">選用點</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10857">an optional dot</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-10858">兩位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10858">two digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-10859">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10859">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-10860">是</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10860">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-10861">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10861">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-10862">當鄰近性300個字元以內時，DLP 原則就會偵測到這種敏感資訊類型：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10862">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-10863">函數 Func_swiss_social_security_number_ahv 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10863">The function Func_swiss_social_security_number_ahv finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-10864">會找到來自 Keywords_swiss_social_security_number_ahv 的關鍵字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10864">A keyword from Keywords_swiss_social_security_number_ahv is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-10865">當鄰近性300個字元以內時，DLP 原則就會偵測到這種敏感資訊類型的信賴度。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10865">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-10866">函數 Func_swiss_social_security_number_ahv 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10866">The function Func_swiss_social_security_number_ahv finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Swiss SSN AHV Number -->
      <Entity id="277cfa4b-6eaa-4a1b-9492-099dec849971" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_swiss_social_security_number_ahv" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_swiss_social_security_number_ahv" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_swiss_social_security_number_ahv" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="taiwan-national-identification-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-10887">臺灣國身分識別號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10887">Taiwan national identification number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-10888">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10888">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-10889">一個英文) 的字母 (後接9位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10889">one letter (in English) followed by nine digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-10890">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10890">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-10891">一個英文) 的字母 (後接9位數：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10891">one letter (in English) followed by nine digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-10892">一個英文字母 (，不區分大小寫) </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10892">one letter (in English, not case-sensitive)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-10893">數位 "1" 或 "2"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10893">the digit "1" or "2"</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-10894">八位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10894">eight digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-10895">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10895">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-10896">是</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10896">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-10897">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10897">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-10898">當鄰近性300個字元以內時，DLP 原則就會偵測到這種敏感資訊類型：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10898">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-10899">函數 Func_taiwanese_national_id 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10899">The function Func_taiwanese_national_id finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-10900">會找到來自 Keyword_taiwanese_national_id 的關鍵字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10900">A keyword from Keyword_taiwanese_national_id is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-10901">校驗和通過。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10901">The checksum passes.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-10902">當鄰近性300個字元以內時，DLP 原則就會偵測到這種敏感資訊類型的信賴度。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10902">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-10903">函數 Func_taiwanese_national_id 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10903">The function Func_taiwanese_national_id finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-10904">校驗和通過。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10904">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Taiwanese National ID -->
```

## <a name="taiwan-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-10921">臺灣護照號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10921">Taiwan passport number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-10922">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10922">Format</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-10923">生物識別護照號碼：9位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10923">biometric passport number: nine digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-10924">非生物識別護照號碼：9位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10924">non-biometric passport number: nine digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-10925">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10925">Pattern</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="94f34-10926">生物識別護照號碼：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10926">biometric passport number:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-10927">字元 "3"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10927">the character "3"</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-10928">八位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10928">eight digits</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-10929">無生物識別護照號碼：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10929">non-biometric passport number:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-10930">九位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10930">nine digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-10931">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10931">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-10932">否</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10932">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-10933">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10933">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-10934">當鄰近性300個字元以內時，DLP 原則就會偵測到這種敏感資訊類型的信賴度。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10934">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-10935">正則運算式 Regex_taiwan_passport 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10935">The regular expression Regex_taiwan_passport finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-10936">會找到來自 Keyword_taiwan_passport 的關鍵字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10936">A keyword from Keyword_taiwan_passport is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Taiwan Passport Number -->
<Entity id="e7251cb4-4c2c-41df-963e-924eb3dae04a" recommendedConfidence="75" patternsProximity="300">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
     <IdMatch idRef="Regex_taiwan_passport"/>
     <Match idRef="Keyword_taiwan_passport"/>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-10940">護照號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10940">Passport number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-10942">護照編號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10942">Passport Num</span></span>

## <a name="taiwan-resident-certificate-arctarc-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-10947">臺灣居民憑證 (ARC/TARC) 號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10947">Taiwan-resident certificate (ARC/TARC) number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-10948">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10948">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-10949">10個字母和數位</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10949">10 letters and digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-10950">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10950">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-10951">10個字母和數位：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10951">10 letters and digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-10952">兩個字母 (不區分大小寫) </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10952">two letters (not case-sensitive)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-10953">八位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10953">eight digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-10954">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10954">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-10955">否</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10955">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-10956">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10956">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-10957">當鄰近性300個字元以內時，DLP 原則就會偵測到這種敏感資訊類型的信賴度。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10957">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-10958">正則運算式 Regex_taiwan_resident_certificate 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10958">The regular expression Regex_taiwan_resident_certificate finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-10959">會找到來自 Keyword_taiwan_resident_certificate 的關鍵字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10959">A keyword from Keyword_taiwan_resident_certificate is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Taiwan Resident Certificate (ARC/TARC) -->
<Entity id="48269fec-05ea-46ea-b326-f5623a58c6e9" recommendedConfidence="75" patternsProximity="300">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
     <IdMatch idRef="Regex_taiwan_resident_certificate"/>
     <Match idRef="Keyword_taiwan_resident_certificate"/>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="thai-population-identification-code"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-10973">泰國人口識別碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10973">Thai population identification code</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-10974">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10974">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-10975">13位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10975">13 digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-10976">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10976">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-10977">13位數：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10977">13 digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-10978">第一個數位不是零或9</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10978">first digit isn't zero or nine</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-10979">12位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10979">12 digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-10980">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10980">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-10981">是</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10981">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-10982">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10982">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-10983">當鄰近性300個字元以內時，DLP 原則就會偵測到這種敏感資訊類型：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10983">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-10984">函數 Func_Thai_Citizen_Id 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10984">The function Func_Thai_Citizen_Id finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-10985">會找到來自 Keyword_Thai_Citizen_Id 的關鍵字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10985">A keyword from Keyword_Thai_Citizen_Id is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-10986">當鄰近性300個字元以內時，DLP 原則就會偵測到這種敏感資訊類型的信賴度。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10986">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-10987">函數 Func_Thai_Citizen_Id 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10987">The function Func_Thai_Citizen_Id finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Thai Citizen ID -->
-<Entity id="44ca9e86-ead7-4c5d-884a-e2eaa401515e" recommendedConfidence="75" patternsProximity="300">
   -<Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
      <IdMatch idRef="Func_Thai_Citizen_Id"/>
      <Match idRef="Keyword_Thai_Citizen_Id"/>
   </Pattern>
   -<Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
      <IdMatch idRef="Func_Thai_Citizen_Id"/>
   </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="turkish-national-identification-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-10996">土耳其國身分識別號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-10996">Turkish national identification number</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-11000">11位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-11000">11 digits</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-11007">當鄰近性300個字元以內時，DLP 原則就會偵測到這種敏感資訊類型的信賴度。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-11007">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-11008">函數 Func_Turkish_National_Id 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-11008">The function Func_Turkish_National_Id finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Turkish National Identity -->
-<Entity id="fb621f20-3876-4cfc-acec-8c8e73ca32c7" recommendedConfidence="75" patternsProximity="300">
   -<Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
      <IdMatch idRef="Func_Turkish_National_Id"/>
      <Match idRef="Keyword_Turkish_National_Id"/>
   </Pattern>
   -<Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
      <IdMatch idRef="Func_Turkish_National_Id"/>
   </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="uk-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-11015">英國。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-11015">U.K.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="94f34-11016">駕駛執照號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-11016">driver's license number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-11017">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-11017">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-11018">以指定格式的18個字母和數位的組合</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-11018">Combination of 18 letters and digits in the specified format</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-11019">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-11019">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-11020">18個字母和數位：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-11020">18 letters and digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-11021">五個字母 (不區分大小寫) 或數位 "9" 取代字母。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-11021">Five letters (not case-sensitive) or the digit "9" in place of a letter.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-11022">一個數位。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-11022">One digit.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-11023">MMDDY 日期格式的5位數（出生日期）。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-11023">Five digits in the date format MMDDY for date of birth.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="94f34-11024">如果驅動程式是女，第七個字元會增加50。若為 exampe，51至62，而不是01到12。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-11024">The seventh character is incremented by 50 if driver is female; for exampe, 51 to 62 instead of 01 to 12.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-11025">兩個字母 (不區分大小寫) 或數位 "9" 取代字母。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-11025">Two letters (not case-sensitive) or the digit "9" in place of a letter.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-11026">五位數。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-11026">Five digits.</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-11027">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-11027">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-11028">是</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-11028">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-11029">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-11029">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-11030">當鄰近性300個字元以內時，DLP 原則就會偵測到這種敏感資訊類型的信賴度。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-11030">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-11031">函數 `Func_uk_drivers_license` 會找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-11031">The function `Func_uk_drivers_license` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-11032">找到來自的關鍵字 `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` 。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-11032">A keyword from `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-11033">校驗和通過。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-11033">The checksum passes.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-11034">DLP 原則在接近300個字元以內時，偵測到此敏感資訊類型的信賴度很低：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-11034">A DLP policy has low confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-11035">函數 `Func_uk_drivers_license` 會找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-11035">The function `Func_uk_drivers_license` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-11036">校驗和通過。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-11036">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
    <!-- U.K. Driver's License Number -->
    <Entity id="f93de4be-d94c-40df-a8be-461738047551" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75" relaxProximity="true" >
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_uk_drivers_license" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_uk_drivers_license" />
        </Pattern>
    </Entity>
```
