## <a name="uk-electoral-roll-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-11157">英國。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-11157">U.K.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="94f34-11158">electoral 編號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-11158">electoral roll number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-11159">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-11159">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-11160">兩個字母后接1-4 位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-11160">two letters followed by 1-4 digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-11161">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-11161">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-11162">兩個字母 (不區分大小寫) 後接1-4 號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-11162">two letters (not case-sensitive) followed by 1-4 numbers</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-11163">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-11163">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-11164">否</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-11164">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-11165">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-11165">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-11166">當鄰近性300個字元以內時，DLP 原則就會偵測到這種敏感資訊類型的信賴度。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-11166">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-11167">正則運算式 Regex_uk_electoral 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-11167">The regular expression Regex_uk_electoral finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-11168">會找到來自 Keyword_uk_electoral 的關鍵字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-11168">A keyword from Keyword_uk_electoral is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- U.K. Electoral Number -->
<Entity id="a3eea206-dc0c-4f06-9e22-aa1be3059963" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
    <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Regex_uk_electoral" />
        <Any minMatches="1">
          <Match idRef="Keyword_uk_electoral" />
        </Any>
    </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-11169">關鍵字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-11169">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_uk_electoral"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-11170">Keyword_uk_electoral</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-11170">Keyword_uk_electoral</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-11171">理事會提名</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-11171">council nomination</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-11172">提名表單</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-11172">nomination form</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-11173">electoral 寄存器</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-11173">electoral register</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-11174">electoral 輥</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-11174">electoral roll</span></span>

   
## <a name="uk-national-health-service-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-11175">英國。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-11175">U.K.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="94f34-11176">本國健康情況服務號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-11176">national health service number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-11177">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-11177">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-11178">以空格分隔的10-17 位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-11178">10-17 digits separated by spaces</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-11179">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-11179">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-11180">10-17 位數：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-11180">10-17 digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-11181">3或10位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-11181">either 3 or 10 digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-11182">一個空格</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-11182">a space</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-11183">三位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-11183">three digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-11184">一個空格</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-11184">a space</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-11185">四位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-11185">four digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-11186">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-11186">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-11187">是</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-11187">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-11188">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-11188">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-11189">當鄰近性300個字元以內時，DLP 原則就會偵測到這種敏感資訊類型：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-11189">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-11190">函數 Func_uk_nhs_number 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-11190">The function Func_uk_nhs_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-11191">下列其中一項為真：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-11191">One of the following is true:</span></span>
    - <span data-ttu-id="94f34-11192">會找到來自 Keyword_uk_nhs_number 的關鍵字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-11192">A keyword from Keyword_uk_nhs_number is found.</span></span>
    - <span data-ttu-id="94f34-11193">會找到來自 Keyword_uk_nhs_number1 的關鍵字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-11193">A keyword from Keyword_uk_nhs_number1 is found.</span></span>
    - <span data-ttu-id="94f34-11194">會找到來自 Keyword_uk_nhs_number_dob 的關鍵字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-11194">A keyword from Keyword_uk_nhs_number_dob is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-11195">校驗和通過。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-11195">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- U.K. NHS Number -->
<Entity id="3192014e-2a16-44e9-aa69-4b20375c9a78" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
    <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_uk_nhs_number" />
        <Any minMatches="1">
          <Match idRef="Keyword_uk_nhs_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_uk_nhs_number1" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_uk_nhs_number_dob" />
        </Any>
    </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-11196">關鍵字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-11196">Keywords</span></span>
   
#### <a name="keyword_uk_nhs_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-11197">Keyword_uk_nhs_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-11197">Keyword_uk_nhs_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-11198">全國健康情況服務</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-11198">national health service</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-11199">Nhs</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-11199">nhs</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-11200">健康情況服務授權</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-11200">health services authority</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-11201">健康情況授權單位</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-11201">health authority</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_uk_nhs_number1"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-11202">Keyword_uk_nhs_number1</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-11202">Keyword_uk_nhs_number1</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-11203">患者識別碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-11203">patient id</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-11204">患者識別</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-11204">patient identification</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-11205">患者否</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-11205">patient no</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-11206">病人編號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-11206">patient number</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_uk_nhs_number_dob"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-11207">Keyword_uk_nhs_number_dob</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-11207">Keyword_uk_nhs_number_dob</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-11208">Gp</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-11208">GP</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-11209">DOB</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-11209">DOB</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-11210">D. B</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-11210">D.O.B</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-11211">出生日期</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-11211">Date of Birth</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-11212">出生日期</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-11212">Birth Date</span></span> 
   
## <a name="uk-national-insurance-number-nino"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-11213">英國。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-11213">U.K.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="94f34-11214">本國保險號碼 (NINO) </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-11214">national insurance number (NINO)</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="94f34-11215">這種敏感資訊類型實體包含在歐盟國身分識別號碼的敏感資訊類型中。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-11215">This sensitive information type entity is included in the EU National Identification Number sensitive information type.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="94f34-11216">它可以做為獨立的機密資訊類型實體。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-11216">It's available as a stand-alone sensitive information type entity.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-11217">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-11217">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-11218">以空格或破折號隔開的七個字元或九個字元</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-11218">seven characters or nine characters separated by spaces or dashes</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-11219">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-11219">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-11220">兩種可能的模式：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-11220">two possible patterns:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-11221"> (有效 NINOs 的兩個字母都只使用此前置詞中的特定字元，此方式會驗證;不區分大小寫) </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-11221">two letters (valid NINOs use only certain characters in this prefix, which this pattern validates; not case-sensitive)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-11222">六位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-11222">six digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-11223">"A"、"B"、"C" 或 "d" (類似前置詞，只允許在尾碼中使用特定字元;不區分大小寫) </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-11223">either 'A', 'B', 'C', or 'D' (like the prefix, only certain characters are allowed in the suffix; not case-sensitive)</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-11224">「或」</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-11224">OR</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-11225">兩個字母</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-11225">two letters</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-11226">一個空格或破折號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-11226">a space or dash</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-11227">兩位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-11227">two digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-11228">一個空格或破折號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-11228">a space or dash</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-11229">兩位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-11229">two digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-11230">一個空格或破折號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-11230">a space or dash</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-11231">兩位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-11231">two digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-11232">一個空格或破折號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-11232">a space or dash</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-11233">' A '、' B '、' C ' 或 ' d ' 是 '</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-11233">either 'A', 'B', 'C', or 'D'</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-11234">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-11234">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-11235">否</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-11235">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-11236">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-11236">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-11237">當鄰近性300個字元以內時，DLP 原則就會偵測到這種敏感資訊類型：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-11237">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-11238">函數 Func_uk_nino 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-11238">The function Func_uk_nino finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-11239">會找到來自 Keyword_uk_nino 的關鍵字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-11239">A keyword from Keyword_uk_nino is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-11240">當鄰近性300個字元以內時，DLP 原則就會偵測到這種敏感資訊類型的信賴度。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-11240">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-11241">函數 Func_uk_nino 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-11241">The function Func_uk_nino finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
    <!-- U.K. NINO -->
    <Entity id="16c07343-c26f-49d2-a987-3daf717e94cc" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75" relaxProximity="true">
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_uk_nino" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_uk_nino" />
      </Pattern>
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_uk_nino" />
      </Pattern>
    </Entity>
```

## <a name="uk-unique-taxpayer-reference-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-11263">英國。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-11263">U.K.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="94f34-11264">唯一的納稅人參考編號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-11264">Unique Taxpayer Reference Number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="94f34-11265">此機密資訊類型僅可用於下列專案：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-11265">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-11266">資料遺失防護原則</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-11266">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-11267">通訊相容性原則</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-11267">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-11268">資訊管理</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-11268">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-11269">記錄管理</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-11269">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-11270">Microsoft cloud app security</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-11270">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-11271">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-11271">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-11272">10位數，不含空格及分隔符號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-11272">10 digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>
 
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-11273">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-11273">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-11274">10位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-11274">10 digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-11275">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-11275">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-11276">否</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-11276">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-11277">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-11277">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-11278">當鄰近性300個字元以內時，DLP 原則就會偵測到這種敏感資訊類型的信賴度。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-11278">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-11279">函數  `Func_uk_eu_tax_file_number` 會找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-11279">The function  `Func_uk_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-11280">找到來自的關鍵字  `Keywords_uk_eu_tax_file_number` 。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-11280">A keyword from  `Keywords_uk_eu_tax_file_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- U.K. Unique Taxpayer Reference Number -->
      <Entity id="ad4a8116-0db8-439a-b545-6d967642f0ec" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_uk_eu_tax_file_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_uk_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="us-bank-account-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-11300">美國銀行帳戶號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-11300">U.S. bank account number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-11301">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-11301">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-11302">6-17 位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-11302">6-17 digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-11303">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-11303">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-11304">6-17 連續位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-11304">6-17 consecutive digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-11305">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-11305">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-11306">否</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-11306">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-11307">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-11307">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-11308">當鄰近性300個字元以內時，DLP 原則就會偵測到這種敏感資訊類型的信賴度。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-11308">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-11309">正則運算式 Regex_usa_bank_account_number 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-11309">The regular expression Regex_usa_bank_account_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-11310">會找到來自 Keyword_usa_Bank_Account 的關鍵字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-11310">A keyword from Keyword_usa_Bank_Account is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- U.S. Bank Account Number -->
<Entity id="a2ce32a8-f935-4bb6-8e96-2a5157672e2c" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
    <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Regex_usa_bank_account_number" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_usa_Bank_Account" />
    </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="us-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-11340">美國駕駛執照號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-11340">U.S. driver's license number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-11341">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-11341">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-11342">取決於狀態</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-11342">Depends on the state</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-11343">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-11343">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-11344">取決於狀態-例如，紐約：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-11344">depends on the state - for example, New York:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-11345">已格式化的九位數，如 ddd ddd ddd 會相符。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-11345">nine digits formatted like ddd ddd ddd will match.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-11346">九位數的 ddddddddd 不相符。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-11346">nine digits like ddddddddd will not match.</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-11347">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-11347">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-11348">否</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-11348">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-11349">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-11349">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-11350">當鄰近性300個字元以內時，DLP 原則就會偵測到這種敏感資訊類型的信賴度。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-11350">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-11351">函數 Func_new_york_drivers_license_number 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-11351">The function Func_new_york_drivers_license_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-11352">找到來自 Keyword_ [state_name] _drivers_license_name 的關鍵字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-11352">A keyword from Keyword_[state_name]_drivers_license_name is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-11353">會找到來自 Keyword_us_drivers_license 的關鍵字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-11353">A keyword from Keyword_us_drivers_license is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-11354">DLP 原則在接近300個字元以內時，偵測到此敏感資訊類型的信賴度很低：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-11354">A DLP policy has low confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-11355">函數 Func_new_york_drivers_license_number 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-11355">The function Func_new_york_drivers_license_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-11356">找到來自 Keyword_ [state_name] _drivers_license_name 的關鍵字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-11356">A keyword from Keyword_[state_name]_drivers_license_name is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-11357">會找到來自 Keyword_us_drivers_license_abbreviations 的關鍵字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-11357">A keyword from Keyword_us_drivers_license_abbreviations is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-11358">找不到 Keyword_us_drivers_license 的關鍵字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-11358">No keyword from Keyword_us_drivers_license is found.</span></span>

```xml
<Entity id="dfeb356f-61cd-459e-bf0f-7c6d28b458c6 patternsProximity="300">
    <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_new_york_drivers_license_number" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_new_york_drivers_license_name" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_us_drivers_license" />
    </Pattern>
    <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_new_york_drivers_license_number" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_new_york_drivers_license_name" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_us_drivers_license_abbreviations" />
        <Any minMatches="0" maxMatches="0">
          <Match idRef="Keyword_us_drivers_license" />
        </Any>
    </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="us-individual-taxpayer-identification-number-itin"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-11456">ITIN) 的美國個別納稅人識別號碼 (</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-11456">U.S. individual taxpayer identification number (ITIN)</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-11457">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-11457">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-11458">以 "9" 開頭且包含 "7" 或 "8" 的九位數做為第四位數，可選擇性地使用空格或破折號格式化</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-11458">nine digits that start with a "9" and contain a "7" or "8" as the fourth digit, optionally formatted with spaces or dashes</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-11459">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-11459">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-11460">格式 化：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-11460">formatted:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-11461">數位 "9"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-11461">the digit "9"</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-11462">兩位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-11462">two digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-11463">一個空格或破折號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-11463">a space or dash</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-11464">"7" 或 "8"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-11464">a "7" or "8"</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-11465">一個數位</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-11465">a digit</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-11466">一個空格或破折號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-11466">a space, or dash</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-11467">四位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-11467">four digits</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-11468">非</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-11468">unformatted:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-11469">數位 "9"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-11469">the digit "9"</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-11470">兩位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-11470">two digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-11471">"7" 或 "8"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-11471">a "7" or "8"</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-11472">五位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-11472">five digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-11473">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-11473">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-11474">否</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-11474">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-11475">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-11475">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-11476">當鄰近性300個字元以內時，DLP 原則就會偵測到這種敏感資訊類型：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-11476">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-11477">函數 Func_formatted_itin 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-11477">The function Func_formatted_itin finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-11478">會找到來自 Keyword_itin 的關鍵字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-11478">A keyword from Keyword_itin is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-11479">當鄰近性300個字元以內時，DLP 原則就會偵測到這種敏感資訊類型的信賴度。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-11479">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-11480">函數 Func_unformatted_itin 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-11480">The function Func_unformatted_itin finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-11481">會找到來自 Keyword_itin 的關鍵字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-11481">A keyword from Keyword_itin is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-11482">DLP 原則在接近300個字元以內時，偵測到此敏感資訊類型的信賴度很低：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-11482">A DLP policy has low confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-11483">函數 Func_formatted_itin 或 Func_unformatted_itin 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-11483">The function Func_formatted_itin or Func_unformatted_itin finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
    <!-- U.S. Individual Taxpayer Identification Number (ITIN) -->
    <Entity id="e55e2a32-f92d-4985-a35d-a0b269eb687b" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_formatted_itin" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_itin" />
      </Pattern>
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_unformatted_itin" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_itin" />
      </Pattern>
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_formatted_itin" />
      </Pattern>
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_unformatted_itin" />
      </Pattern>
    </Entity>
```

- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-11487">納稅識別碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-11487">tax id</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-11488">納稅識別</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-11488">tax identification</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-11489">itin</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-11489">itin</span></span>

## <a name="us-social-security-number-ssn"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-11498"> (SSN) 的 U.S. 社會安全號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-11498">U.S. social security number (SSN)</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-11499">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-11499">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-11500">九位數（可能是格式化或未格式化的模式）</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-11500">nine digits, which may be in a formatted or unformatted pattern</span></span>

> [!NOTE]
> <span data-ttu-id="94f34-11501">若在 2011 mid 之前發出，則 SSN 具有強格式，其中的號碼的某些部分必須在特定範圍內，才能 (，但沒有任何) 校驗和。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-11501">If issued before mid-2011, an SSN has strong formatting where certain parts of the number must fall within certain ranges to be valid (but there's no checksum).</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-11502">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-11502">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-11503">四種功能會在四種不同的模式中尋找主旨 ssn：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-11503">four functions look for SSNs in four different patterns:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-11504">Func_ssn 會找到主旨 ssn，其強格式為2011的強格式設定，格式為破折號或空格 (ddd-dd-dddd 或 ddd dd dddd) </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-11504">Func_ssn finds SSNs with pre-2011 strong formatting that are formatted with dashes or spaces (ddd-dd-dddd OR ddd dd dddd)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-11505">Func_unformatted_ssn 會以2011的預先設定格式將其強格式設定為九個連續位數 (ddddddddd 的主旨 ssn) </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-11505">Func_unformatted_ssn finds SSNs with pre-2011 strong formatting that are unformatted as nine consecutive digits (ddddddddd)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-11506">Func_randomized_formatted_ssn 會找到以破折號或空格格式化的2011後主旨 ssn， (ddd-dd-dddd 或 ddd dd dddd) </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-11506">Func_randomized_formatted_ssn finds post-2011 SSNs that are formatted with dashes or spaces (ddd-dd-dddd OR ddd dd dddd)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-11507">Func_randomized_unformatted_ssn (ddddddddd 中尋找未格式化為九個連續數位的2011後主旨 ssn) </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-11507">Func_randomized_unformatted_ssn finds post-2011 SSNs that are unformatted as nine consecutive digits (ddddddddd)</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-11508">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-11508">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-11509">否</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-11509">No</span></span>


### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-11510">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-11510">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-11511">當鄰近性300個字元以內時，DLP 原則就會偵測到這種敏感資訊類型：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-11511">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-11512">函數 Func_ssn 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-11512">The function Func_ssn finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-11513">會找到來自 Keyword_ssn 的關鍵字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-11513">A keyword from Keyword_ssn is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-11514">當鄰近性300個字元以內時，DLP 原則就會偵測到這種敏感資訊類型的信賴度。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-11514">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-11515">函數 Func_unformatted_ssn 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-11515">The function Func_unformatted_ssn finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-11516">會找到來自 Keyword_ssn 的關鍵字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-11516">A keyword from Keyword_ssn is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-11517">DLP 原則在接近300個字元以內時，偵測到此敏感資訊類型的信賴度很低：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-11517">A DLP policy has low confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-11518">函數 Func_randomized_formatted_ssn 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-11518">The function Func_randomized_formatted_ssn finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-11519">會找到來自 Keyword_ssn 的關鍵字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-11519">A keyword from Keyword_ssn is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-11520">如果接近300個字元以內，則 DLP 原則偵測到此敏感資訊類型的置信量是55%：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-11520">A DLP policy is 55% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-11521">函數 Func_randomized_unformatted_ssn 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-11521">The function Func_randomized_unformatted_ssn finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-11522">會找到來自 Keyword_ssn 的關鍵字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-11522">A keyword from Keyword_ssn is found.</span></span>


```xml
<!-- U.S. Social Security Number (SSN) -->
  <Entity id="a44669fe-0d48-453d-a9b1-2cc83f2cba77" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_ssn" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_ssn" />
      </Pattern>
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_unformatted_ssn" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_ssn" />
      </Pattern>
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_randomized_formatted_ssn" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_ssn" />
      </Pattern>
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="55">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_randomized_unformatted_ssn" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_ssn" />
      </Pattern>
  </Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-11523">關鍵字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-11523">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_ssn"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-11524">Keyword_ssn</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-11524">Keyword_ssn</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-11525">SSA 編號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-11525">SSA Number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-11526">社會安全號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-11526">social security number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-11527">社會保障#</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-11527">social security #</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-11528">社會保障#</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-11528">social security#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-11529">社會安全性否</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-11529">social security no</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-11530">社會保障#</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-11530">Social Security#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-11531">Soc Sec</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-11531">Soc Sec</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-11532">Ssn</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-11532">SSN</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-11533">主旨 SSN</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-11533">SSNS</span></span>

## <a name="us--uk-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-11537">美國/英國</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-11537">U.S. / U.K.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="94f34-11538">護照號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-11538">passport number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-11539">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-11539">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-11540">九位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-11540">nine digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-11541">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-11541">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-11542">九個連續數位</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-11542">nine consecutive digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-11543">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-11543">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-11544">否</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-11544">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-11545">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-11545">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-11546">當鄰近性300個字元以內時，DLP 原則就會偵測到這種敏感資訊類型：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-11546">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-11547">函數 Func_usa_uk_passport 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-11547">The function Func_usa_uk_passport finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-11548">`Keywords_eu_passport_number`找到或的關鍵字 `Keywords_uk_eu_passport_number` 。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-11548">A keyword from `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_uk_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-11549">找到來自的關鍵字 `Keywords_eu_passport_date`</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-11549">A keyword from `Keywords_eu_passport_date` is found</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-11550">當鄰近性300個字元以內時，DLP 原則就會偵測到這種敏感資訊類型的信賴度。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-11550">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-11551">函數 Func_usa_uk_passport 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-11551">The function Func_usa_uk_passport finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-11552">`Keywords_eu_passport_number`找到或的關鍵字 `Keywords_uk_eu_passport_number` 。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-11552">A keyword from `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_uk_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span>

```xml
    <!-- U.S. / U.K. Passport Number -->
    <Entity id="178ec42a-18b4-47cc-85c7-d62c92fd67f8" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
       <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_usa_uk_passport" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_date" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_uk_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_usa_uk_passport" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_uk_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
    </Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-11553">關鍵字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-11553">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keywords_eu_passport_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-11554">Keywords_eu_passport_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-11554">Keywords_eu_passport_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-11558">護照</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-11558">passports</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-11559">passportno</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-11559">passportno</span></span>

## <a name="ukraine-passport-domestic"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-11568">烏克蘭護照（國內）</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-11568">Ukraine passport domestic</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="94f34-11569">此機密資訊類型僅可用於下列專案：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-11569">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-11570">資料遺失防護原則</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-11570">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-11571">通訊相容性原則</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-11571">communication compliance policies</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-11575">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-11575">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-11576">九位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-11576">nine digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-11577">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-11577">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-11578">九位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-11578">nine digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-11579">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-11579">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-11580">否</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-11580">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-11581">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-11581">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-11582">當鄰近性300個字元以內時，DLP 原則就會偵測到這種敏感資訊類型的信賴度。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-11582">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-11583">Regex Regex_Ukraine_Passport_Domestic 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-11583">The regex Regex_Ukraine_Passport_Domestic finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-11584">會找到來自 Keyword_Ukraine_Passport_Domestic 的關鍵字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-11584">A keyword from Keyword_Ukraine_Passport_Domestic is found.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Ukraine Passport Domestic -->
      <Entity id="1817a540-221f-4459-9202-3bd78b81d803" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Regex_Ukraine_Passport_Domestic"/>
          <Match idRef="Keyword_Ukraine_Passport_Domestic"/>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="ukraine-passport-international"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-11593">烏克蘭護照（國際）</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-11593">Ukraine passport international</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="94f34-11594">此機密資訊類型僅可用於下列專案：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-11594">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-11595">資料遺失防護原則</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-11595">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-11596">通訊相容性原則</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-11596">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-11597">資訊管理</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-11597">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-11598">記錄管理</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-11598">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-11599">Microsoft cloud app security</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-11599">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-11600">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-11600">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-11601">八個字元的數位元格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-11601">eight-character alphanumeric pattern</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-11602">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-11602">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-11603">八個字元的字母數位樣式：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-11603">eight-character alphanumeric pattern:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-11604">兩個字母或數位</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-11604">two letters or digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-11605">六位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-11605">six digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-11606">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-11606">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-11607">否</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-11607">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="94f34-11608">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-11608">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="94f34-11609">當鄰近性300個字元以內時，DLP 原則就會偵測到這種敏感資訊類型的信賴度。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-11609">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-11610">Regex Regex_Ukraine_Passport_International 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-11610">The regex Regex_Ukraine_Passport_International finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="94f34-11611">會找到來自 Keyword_Ukraine_Passport_International 的關鍵字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94f34-11611">A keyword from Keyword_Ukraine_Passport_International is found.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Ukraine Passport International -->
      <Entity id="cfbe032d-22e0-4f28-ab68-d66e9641f1e2" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_Ukraine_Passport_International"/>
          <Match idRef="Keyword_Ukraine_Passport_International"/>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```
